  <para style="h">ATNU-TNUYI AƁOZHIN</para>
  <para style="toc1">Atnu-tnuyi Aɓozhin</para>
  <para style="toc2">Atnu-tnuyi Aɓozhin</para>
  <para style="toc3">Atnu-tnuyi Aɓozhin</para>
  <para style="mt1">ATNU-TNUYI AƁOZHIN</para>
  <para style="im">Nyakayi–Luka nu</para>
  <para style="im">Aba nwo ɓei dna–Ata kpe lo m</para>
  <para style="im">Aye–A.D. 65–70</para>
  <para style="im">Aɓo nɓa kafi–Littafi ye gyi abye nu nɓo yi n Luka ɓei ka, woi wu ɓo n Yesu ɓei ya zhin dna anyi, wa gyi abye ncei dna ikklisiya. Wo ɓei ya shi abara ɓei bwa iko Shekwoyi nya ɓa zhin wazi aza 3,000 ɓa ye abui nyipyeyi gmanyi. (2:41) Ikklisiya n Urushelima, Nabari manayi kwa gnami har Samaria, n Bitrus tnu-tnuyi n wahalai nna ɓei ga a Yesu-viyi nyi. Wa wu Bulus zan-zan har abwa ngun ata woi zhin wazi n abyedo aba wa kmazo n Bulus zan-yi woi lo Roma. Aɓopmiyi ho da ngye Luka ɓei cei pma wa ka littafi tayi nkwo ɓa wu shi aɓei lo Bulus ya nzan-yi nwo ɓei je zan, aje wo wan, wa kpe fi.</para>
  <para style="iot">Aɓo-tukwo:</para>
  <para style="io1">1. Ikklisiya kmisunyi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 1:1-5:42">1:1–5:42</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">2. Wahala n Nabari pata-mwayi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 6:1-9:31">6:1–9:31</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">3. Bitrus atnu-tnu wazi nya <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 9:32-12:25">9:32–12:25</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">4. Bulus zan wazi nya kmisunyi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 13:1-14:28">13:1–14:28</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">5. Shaula zhin n Urushelima <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 15:1-41">15:1-41</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">6. Bulus wazi zan bayi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 16:1-18:22">16:1–18:22</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">7. Bulus wazi zan Tayi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 18:23-21:14">18:23–21:14</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">8. Bulus wan-wan nwo Roma loyi <char style="ior"><ref loc="ACT 21:15-28:31">21:15–28:31</ref></char></para>
  <para style="imte1">Atnu-tnuyi Aɓozhin</para>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="ACT 1"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1-2" style="v" pubnumber="1,2" sid="ACT 1:1-2"/> Emi nugundo nwo ye Shekwoyi nyi. Nɓo ku shin ho ka. Ma wu ho anya n Yesu ɓo wu aza. Wa wu wo abara kafin wo kpe eshe lo. <verse eid="ACT 1:1-2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 1:3"/>Shi wo ɓo laka evingwo wo ɓei bwa anyipyei shinyi woi wu wohin nwo wo abara aba. Ntu ge ɓa kpe ge wo wye-wyeyi lo. Woi da ɓo n ɓai tu Shekwoyi ebe ɓo.<verse eid="ACT 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Yesu Du Gun Lo Eshe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 1:4"/>N Wyihoi wagna ɓa ge, ɓa to kun n Urishelima m, ama ɓa pmi har Zafun Gyi-gyiyi wa ɓe, ntu ge alkawali Dada nya ɓa nu.<verse eid="ACT 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 1:5"/>Yohanna ɓei zhin baptizma n nuwan yi amma a ɓa zhin fye n j Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi.<verse eid="ACT 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 1:6"/>N Wyihoi wa je ɓa ba ɓe ɓa nya Yesu ge, “a ɓo gni a Yahudiyayi nkni sayi nuʼa? Wato a knu ɓa nu a Romayi aknu.”<verse eid="ACT 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 1:7"/>Yesu ɓo gna ɓa ge, “Efya nuwan nu tom fya kpe anyipyei yem.” <verse eid="ACT 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 1:8"/>Ama Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓei ga fye iko esa n wa ɓe ncei, fye da mi nabari dna n Urishelima n Yahudiya yi n Samariya yi n na bai vinya. Fye da ʼmi kala-la ɓo n vingwo.<verse eid="ACT 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 1:9"/>Safyewyi wa laka tulo ʼshe owo abara ɓa shi wo awye har wa bwi wye. <verse eid="ACT 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 1:10"/>Ɓa zhi ɓai shi awye ʼshe ɓa gye aza ngun aba na je bui-bui kpe. <verse eid="ACT 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 1:11"/>Aza n ɓa nu a gna “Agalili yi fye gye kniyi nu ʼshe a? She fye gye Yesu woi lo nyi elonu wo ɓa jeze ɓe.”<verse eid="ACT 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 1:12"/>Aɓeye vinya ɓo zhin kpe a zaitun ʼpe nu. Ɓa jezelo Urishelima mi. <verse eid="ACT 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 1:13"/>Ɓa lo ɓa ku fi n nyakun ʼshe ɓai zhin adduwa.<verse eid="ACT 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 1:14"/>Aza nyi n ɓa ɓei fi ɓo. Bitrus, Yohanna, Yakub, Andrawus, Filibus Toma Bartalamawus, Matta, Yakub Halfa nugun, Siman owo ye bayi ge Zelotes ɓedo n Yesu azaje yi. Na anyikozayi n Yesu ʼya yi. <verse eid="ACT 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 1:15"/>Wyiho ɓa ye zhi aza 120 ɓa zhin adduwa Bitrus wa laka gni wa da ɓo n ɓai.<verse eid="ACT 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 1:16"/>Wa gna “Emi azaje dole Shekwoyi ɓeda kwa nu tu n Yahuda tukwo. Woɓo la Yesu kun aɓo ku anabci zhin tu wo tukwo kafin ama wo. Esu Dawuda nu ɓo da, shin Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓei wu wo. <verse eid="ACT 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 1:17"/>Yahuda ɓo gnisun n yi nu. Har ma n zhin bara.” <verse eid="ACT 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 1:18"/>Amma wo ɓo la ekni si n na ʼgyiwye nukwoyi wa gyi wohin, Wa kaya har waɓaya. <verse eid="ACT 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 1:19"/>Aɓo ku ce wo vinya n Urushelima. A aba ho tuye ge, “ami ʼba.” <verse eid="ACT 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 1:20"/>Anabci ye dna n Zabura nu kwa da ge, “Fa owo puwa kwa wunya to oza wa dnam. ‘Njesun a lawo tnu-tnu ga ozado wa zhin.’<verse eid="ACT 1:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21-22" style="v" pubnumber="21,22" sid="ACT 1:21-22"/> “Dole ozado n yi mi wa la Yahuda apita n wo ɓo gnisun n yi tunyi n Yesu baptisma zhin sa har esa n wo ɓo lo ʼshe nyi.” <verse eid="ACT 1:21-22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 1:23"/>A ɓe n na za aye yi ngun-aba Yusufu Jastis (ko Barsabas) ɓedo n Matiyas yi. <verse eid="ACT 1:23"/><verse number="24-25" style="v" pubnumber="24,25" sid="ACT 1:24-25"/> Ɓa zhin adduwa ntu ge Shekwoyi wa wu ɓa oza na ɓa kni. Ɓa gna, “O Dagayi ho kpe eyi abugba yelo, wuyi oza nu ho ye nɓa mi wa la Yahuda apita, owo nu n wo la wo zokwo kni nyi.”<verse eid="ACT 1:24-25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 1:26"/>N adduwa zhin avun ɓa she kuriʼa, Kuriʼa wan kpe n Mathias. A wo kni, wa ze bara ɓedo awocei-gmanyi yi.<verse eid="ACT 1:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="ACT 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Pantikos Nyipyeyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 2:1"/>A mako ɓo ku sun ngu shi. Yesu ɓei fi. Pentikos nyipyei koi la wu vi a Yesu viyi ɓa yezhi. <verse eid="ACT 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 2:2"/>Sa fyewyi a wo aɓo ho ɓai ci ngye ogma jewyi, aɓo ci hi ɓa nu nyakun n ɓa ɓo fi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 2:3"/>Ɓa gye ena anyitala kwoi yakpe ɓa na tukwo. <verse eid="ACT 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 2:4"/>Oɓa vinya ɓa nu n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. Ɓai da ɓeda n na byei gbo-gbo n ɓa ta shin da m. Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi nu ɓo ga ɓa iko ye.<verse eid="ACT 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 2:5"/>A Yahudiyi yi ɓei fi n mwa n Urushelima n wyihi yi. Ntu ge ɓa la Shekwoyi tu n Urushelima mi. <verse eid="ACT 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 2:6"/>Shi aza ɓo wo kasun, ɓa kun ɓe ntu ge ɓa gye ɓo kwo nyi, Sai ɓa wo abara ɓai da ɓa bye, ceʼa wo ɓa.<verse eid="ACT 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 2:7"/>Ɓa nya ge, “Aza deye zhin a Galiliyi nu, ɓa mi n wuna ɓai da abye deyeʼa? <verse eid="ACT 2:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 2:8"/>Ya wo ɓai da ɓeda n byei nu aba n ya kun nyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 2:9"/>Eyi a Patiyayi Amidiyi, Alamitiyi, aza n ɓa kun n Mesopotamiya n Yahudayi, Kapadokiya, Pontus, Asiya. <verse eid="ACT 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 2:10"/>Filijiya, Pamfiliya, Masar n na abyei n ɓa she Libya gun nyi. Aza n Roma n ɓa zhin a Yahudiyi ɓedo n ɓai n ɓa zhin a Yahudiyayi alaloi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 2:11"/>Akaritayi ɓedo na, Larabawa yi. Ya wo ɓai da abye deye ɓai gna yi aɓo awo-woyi Shekwoyi nya.”<verse eid="ACT 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 2:12"/>Ca wo aza n kalayi. Ɓa gna, “kniyi nu wu la yiʼa?” <verse eid="ACT 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 2:13"/>Amma azaho ɓa kpe agye ɓa gna, “Ai ɓa ku nya nu sin.” <verse eid="ACT 2:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 2:14"/>Sai Bitrus n abara awo cei gmanyi (11) ɓa gna, “Efye vinya fye kna tnubua, Yi ye ya da ɓo n fyei, azhiɓeyi du na pi dai. <verse eid="ACT 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 2:15"/>Azaho n fye mi ku da ge, Yi ku onya nu sin. Ɓa to da gaiciyan sam. Aza ta sin nya n labmiyi la yim, wato karfe 9. <verse eid="ACT 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 2:16"/>Ɓeye kwa zhin nyi Joel Anabi ɓo ku ce da tunyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 2:17"/>Shekwoyi ɓo da ge, ‘Nna a nyipyeyi kmaknayi n ɓo ze omi Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ya kpe aza, efye anugun n anyigun yi ɓa ɓo zhin anabci. Efye a samari ɓa ɓo gye aɓe-wyegye. Azakwoyi ɓo nu ana. <verse eid="ACT 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 2:18"/>Emi Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi, ɓa ɓe tu emi abara anugbayi n anyikwoyi tukwo, ɓa ɓo zhin anabci. <verse eid="ACT 2:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 2:19"/>N ɓo zhin aɓo awo-woyi n ʼshe n ʼkni yi, Aɓo gye ami nonayi ɓedo anyi, awu nya yi. <verse eid="ACT 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 2:20"/>Npyei ɓo ze zhi-zhiyi, epya ko ze ami. Kafin Dagayi nyipyei dnawo nya ko ɓe. <verse eid="ACT 2:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 2:21"/>Oza n wa ye sun-sungye wo ɓa bwa. Ai gni wo n jesun.’<verse eid="ACT 2:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22-23" style="v" pubnumber="22,23" sid="ACT 2:22-23"/> “A Israilayi fye wo! Fye kpe la ge Shekwoyi nu ɓo zhin ama Yesu Nazaratiyi wa zhin aɓo wo-woyi n wo aba. Ama dna Shekwoyi shiri, wa fa fya zhin ampanyi na Roma yi, fya wu Yesu tu n zundu. <verse eid="ACT 2:22-23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 2:24"/>Amma Shekwoyi ɓo la wo gmi n wahala har wa wo laka n vingwo. Efi to zhinwo nyaho m.<verse eid="ACT 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 2:25"/>“Esu Dawuda ɓo da Yesu ɓeda wa gna, ‘Mi kpe lo Dagayi kunsun n miyi cici, woi bma mi zhin. Iko Shekwoyi nya koi ce mi bwa. <verse eid="ACT 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 2:26"/>Ce nu zhin mi yi dagma. Omi ʼgbe nunu yi n wo ciciyi. Mi kpe lo ge ko mi yi fi milo wo aba nu. <verse eid="ACT 2:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 2:27"/>Ho ta fami dna ena m, Ho taye oho Nugun Gyi-gyi-yi nayi kwa buo m. <verse eid="ACT 2:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 2:28"/>Ho ɓoje mi wye-wyei ga Ha ga mi agmada n ho abye.’<verse eid="ACT 2:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 2:29"/>“Omi azaje Dawuda ta da wohin nu ɓo m. Dawuda ɓei la fi a wo bi, owo vingwo shi lo n ya ba. <verse eid="ACT 2:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 2:30"/>Dawuda ɓo zhin anabci Shekwoyi nya nu. Woi kpe ge oza ɓe lo n wo ɓa zhin Kristi dna nwa a yawyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 2:31"/>Wo ɓo gye nya ko ɓe lo nabye, wa da Kristi kalala ɓo evingwo. Wa gna Kristi wye-wyei ta dna e nam Kwo kwa buo m <verse eid="ACT 2:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 2:32"/>Wo ɓei da Yesu nu ɓo, yi zhin aseda da nu ge Yesu la laka evingwo.<verse eid="ACT 2:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 2:33"/>“Wo lo n gnisun n Shekwoyi, Dada n la iko gawo wa tnu n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi, Elonu n fye gye n naiye.<verse eid="ACT 2:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 2:34"/>“Dawuda ta da wohin nu ɓo m. Woto shin gun lo ʼshen. Wa da ge, Shekwoyi wa da ɓo n mi Dagayi yi wato Kristi, wa gna, la sase nwu viyi nmiyi n latu aba. <verse eid="ACT 2:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 2:35"/>Har maze oho anuwuyi, oho apita kpe ʼba.<verse eid="ACT 2:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 2:36"/>“Ntu ce nu mi gna a Israilayi ge Yesu n fye ɓo wu nyi, Shekwoyi la wo ze Dagayi n Masihu yi.”<verse eid="ACT 2:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 2:37"/>Bitrus ɓeda ɓo ku lo aza sosai. Har ɓa gna, “eyi azaje, yi ɓa zhin wuna?”<verse eid="ACT 2:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 2:38"/>Bitrus wa gna, “Fye fa alaifi, fya yi Shekwoyi a zhin fye baptisma dna Kristi ye. <verse eid="ACT 2:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 2:39"/>Kristi ɓo ku alkawali zhin ga fye. Ofye n Shekwoyi la fye yi nyi, duk n fye aɓi yi, nge woɓa ga fye Zafun Gyi-gyiyi.”<verse eid="ACT 2:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 2:40"/>Bitrus ɓei zhin waʼazi Yesu nya wa gna ge ɓa ye abui ɓa vi Shekwoyi. <verse eid="ACT 2:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 2:41"/>Aza 3,000 ɓei ku gaiciya ga aku baptisma zhin ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 2:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 2:42"/>Ɓa ye ɓedo a Yesu viyi, abara ɓai wu ɓa nya, ɓai zhin zumun ta, ɓai zhin aduwa n gnisun.<verse eid="ACT 2:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 2:43"/>Ɓa ɓo wo edna n mwa cei wo ɓa. Abara n jesun ɓa zhin aɓo wo-woyi n mwa. <verse eid="ACT 2:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 2:44"/>A Yesu viyi ɓei zhin ɓai yezhi cici, ɓai gna anya n gnisun. <verse eid="ACT 2:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 2:45"/>Ɓa ɓo kun ɓa nyabwa, ɓa gna ngnisun, n aza yi n ɓa gyisan. <verse eid="ACT 2:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 2:46"/>Ɓai ga mwa-mwa nu aduwa nyakun, ɓai yezhi n aje puwa ntu zumunta ɓo. Ɓai gyi nyagyi ngnisun nagmadai. <verse eid="ACT 2:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 2:47"/>Ɓai ci Shekwoyi, Har ezhi vinya kwa dagma nɓai, har Shekwoyi woi ɓe ɓa begye fyegyi-fyegyi.<verse eid="ACT 2:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="ACT 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Bitrus N Yohanna Yi La Zabmazhi Kagna</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 3:1"/>Nwyihoyi n wyeshe yi, Bitrus n Yohanna yi, ɓa lo aduwa zhin ngnisun na za yi. <verse eid="ACT 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 3:2"/>Vivi n aduwa nyakun yi, ɓa gye za-bmazhi shi. A ɓo ma wo lo nu nu. Cici ai ɓe n woi n abwokumin manayi ʼgbe, vivi n aduwa nyakun yi. <verse eid="ACT 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 3:3"/>Shi Bitrus n Yohanna yi ɓei duya, wa ɓa sadaka.<verse eid="ACT 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 3:4"/>Ɓa shi wo awye, Bitrus wa ciwo ge ʼshi awye ya.<verse eid="ACT 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 3:5"/>Wa gye ngye ɓaye ɓa ga wo nya ho nu.<verse eid="ACT 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 3:6"/>Amma Bitrus wa ciwo ge, “Yito nagyiwye yi lo ya gahon, Amma miɓa ga ho nyado. Dna Yesu Kristi Nazarati eye laka ha zan-zan.”<verse eid="ACT 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7-8" style="v" pubnumber="7,8" sid="ACT 3:7-8"/> Bitrus wa shiwo bwa wa laka owo apita bwa lafiya wa gye agna. Wa zan woi gye agna. Wa kwo anyi woi ci Shekwoyi. Wa lo aduwa nyakun wa ci Shekwoyi.<verse eid="ACT 3:7-8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 3:9"/>Aza gye wo dna aduwa nyakun woi zan-zan, ɓa ci Shekwoyi. <verse eid="ACT 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 3:10"/>Ɓa kpe ge wo zhin nyaɓayi nu, n wo shi abwokunmi manayi gbe cici nyi. To ɓa kpe shi kwa ze woi zan-zan m. <verse eid="ACT 3:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 3:11"/>Ɓa busi lo Solomon ashiragyi, aba n wo ɓo gni n Yohanna n Bitrus shibwa, ce a wo ɓa vinya ntu ɓo wo-woyi ye ɓo.<verse eid="ACT 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 3:12"/>Bitrus wa gna, “A Israilayi kniyi nu zhin cei wo fya? Fyei shi yi awye ngye ya zhin deye n yihin iko yiʼa? <verse eid="ACT 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 3:13"/>Shekwoyi Ibrahim nya, n Ishaku yi, n Yakub yi ɓedo n yi azakwoyi nyayi na zhin deye, wo la Yesu ga mwa-mwa ntu aɓeye ɓo. Yesu n fye ɓo na wo aɓo n Bilatus abye nyi kwo shi ko nyi Bilatus ɓo la ye wa lo wo ya nyi. <verse eid="ACT 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 3:14"/>Fye to ɓo ye a lo oza Gyi-gyi-yi yam, sai ʼzawuyi. <verse eid="ACT 3:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 3:15"/>Fye ɓo la wye-wyei Dagayi wu, ama Shekwoyi ɓo la wye-wyei gawo njesun. Yohanna n mihin yi zhin aseda da nu gama yi ɓei ku wo gye n wye-wyeyi.<verse eid="ACT 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 3:16"/>“Gaiciya ga, dna Yesu eye okwo na ka oza deye gna.<verse eid="ACT 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 3:17"/>“Fye ɓei zhin Yesu aɓe deye dna n wyegma nu elonu ofye abyeda. <verse eid="ACT 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 3:18"/>Ama anabci nu ɓo nu. Gama dole Kristi wa sin wahala ye. <verse eid="ACT 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 3:19"/>Ko bmiya fya shan bugba do, fya ɓe Dagayi aba, Fye ye abui a zhan fye ya, fye ɓa bwa agmada m Shekwoyi aba. <verse eid="ACT 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 3:20"/>Shekwoyi wo ɓa je fye tnu n fye Masihu yi. <verse eid="ACT 3:20"/><verse number="21-22" style="v" pubnumber="21,22" sid="ACT 3:21-22"/> Gama woɓa sase n ʼshe har anya vinya la kun n laifi, ɓo nu aɓo ku da n kwo-kwoyi. Musa ɓo da ge Dagayi ɓa ga fye anabi nfye mi ngye mihin, sai fya wo wo. <verse eid="ACT 3:21-22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 3:23"/>Oza n wo to wo won, aɓa wu wo.<verse eid="ACT 3:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 3:24"/>“Samuila n Anabi yi, ɓei ku aɓe ye da nɓa zhin n anyipyei ye nyi. <verse eid="ACT 3:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 3:25"/>Fyei ɓedo lo nu alkawali n Shekwoyi ɓo ga Ibrahim nyi. Nge ntu na a Israila yi ɓo, anyi vinya ɓa bwa Shekwoyi anabarka. Fyehin kwa fye zhin anabi nu. <verse eid="ACT 3:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 3:26"/>Shi Shekwoyi ɓo ga wo abara wye-wyei n jesun wo ɓo tnu n wo yi n fye aba a Israila yi. Ntu ge wa tu fye anabarka. Wa pmi fye awye ya n fye alaifi.”<verse eid="ACT 3:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="ACT 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Ala Bitrus Wan N Yohanna Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 4:1"/>Amma sanu ɓa ɓei zhi ɓai daɓo na zayi nyi, a priest a dan-doka aduwa nyakun nya, n Assadukiyayi ɓa ɓe da ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 4:2"/>Ɓa gyi minagyi, Nge Bitrus n Yohanna yi ɓa fa waʼazi zhin Yesu kala-ka nya evingwo. <verse eid="ACT 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 4:3"/>Ɓa wan ɓa, ɓa ku ɓa gu fi n kurkuku, har efye a gyi. <verse eid="ACT 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 4:4"/>Amma aza nɓa ɓei wo Bitrus waʼazi nyi ɓa ga gaiciya. A Yesu viyi ɓa ku mwa begye har aza ɓa ku sun 5,000 (dubu ngun atnu).<verse eid="ACT 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 4:5"/>A ɓeye ɓo zhin, a Yahudiyi atukwoda, ɓai ye zhi n Urishelima n sayi. <verse eid="ACT 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 4:6"/>Annas Pirist dnagmayi ɓo nyi n Kayafa yi, Yohanna, Alekzanda n na zajeyi n ɓa nyi n prist bwa. <verse eid="ACT 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 4:7"/>A ɓe n Bitrus n Yohanna yi n ɓa ʼbye. Ɓa nya ɓa ge, “Fya bwa iko n na? Nyika ga fye izni fyei zhin ɓeyeʼa?”<verse eid="ACT 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 4:8"/>Bitrus n nunuyi n Zafun Gyi-gyi yi wa gna, “Eyi abye atukwoda dnagmayi. <verse eid="ACT 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 4:9"/>Fye daɓe manayi ye nu n na zhin zabmazhi nyi? <verse eid="ACT 4:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 4:10"/>Ya zhin deye dna Yesu ye nu, Wo nu zhin Kristi n fye ɓo zundu nyi. Amma Shekwoyi ɓei la wye-wyei gawo, owo iko na zhin ce, ko kunce lo fya kpe lo nu. <verse eid="ACT 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 4:11"/>Yesu Masihu nu n na daɓo ge, kuta n na nyamiyi na ko aɓo, oko nu la ze kuta kusurwa nya. <verse eid="ACT 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 4:12"/>Gni-gni to lo n na babaho yin, n Eshe sinta, eye do to lo n aza ɓa yi ɓa pwo nkwo aba m.”<verse eid="ACT 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 4:13"/>Shi ɓa ɓo gye Bitrus n Yohanna yi n bugba kala yi, ce a wo ɓa ntuge ɓa to zhin aza nu nɓa zhin makaranta m. Amma ɓa gye n sayi ge ɓa ɓo ku gnisun n Yesu yi. <verse eid="ACT 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 4:14"/>A shaula zhin yi to ɓo mi, ɓa na zabmazhi kagna ɓo m, ntu ge wo ɓo gni ɓo n wohin. <verse eid="ACT 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 4:15"/>Ɓa kun ɓa ya zhi ebmi.<verse eid="ACT 4:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 4:16"/>Ɓa nya aje ge, “Yi ɓa zhin wuna naza deye yiʼa? Yi ta mi ya na aɓo wo-woyi ye ɓom, aku ce kpe n Urushelima vinya. <verse eid="ACT 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 4:17"/>Amma yi ɓa mi ya hana nɓai to ɓa gyi abye m, ɓa ku ce pi. Ko kwa ɓa sin wahala.” <verse eid="ACT 4:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 4:18"/>Shi ɓa ɓo ku da lonu ɓa yi ɓa, ɓa gna ʼfye to je nyaho da tu n Yesu tukwon.<verse eid="ACT 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 4:19"/>Bitrus n Yohanna yi ɓa gna ge, fye gna yi kwo Shekwoyi ye ya vi oza ɓena nu kwo owo nya! <verse eid="ACT 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 4:20"/>Yi ta mi ya fa aɓo wo-woyi da ɓo, na yi ɓo gye Yesu woi zhin woi da njesun nyi m.<verse eid="ACT 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 4:21"/>A shaula zhinyi to ɓo mi ɓa ta ɓa m. Amma ɓa gna kni ɓa, ɓa fa ɓa lo. Ɓa ɓo gna ɓa ta ɓa, wahala ɓei ɓa laka, ntuge aza ɓo ci Shekwoyi ntu aɓo wo-woyi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 4:22"/>Zabmazhi ye ɓo ku aye bwa ngun-shinyi.<verse eid="ACT 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 4:23"/>Bitrus n Yohanna yi ɓa kuka ɓa lo ɓa da abara je enya n ko ku zhin.<verse eid="ACT 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aduwazhin N Latu Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 4:24"/>A Yesu viyi vinya ɓa yezhi, Ɓa zhin aduwa. Ɓa gna “O Dagayi n ha zhin eshe n ʼkni, a nuwan yi, n anya yi vinya n ɓa fi n ɓa nyi. <verse eid="ACT 4:24"/><verse number="25-26" style="v" pubnumber="25,26" sid="ACT 4:25-26"/> Sapai ho ɓo da ɓo eyi zakwoyi gbe Esu Dawuda, she Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓei wu wo. Knihi nu zhin abyedo gyi minagyi n Dagayi, amama ɓai pa kulu tu Shekwoyi dnagmayi tukwo a? Asu anyi nya ɓa ku gbe gun ntu ge ɓa sun kun n Shekwoyi Nugun yi!<verse eid="ACT 4:25-26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 4:27"/>“Enya nu n kwa zhin n naiye! Hirudus n Bilatus gwamna yi ɓedo n a Israilayi yi ɓa la ʼgbe dnado gabna n Shekwoyi nugun yi, oho nugun kni-kniyi, oho fyenu gyi-gyi-yi. <verse eid="ACT 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 4:28"/>Ɓa ta fa ɓo zhin ɓo n ho iko ye ɓa zhin. <verse eid="ACT 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 4:29"/>O Dagayi wo ɓa shaula nukwoyi, ha ga ho a fyenubugba kala ɓa zhin waʼazi. <verse eid="ACT 4:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 4:30"/>Tnu ho iko kagna nya yi, fa ya zhin aɓo wo-woyi dna n Yesu eye, oho fyenu gyi-gyi-yi.”<verse eid="ACT 4:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 4:31"/>Shi ɓa ɓei zo aduwa zhin, nyakun kwa shan-shan, oɓa vinya ɓa nu n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓa zhin waʼazi ntna edna.<verse eid="ACT 4:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 4:32"/>A Yesu viyi bugba vinya ɓei nyi gmanyi nu. Ozaho-zahoi to ɓo shi nyanyaho yi n wo gmanyi ɓo nun, ɓa ɓo ce ga aje.<verse eid="ACT 4:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aɓozhin-zhin Ngun Aba Tu Gyiwye Tukwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 4:33"/>Abara ɓa zhin waʼazi Yesu kalala nya evingwo. Zumunta ɓei nyi nna a Yesu viyi mi dei-dei. <verse eid="ACT 4:33"/><verse number="34-35" style="v" pubnumber="34,35" sid="ACT 4:34-35"/> San-gyi to ɓe nyi nɓa ba m. Ntu ge afwaiza ɓei ku oɓa afan kun ɓa ɓe nagyiwye yi n abara aba, ɓa zhin ampanyi cei gnisun.<verse eid="ACT 4:34-35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 4:36"/>Misali Yusufu (aje wo yi nugun waʼazi zhin yi) wo bi Saiprus wo zhin Levi bye nu. <verse eid="ACT 4:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 4:37"/>Wo ɓei la owo fwa knu, wa ɓe nnagyiwyei n aba, a gna aza n ɓa gyisan nyi.<verse eid="ACT 4:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="ACT 5"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 5:1"/>Amma ozaho ɓo nyi ai yi wo ge Hananiya, owo nyikwo Safiratu. Wo ɓ o la owo ʼkni kun ce. <verse eid="ACT 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 5:2"/>Ɓa kni agyiwye ɓa ɓe n cei ngye nya ɓa kun nu.<verse eid="ACT 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 5:3"/>Amma Bitrus wa gna wo, “Hananiya, Shetan la nu ho bugba har hoi ce akata fi Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. <verse eid="ACT 5:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 5:4"/>Ofwa oho nya nu ho ɓei n dama yi ha kun, ko kwa to ha kun m. Esa hola kun agyiwye zhin ho nya nu ha ga kwo shi ho ye. Kni a zhin hoi zhin nlaiʼa?”<verse eid="ACT 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 5:5"/>Hananiya n wo-woyi lo nu wa miya wa fi. Edna kwa wo azaho-zahoi. <verse eid="ACT 5:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 5:6"/>A samari ɓa ku aje puwo ɓa lo ɓa wo bi.<verse eid="ACT 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 5:7"/>Esa fyewyi owo nyikwo wa lo ɓe, to woi kpe enya nkwo ku zhin m. <verse eid="ACT 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 5:8"/>Bitrus wa nya wo ɓo. “Fya kun ofwa na gyiwyei layi nu?” Wa ye ge “Eh”.<verse eid="ACT 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 5:9"/>Bitrus wa gna wo, “Kni yi a zhin oho n ho ɓai fyei zhin shiri deye, fya mwi Shekwoyi zafun ko? Aza n ɓa bi oho ɓa nyi ɓa ɓe nyi ɓakaho bi.”<verse eid="ACT 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 5:10"/>N sayi-sayi wa fi. A samari ɓa ɓe ɓa wo lafi ɓa lawo ɓa biwo vivi nwo ɓai. <verse eid="ACT 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 5:11"/>Edna kwa wo ikklisiya vinya, du aza yi n ɓa ɓo ku ce wo.<verse eid="ACT 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 5:12"/>Abara ɓa gyi abye dna Solomon ashiragyi, n yezhi cici ɓai zhin aɓo wo-woyi n mwa. <verse eid="ACT 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 5:13"/>Azadoho to ɓei lo da ɓam, ama aza ɓei zhin ɓai gye ɓa mwa-mwa. <verse eid="ACT 5:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 5:14"/>Aza n mwa begye ɓa ga gaiciya anugbayi du na nyikwoza yi. <verse eid="ACT 5:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 5:15"/>A nyasan yi mwa begye, aɓe n ɓai nbmi ntuge Bitrus ofun kwa to ɓa, ɓa gwo kagna. <verse eid="ACT 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 5:16"/>Aza ɓa kun n Urushelima a kauye, ɓa ɓe nna nyasan yi du nna za yi nɓa ɓei n alijenu yi, a ɓa ka gna vinya.<verse eid="ACT 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aku Atnu-tnuyi Je Wan</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 5:17"/>Amma pirist dnagmayi n asadukiyi ɓa wo she ntu atnu-tnu manayi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 5:18"/>Ba wan abara ɓa fi ɓa n kurkuku.<verse eid="ACT 5:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 5:19"/>Amma nsukwoyi Malaika ɓe wa gu ɓa abaya ɓa kun. Wa gna ɓa ge. <verse eid="ACT 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 5:20"/>“Fye lo aduwa nyakun fye zhin waʼazi wye-wyei nya.”<verse eid="ACT 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 5:21"/>N labmi yi, ɓa lo aduwa nyakun ɓa zhin waʼazi. Amma pirist dnagmayi n wo atukoda aje yi, ɓa ye zhi na shaula zhinyi. Ɓa yi abara ɓe cei. <verse eid="ACT 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 5:22"/>Dan-sanda wa lo kurkuku to wa gye ɓa fi m. Ɓa lo ɓa da atukwoda nya ɓa gye. <verse eid="ACT 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 5:23"/>“Kurkuku abokunmi ɓo guguyi aza n ɓa gu aba nyi n zhi, amma esa ya guya, yi to gye zaho-zahoi n dna m.”<verse eid="ACT 5:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 5:24"/>Ce awo ɓa vinya, to ɓa kpe nya nɓa ɓa zhin. <verse eid="ACT 5:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 5:25"/>Ozaho wa ɓe wa da ge ai aza nfye zanshi nyi, ɓa fi nu n aduwa nyakun ɓai zhin waʼazi.<verse eid="ACT 5:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26-27" style="v" pubnumber="26,27" sid="ACT 5:26-27"/> Yan-sanda tukwoda, ɓa lo ɓa wan abara, ɓai zhin ɓa peceye, ntuge ɓa ɓo wo aza dna. Har ɓa ɓe n ɓai n ashaula zhinyi aba.<verse eid="ACT 5:26-27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 5:28"/>Pirist dnaygmayi wa nya ɓa ge, “Kni a zhin to fyei vi eyi wyidna ma? Yi ku gna fye ge fye to je waʼazi zhin. Amma Urushelima la nu n fye wu-wu yi. Fye ye a gye eyi laifi nu dna oza deye fi ko?” <verse eid="ACT 5:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 5:29"/>Bitrus wa gna ɓa ge, “Yi vi Shekwoyi ɓeda nu ndu oza nya. <verse eid="ACT 5:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 5:30"/>Fye ɓo la esu gyi to nshiwan, fya wo wu. Amma Shekwoyi eyi azakwoyi nya ɓo la wo laka evingwo. <verse eid="ACT 5:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 5:31"/>Shekwoyi lawo ze yerima ɓedo n gniyi. Wa zhin ce lo nu ntu ge a Israilayi ɓa ya bui, a zhin ɓa laifi gafara. <verse eid="ACT 5:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 5:32"/>Eyihin ɓedo n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi n Shekwoyi ga zaho-zahoi n ya, yi zhin aseda da nu.”<verse eid="ACT 5:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 5:33"/>Shi a shaula zhin yi ɓo wo lonu, ɓa gyi minagyi har ɓa ye ɓa wu ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 5:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 5:34"/>Amma Gamaliel wa da ɓo ge, “A la abara kun ya zhin n bmi kpa.” Gamaliel ɓo zhin ilimi da nu. Aza mwa ɓai kpe lonu.<verse eid="ACT 5:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 5:35"/>Wa gna wo azaje ge, “A Israilayi fye zhin peceiye enya yi nfye ye fya zhin aza ye nyi. <verse eid="ACT 5:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 5:36"/>Fye ku ze amui enya Theudas ɓo zhin? Wo ɓo ɓe n gye oza dnagmayi nu. Har aza 400 ɓa viwo. Amma shi aɓo wuwo owo aviyi ɓa gnami.<verse eid="ACT 5:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 5:37"/>“Elonu Yahuda Galili nya, ngadu sayi, wo ɓo ku aza bwi n mwa. Amma shi wo ɓo fi aza gna mi.<verse eid="ACT 5:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 5:38"/>“Ntu ce nu mi ye fya fa ɓa. Nɓa zhin n ɓahin tukwo nu sa fyewyi ko ɓa ze gboloyi. <verse eid="ACT 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 5:39"/>Amma ngye ɓa zhin Shekwoyi nya nu, fye ta mi fya hana ɓai m. Kada fya gye fyei zhin gaba n Shekwoyi.” <verse eid="ACT 5:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 5:40"/>A shaula zhin yi ɓa yi abara ɓa lu ɓa. Ba gna ɓa ge ɓa to je Yesu ɓeda da m. <verse eid="ACT 5:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 5:41"/>Abara kun ɓai dagma gama ɓa ku kunce ɓa sun wahala ntu Yesu ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 5:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 5:42"/>Ɓa gyi abye fyegyi-fyegyi n aduwa nyakun ɓai wu nya ɓai zhin waʼazi ge Yesu nu zhin Kristi.<verse eid="ACT 5:42"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="ACT 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 6:1"/>Shi a Yesu-viyi ɓei ku mwa begye a wahala ya kala ku. A Helleniyi ɓai gna, ata gye ɓa nuwan lo n ɓa anyigbayi-yin. A gna a Ibraniyi anyi-gbayi nyagyi ga lo.<verse eid="ACT 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 6:2"/>Abara ɓa yezhi ɓa gna. “Waʼazi zhin yi tnu-tnu nu. Yi ta wun esa ya ntu nya gyi gna ɓo m. <verse eid="ACT 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 6:3"/>Fa ya kni aza tnaba eyi m. Aza nɓa nunuyi n Zafun yi! N nyagyi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 6:4"/>Ntu ge ya mi ya bwa sa ya zhin aduwa n waʼazi ɓedo n wu-wu yi.”<verse eid="ACT 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 6:5"/>Shaula ye kwa da ɓa, ɓa kni Istifanus, (Istifanus ɓei nunuyi n Zafun yi sosai). Ɓa kni njesun Filibus, Buruhoris, Nikano, Timon, Barminas n Nikolawus, Antakiya nya. Wo ɓei zhin ebye do nu n wo ɓo ga gaiciya. <verse eid="ACT 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 6:6"/>Abara ɓa zhin aduwa ntu ɓa ɓo, ɓa kpe ɓa abwa tukwo.<verse eid="ACT 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 6:7"/>A da Shekwoyi nabari abaho-bahoi. Aza n mwa ɓai ga gaiciya n Urushelima har du Ayahudiya yi aprist yi.<verse eid="ACT 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 6:8"/>Istifanus ɓei nu Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi iko yi. Ntu ce nu wa mi wa zhin aɓo wo-woyi.<verse eid="ACT 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 6:9"/>N wyihoi a Yahudiyi ɓa na ɓo n woi har a Yahudiyi n ɓa kun n Sirine, Alekzanda n Masar. Tarki Silisiya nya Asiya yi ɓa ʼgbe dna do. <verse eid="ACT 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 6:10"/>Amma ɓa to ɓo min n Istifanus ɓo m. Gama wo ɓei nunuyi n ɓeyekpe yi, ɓedo n Zafun yi.<verse eid="ACT 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 6:11"/>Sai ɓa ɓe aza yi ɓa ce akata fi Istifanus. Ɓa gna ge wa da Musa ɓenukwoyi woi ce akata njesun.<verse eid="ACT 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ala Istifanus Wan</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 6:12"/>Deye kwa ga aza minagyi, A Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓa wan wo ɓa ɓe n woi n a shaula zhinyi aba. <verse eid="ACT 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 6:13"/>Aseda katai da ɓa gna, “Istifanu wa da ɓeda nukwoyi ntu aduwa nyakun tukwo ɓedo n Musa owa yi.<verse eid="ACT 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 6:14"/>“Yi ku wo woi da ge, Yesu ɓa la aduwa nyakun ya, wa she Musa owa ya.” <verse eid="ACT 6:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 6:15"/>Aza vinya n ɓa ɓei fi ɓo nyi ɓa gye Istifanus awyeba la shando ngye malaika nya!<verse eid="ACT 6:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="ACT 7"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 7:1"/>Pirist dnagmayi wa nya wo ge, “Aɓe ye wu lo nu.” <verse eid="ACT 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 7:2"/>Istifanus wa gna ge, “Shekwoyi ɓei wu wohin tukwo eyi dada Ibrahim aba n Irak kafin wo lo Suriya. <verse eid="ACT 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 7:3"/>Shekwoyi ɓei gna wo ge wo fa ʼkni, n wo azayi wa lo aba n wo ɓa wu wo. <verse eid="ACT 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 7:4"/>Wa fa Kaldiya ʼkni wa lo Haran. Wa sase ɓo har owo dada wa fi, Shekwoyi wa gna ge wo lo Israila kni. <verse eid="ACT 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 7:5"/>Shekwoyi to ɓo sa ekni gawo m, amma wo ɓei zhin wo Alkawali ekniyi nya vinya. Alkawali ye ɓo nu peceiye nu.<verse eid="ACT 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 7:6"/>“Shekwoyi ɓo gna wo ge owo ayawyi ɓo fa ekniye ɓo zhin bauta ekni do har aye 400. <verse eid="ACT 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 7:7"/>Amma Shekwoyi alkawali nu ge, wo ɓei kun ɓa n bauta. Wa ta ekni n kwa fi ɓa n bauta nyi.<verse eid="ACT 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 7:8"/>“N sahi nu n Shekwoyi ɓo gna Ibrahim wa zhin kachiya. Deye zhin tuze nu Shekwoyi alkawali nya. A zhin Ishaku kaciya woi na anyipyei nymwa-nyimwa. Ishaku wa ma Yakub, Yakub wa ma eyi azakwoi awo-cei-aba a Yahudiyi bye. <verse eid="ACT 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 7:9"/>Aza deye ɓa wo she n Yusufu yi, ɓa wo kun <verse eid="ACT 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 7:10"/>wa ze fyenu dna n Masar ʼkni. Amma Shekwoyi ɓei kunsun nwoi, wa gni wo nwo awahala vinya, wa zhin Firʼauna Sa-Masar yi wa ye wo. Shekwoyi wa ga Yusufu ɓeyekpe, kwa zhin Firʼauna wa gwamna ga wo n Masarʼkni, wa wo ze tukwoda n garukwo.<verse eid="ACT 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 7:11"/>“Sa fyewyi mikun laka n Kanʼana. Eyi adada to ɓa bwa nyagyi m. <verse eid="ACT 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 7:12"/>Shi Yakub ɓo wo ge nyagyi lo n Masar, wa tnu n wo aɓi ɓa lo ɓa si. <verse eid="ACT 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 7:13"/>Ba je bwa ɓayi lo, Yusufu wa wu ɓa wohin tukwo. A lo n ɓai n Firʼauna ba. <verse eid="ACT 7:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 7:14"/>Sai Yusuf il wa tnu wo dada ɓo ɓedo n wo azaje yi, oɓa vinya ɓa ɓei nyi 70 nu. <verse eid="ACT 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 7:15"/>Yakub wa ɓe Masar, nɓonu n wo ɓo fi n wo anugun yi. <verse eid="ACT 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 7:16"/>A ɓei la ɓa ku lo n cei n Kanʼana kni, a bi ɓa n Sakar kni n Ibrahim ɓo si nyi.<verse eid="ACT 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17-18" style="v" pubnumber="17,18" sid="ACT 7:17-18"/> “A Yahudiyi ɓa ku mwa begye, Esa wo vi n Shekwoyi ɓa gni ba. Amma esu ho wa gyi be. To wa gye wo anuwan n Yusufu ajeyin. <verse eid="ACT 7:17-18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 7:19"/>Esuhi wa gaɓa wahala, wa tu dole ɓa wu ɓa aɓi.<verse eid="ACT 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 7:20"/>“Nsayi nu aɓo ma Musa, amma shi owo azamayi ɓei gye wo zhin oɓi manayi nu ɓa wo so har apya ngun-ata. <verse eid="ACT 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 7:21"/>Shi ɓa ɓo gye ɓa tami nwo som, dole ɓa ya wo. Har Firʼauna nyigun wa wo bwa, wa wo ze owo nugun. <verse eid="ACT 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 7:22"/>Wa wu wo ɓeyekpe a Masar nya. Har Musa wa ze oza dnagmayi.<verse eid="ACT 7:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 7:23"/>“Musa woi na ayei 40, wa ɓe owo azaje aba. <verse eid="ACT 7:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 7:24"/>Shi wo ɓo lo wa gye Masar ʼza woi ga Israila za wahala, wa Masar yi za wu. <verse eid="ACT 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 7:25"/>Musa wagye ge owo azaje ɓa gye ge Shekwoyi na tnu woi, ntu ge wa bma ɓa zhin. Amma ɓa to ɓei gye lo nun.<verse eid="ACT 7:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 7:26"/>“Nwyihoi wa lo wa gye a Israilayi ɓai sungu ɓahin-ɓahin, wa gna kni ɓa wa gna, ‘kwo to bmiya lo fya sungu fyehin-fyehin m.’<verse eid="ACT 7:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 7:27"/>“Ama ɓa nya wo ge, ‘nka dna ho alkali n yi tukwa? Ngye ha nuwan n yi. <verse eid="ACT 7:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 7:28"/>Ho ye ha wu mi nu, n gye shi ho wui Masar yi ʼza nsu nyi.’<verse eid="ACT 7:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 7:29"/>“Shi Musa ɓo wa lonu wa busi wa lo Midiya kni. Har wa ku aɓi bwa n ɓo ngun-aba.<verse eid="ACT 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 7:30"/>“Shi wo ɓo bwa aye shinyi ɓo, Malaika ɓe wo aba nfwa. Wa gye ena anyitala n wu vivi n Sinai pei. <verse eid="ACT 7:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 7:31"/>She wo ɓo gye ceʼa wo wo n mwa, wa lo ntu ge wo gye. Wa wo begye kwoi yi wo. <verse eid="ACT 7:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 7:32"/>Omi nu zhin Shekwoyi oha dada Ibrahim, Ishaku, n Yakubu yi nya.” Musa wo dna wa ku awye bwi.<verse eid="ACT 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 7:33"/>“Dagayi wa gna wo ge, ‘La ho abuada kun, ntu ge ho gni aba gyi-gyiyi nu. <verse eid="ACT 7:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 7:34"/>Mi ku omi aza bwi ci wo n Masar, Mi ye ma kunɓa n wahala. Ɓe ma tnu ho ha lo Masar.’ <verse eid="ACT 7:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 7:35"/>Oza nɓa ɓo na wo aɓo nsapa ɓai gna nyikanu na ze ho begyi-i nwadayi n yi tukwoa? Shekwoyi wa je tnu nwoi nu. A ɓei tnu n Musa yi nu wa zhin ɓa tukwoda wa gni ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 7:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 7:36"/>Musa ɓei ku aɓo wo-woyi zhin n Masar kafin wo kun ɓa. Ɓa pi ela byei-byei ya, ɓa zan-zan n zhabui ɓai jeze kpe har aye shinyi (40).<verse eid="ACT 7:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 7:37"/>“Musa ɓei gna aza ge, ʼShekwoyi ɓei ga fye anabi nwu gye mi n fye mi. <verse eid="ACT 7:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 7:38"/>Deye gaiciya nu, gama Musa nu ɓei dna aza tasin n Malaika yi n wo ɓei gaɓa Shekwoyi awyidna n zhabui nyi.<verse eid="ACT 7:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 7:39"/>“Amma eya dada ɓo la Musa aɓo na, har ma ɓai ye ge ɓa jeze lo Masar. <verse eid="ACT 7:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 7:40"/>Ba gna Haruna ge wo zhin ɓa eshan, n kwo ɓa je lo n ɓai n Masar, gama ɓa ta kpe nya lo n kwo ku zhin Musa, n wa kun ɓa n Masar nyi m. <verse eid="ACT 7:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 7:41"/>Sai ɓa zhin nakwo ɓiyi, ɓa ga kwo sadaka aminya ɓa dagma.<verse eid="ACT 7:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 7:42"/>“Shekwoyi kwa wa fa ɓa, har ɓa ga npyei, epya, ɓedo n akpasuyi mwa-mwa. Shekwoyi wa nya Israilayi n Amos gbe ge, Fye ɓo ga mi nu sadaka ami nya sa fye ɓei zan-zan anye shinyi n zhabui nyi? <verse eid="ACT 7:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 7:43"/>Awo, of ye bugba ɓei shi na ashekwoyi do aba nu. Ngye sakut n kaiwe yi. Ntuce nu nɓa tnu nfyei n bauta ndu Babila ya.<verse eid="ACT 7:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 7:44"/>“Eyi adada ɓei aduwa zhin ba yi shi, ɓa ɓei allo yi shi, n Shekwoyi awyidna yi ka kpe. A ɓei zhin ɓa nwu dai-dai nu ngye shi malaika ɓai wu Musa. <verse eid="ACT 7:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 7:45"/>Aye mwa begye avun Joshua wa sun okun n abye do yi, Ɓa aduwa zhin ɓa la ɓe n cei. Ɓa zhin ampanyi nkwoi har Esu Dawuda sa.<verse eid="ACT 7:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 7:46"/>“Shekwoyi ɓei la Dawuda tu anabarka, har Dawuda wa ye ntu ge wa mi nyakun ntu Shekwoyi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 7:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 7:47"/>Amma Solomon nu ɓei mi nyakun yi. <verse eid="ACT 7:47"/><verse number="48-49" style="v" pubnumber="48,49" sid="ACT 7:48-49"/> Amma Shekwoyi ta dna aduwa nyakun, n na mi n abwayi m. ‘Eshe nu zhin mi asese ba. Ekni kwa zhin mi apita kpe ba.’ Nya nu n Dagayi wa da. Kni nyakun yi pya nu n ho ɓa mi, n mi ɓa mi ma dna koʼa? <verse eid="ACT 7:48-49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="ACT 7:50"/>Omi nu to zhin Eshe n kni yi m?<verse eid="ACT 7:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="ACT 7:51"/>“Efye aza bugba kala kpe yi! Fye ɓa gyi abye fyei na Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi aɓo? Efye adada ɓo ku zhin, ekonu nfye zhin nfye hin. <verse eid="ACT 7:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="ACT 7:52"/>Ɓa ɓei ga anabi wahala, har ɓai wu anabi n ɓa da ge Masihu ɓelo nyi, Owo n fya ga a wu wo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 7:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="ACT 7:53"/>I, efyehin fya Shekwoyi awyidna wunya ko shi ko nyi fya gwo ɓa n a malaika akun.”<verse eid="ACT 7:53"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ala Istifanus Wu Nna Kuta Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="ACT 7:54"/>A Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓa gyi minagyi n Istifanus yi. <verse eid="ACT 7:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="ACT 7:55"/>Amma Istifanus ɓei nunuyi n Zafun yi, wa shi awye ʼshe wa gye Shekwoyi mwa-mwa wye. Har n Yesu yi gni agni-gni n Shekwoyi bwai-zhe bwa. <verse eid="ACT 7:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="ACT 7:56"/>Wa gna, “Migye eshe lo nguya gni n Yesu yi gni a gni-gni n Shekwoyi bwai-zhe bwa.”<verse eid="ACT 7:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="ACT 7:57"/>Ɓa tabwa shi wo ɓai gu ɓa atnubua, ɓai ɓewyi ntuge wa cepi. <verse eid="ACT 7:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="ACT 7:58"/>Ɓa gni wo ɓa gmiwoya n zhi mi ntu ge ɓa kni wo akuta. Ɓa oɓa aje kmaya zhi Samari ho ai yi wo ge Bulus, woi dna Ɓa ajeyi wye.<verse eid="ACT 7:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="ACT 7:59"/>Shi ɓa ɓo kni wo akuta Istifanus wa zhin aduwa wa gna Dagayi Yesu gwo mi wye-wyeyi. <verse eid="ACT 7:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="ACT 7:60"/>Wa ce akwo-kwo wa da ɓo n kala yi wa gna, “Dagayi zhin ɓa gafara,” wa fi wo nya.<verse eid="ACT 7:60"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="ACT 8"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 8:1"/>A ɓo da Bulus ntu Istifanus fi ɓo. Esayi a ga Yesu-viyi wahala, har kwa ɓa ze dole ɓa busi ɓa lo Yahudiya ɓedo n Samaria yi. <verse eid="ACT 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 8:2"/>A Yahudiyi, a Shekwoyi aza, ɓa ɓe ɓa Istifanus bi. <verse eid="ACT 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 8:3"/>Amma Bulus wa lo labaho-bahoi woi ga a viyi wahala, woi lo a puwa woi kun ɓa ɓe cei, Anugbayi du na nyikwoyi, woi lo ɓai n kurkuku.<verse eid="ACT 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Filibus Wa Lo Samariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 8:4"/>A viyi n ɓa ɓo busi nyi ɓa lo aba gbo-gbo ɓai zhin waʼazi Yesu nya. <verse eid="ACT 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 8:5"/>Filibus wa lo Samaria wa da nabari Kristi nya nbwai. <verse eid="ACT 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 8:6"/>Aza ɓo kna tnubua ge wo ɓei zhin aɓo wowoyi n ɓa ba. <verse eid="ACT 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 8:7"/>Woi kun azafun nukwoyi ya, anyasan yi ɓai bwa lafiya. <verse eid="ACT 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 8:8"/>Aza ɓo dagma n mwa n ezhi yi.<verse eid="ACT 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9-11" style="v" pubnumber="9,10,11" sid="ACT 8:9-11"/> Ozaho ɓei nyi ɓo a yi wo ge Siman. Wo zhin ɓeyi nu, wo ɓei mi woi zhin aɓo gbo-gbo har ai da wo ɓo ngye wo zhin Kristi nu. <verse eid="ACT 8:9-11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 8:12"/>Amma shi Filibus ɓei zhin ɓa Yesu waʼazi ge wonu zhin Masihu, njesun wa gna ɓa Shekwoyi bemi ɓo, aza ɓa ɓei ga gaiciya nyi, a ku ɓa zhin baptizma. <verse eid="ACT 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 8:13"/>Siman ce, wa gaiciya ga har a ku wo zhin batizma. Wa vi Filibus cei wo wo, ntu aɓo wowoyi ɓo nwo zhin nyi.<verse eid="ACT 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 8:14"/>Shi abara n Urushelima ɓei wo ge a Samariya yi ku gaiciya ga, ɓa tnu n Bitrus ɓedo n Yohanna yi ɓa lo Samariya. <verse eid="ACT 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 8:15"/>Ɓa lo ɓa si ɓa zhin aduwa ga ɓa, ntu ge ɓa gwo Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. <verse eid="ACT 8:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 8:16"/>Ɓa to ɓei gwo Zafun kpam, aɓo bwa ɓa baptizma nu zhin dna n Yesu Kristi eye mi. <verse eid="ACT 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 8:17"/>Bitrus n Yohanna yi ɓa kpe ɓa abwa n tukwo ɓa gwo Zafun Gyi-gyiyi.<verse eid="ACT 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 8:18"/>Shi Siman ɓo gye lo nu, wa ga agyiwye ntu ge wa si iko hi.<verse eid="ACT 8:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 8:19"/>Wagna ge “Mi ye iko ye lo ntu ge aza gwo Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi, esa ma tu ɓa bwa cei n tukwo.”<verse eid="ACT 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 8:20"/>Bitrus wa gna wo ge, “Oho n ho agyiwyei fye ku zhangma. Ho gye ge ho ɓa mi ha si Shekwoyi kyauta ko? <verse eid="ACT 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 8:21"/>Ho ta gni deye bwa n zayi m, gama oho bugba to wu lo n Shekwoyi bwa m. <verse eid="ACT 8:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 8:22"/>Fa ɓenukwoyi ye ya zhin aduwa ntu ge Shekwoyi wa zhin ho gafara. <verse eid="ACT 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 8:23"/>Gama mi gye shewo lo ɓedo n laifi n ho bugba.”<verse eid="ACT 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 8:24"/>Siman wa gna ge, “Zhin aduwa ntuge aɓo nukwoyi ye ta bwa min.”<verse eid="ACT 8:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 8:25"/>Shi ɓa ɓo ku waʼazi zhin n Samaria ɓa je ze lo Urushelima. Ɓai zhin waʼazi nabari manayi nya n zokwo.<verse eid="ACT 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 8:26"/>Amma malaika gna Filibus ge, “Lo Urushelima zokwo n Gaza zhabui bwa.” <verse eid="ACT 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 8:27"/>Wa lo wa gye Habashayi za woi ɓe. Wo ɓei zhin tnu-tnuyi n Sarauniya Kandas nya nu. Woi zhi sujada zhin n Urushelima. Wo ɓei zhin oza kakayi nu. <verse eid="ACT 8:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 8:28"/>Woi zhi dna karusa woi ba nya dna Littafi Ishaya nya.<verse eid="ACT 8:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 8:29"/>Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa da ɓo n Filibus yi ge, “Lo vivi n karusa yi.” <verse eid="ACT 8:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 8:30"/>Filibus wa lo wa wo nya n wo ba. Wa nya wo ge, “Ho kpe nya ye lo n ho ba?”<verse eid="ACT 8:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 8:31"/>Ozahi wa gna ge, “Mɓa kpe ye n wuna, to oza yi lo n wo ɓa ga mi awyegan ma?” Wa ci Filibus ge wo gun tu karusa wa sase n gnisun woi.<verse eid="ACT 8:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 8:32"/>Nya nyi n wo ɓei ba: “A lo n woi ngye ekni n ana wu ba, ngye kugya sanu a gbe kwo eyi ya. To wa daɓon. Wa wo pipi.<verse eid="ACT 8:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 8:33"/>“Ntu wohin tukwo gba ɓo, to a gye wo ɓe manayi m. Ntu ge aza n wo ʼsa, ɓa ɓei zhin aza nukwoyi nu. Har ɓa wo wu.”<verse eid="ACT 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 8:34"/>Oza kakayi wa nya Filibus ge, “Ishaya ɓo da wohin nu ɓo ko ozado?”<verse eid="ACT 8:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 8:35"/>Sai Filibus wa ya wo awyega wu nya na da ntu Yesu tukwo.<verse eid="ACT 8:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 8:36"/>Shi ɓa ɓei lo ɓa gye nuwan, zahiwa cige, “Ma gye nuwan dna nyi, kni ɓa zhin to ha zhin mi batizma ma?”<verse eid="ACT 8:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 8:37"/>Filibus ci wo ge, “A ɓa mi a zhin ho baptizma n dai ho la gaiciya ga n ho bugba yi vinya.” Wa gna “Mi la gaiciya ga ge Yesu Kristi nu zhin Shekwoyi nugun.”<verse eid="ACT 8:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 8:38"/>Wa kpe karusa gni, ɓa ka fi n nuwan a zhin wo batisma. <verse eid="ACT 8:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 8:39"/>Shi ɓa ɓei kun n nuwan Zafun Gyi-gyi-gyi-yi wa la Filibus to za kakayi wa je wo gye m amma walo wo nya woi dagma. <verse eid="ACT 8:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 8:40"/>Sa fyewyi Filibus a gye wo gni n Azatus, wa da nabari manayi n bwai, dna ezhi doho-dohoi woi duya har wa lo Kaisariya.<verse eid="ACT 8:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="ACT 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Abuiye Ɓo Wowoyi Nya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 9:1"/>Amma Bulus ɓei gna ye wa wu a Yesu viyi, ntu cenu wa lo prist dnagmayi aba n Urushelima. <verse eid="ACT 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 9:2"/>Wo ɓei ye ntu ge ɓa dna egbe do n woi, ɓa g wo takarda ntu ge walo Dimashika wo wan a Yesu viyi ɓe cei n Urushelima.<verse eid="ACT 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 9:3"/>Shi wo ɓo wu vi n Dimashika yi, buzangna dnagmayi eshe kwa bmiya fi wo. <verse eid="ACT 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 9:4"/>Wa miya shi ekni wa wo ai yiwo, “Bulus, Bulus kniyi nu zhin hoi gami wahala?”<verse eid="ACT 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 9:5"/>Wa nya ge, “nka nu da ɓoa?” Begyehi kwa gna, “Omi, nu Yesu, n ho ga wo wahala nyi.”<verse eid="ACT 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 9:6"/>“Laka ha lo zhimi n ɓo gna ho nya miye.”<verse eid="ACT 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 9:7"/>Aza n ɓa ɓei gnisun n woi nyi ce a wo ɓa, to ɓa mi n nyaho da m, gama ɓa ɓo wo oza ɓeda amma to ɓa gye za m. <verse eid="ACT 9:7"/><verse number="8-9" style="v" pubnumber="8,9" sid="ACT 9:8-9"/> Shi wo ɓo laka la to wa wye ɓa ye wo kpe yam. A shi wo busi bwa shi shi nu wa lo Dimashika. Wa dna ɓo anyipyei ngun-ata to woi gye wyeba m, to woi gyi nyagyi m.<verse eid="ACT 9:8-9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 9:10"/>Yesu viyi ho ɓo dna n Dimashika ai yi wo ge Hananiya. Dagayi wa da ɓo n woi ngye wo nuna n ge, “Hananiya,” wa gna mi gni nyi Dagayi.<verse eid="ACT 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 9:11"/>Dagayi wa gna wo ge, Lo zokwo tatayi, Ha lo Yahuda puwa, Bulus dna lo ɓo woi zhin aduwa. <verse eid="ACT 9:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 9:12"/>Mi ku wu wo n ruya ge, oza ɓelo wa kpe wo awye ya, a yi wo ge Hananiya.<verse eid="ACT 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 9:13"/>Hananiya wa gna ge, Dagayi mi ku aɓo nukwoyi wo n Bulus zhin lo na viyi n Urushelima mi. <verse eid="ACT 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 9:14"/>Yi ku wo shi wo ku aza wan n mwa fi n kurkuku, woi la izni gwo n na prist dnagmayi aba, ntu ge wa ga a Yesu viyi wahala, n tna edna n Dimashika ye.<verse eid="ACT 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 9:15"/>Amma Dagayi wa gna wo e, “lo ho zhin ɓo ma gna ho, gama Bulus zhin omi ʼza kni-kniyi nu ntu ge wa dami nabari n abye aba, n asu yi, na Israilayi vinya. <verse eid="ACT 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 9:16"/>N ɓa wu wo shi wo ɓa sin, wahala nsun ntu mi ɓo.”<verse eid="ACT 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 9:17"/>Sai Hananiya wa lo, wa to Bulus bwa wa gna wo, “Omi zado Bulus Yesu n wa wu ho wohin n zokwo nyi, wo na tnu mi ntu ge ha nu Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi, ha gwo wyeba gye njesun.”<verse eid="ACT 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 9:18"/>Nsai-sayi anya ɓa kaya ngye ashiwan gulu n Bulus awye, wa gwo wyeba gye a zhin wo batizma n sai-sayi. <verse eid="ACT 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 9:19"/>Wa gyi nyagyi wa bwa kala. Wa dna ɓo n gnisun n a Yesu viyi anyi-pyei fyewyi. <verse eid="ACT 9:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 9:20"/>Wa lo aduwa zhin ba, ntu ge wa da nabari manayi Yesu nya, n ge wo zhin Shekwoyi nugun nu.<verse eid="ACT 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 9:21"/>Ca wo aza, ɓa nya ge, ʼoza deye nu to ɓo zhin, woi ga a Yesu viyi wahalan, har woi ɓe Dimashika ntu ge, wo wan ɓa lo cei n Urushelima m?<verse eid="ACT 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 9:22"/>Bulus wa gyi abye n waʼazi yi sosai, har ma wa du a Yahudiyi n ɓa nyi n Damashika nyi, ngye shi wo daɓo tu n Yesu tukwo ge wo nu zhin Masihu.<verse eid="ACT 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 9:23"/>Safyewyi a Yahudiyi ɓa zhin shaula ntu ge ɓa wu wo. <verse eid="ACT 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 9:24"/>A ku ce gna Bulus ge aza zhi lo na bokunmi ɓai zan wo shin n sukwoyi n nyipyei ntu ge ɓa wu wo. <verse eid="ACT 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 9:25"/>Shi ɓa ɓei ku kpe, a Yesu viyi ho ɓa la wo dna n cekun n sukwoyi, ɓa gun kpe n garu ɓa ya wo shi n wun yi ebmi wa lo wo nya.<verse eid="ACT 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 9:26"/>Shi wo ɓo si Urushelima woi ye wa ye gu a Yesu viyi, amma ɓa wo wo ʼdna ʼdna ɓa gye ge wo zhin ɓa dabara nu wa wan ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 9:27"/>Nsayi Barnaba wa ɓe n Bulus yi n abara aba, wa wu ɓa ngye shi Bulus ɓo gye Dagayi, n nya yi n Dagayi ɓo gnawo. Wa wu ɓa njesun, waʼazi n wo zhin lo n iko yi ntu Yesu ɓo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 9:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 9:28"/>Nsayi ɓaye ɓa go wo, wa kunsun n aviyi cici. <verse eid="ACT 9:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 9:29"/>Wa zhin waʼazi n Yesu eye yi ntna edna. Amma a Yahudiyi n ɓa da Helleni bye, ɓa nu nwo ɓei naɓo n ɓai nyi, ɓa zhin shaula ntuge ɓa wu wo. <verse eid="ACT 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 9:30"/>Amma a Yesu viyi ɓa ku wo ɓa la wo ɓa lo woi n Kaisiariya ɓa tnu woi n Tarsusu owo ayi.<verse eid="ACT 9:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 9:31"/>Nsayi Ikklisiya kwa bwa lafiya n Yahudiya, Galili n Samariya yi kwa mwa n kalayi. Ɓai zan-zan dna n Dagayi dnawo, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi woi ga a bugba fu.<verse eid="ACT 9:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aɓo Wowoyi Ngun Aba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 9:32"/>Bitrus wa lo abai gbo-gbo woi ɓi ɓa gna har wasi a viyi aba n Lida. <verse eid="ACT 9:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 9:33"/>Wa gye ozaho a yiwo Aniyas nayi fifiyi da ntu n gado har aye nyimwa-nyimwa. <verse eid="ACT 9:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 9:34"/>Bitrus wa gna wo ge Aniyas Yesu Kristi la ho kagna, laka ha zan-zan, wa gwo kagna n sayi-sayi. <verse eid="ACT 9:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 9:35"/>Sai aza vinya n Lida ɓedo n Sharo yi ɓa ga gaiciya ngye shi ɓa gye Aniyas woi zan-zan.<verse eid="ACT 9:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 9:36"/>N Joppa nyikwoza ho dna ɓo n zhin viyi a yi wo Dokas ko Tabita woi bma aza zhin tun ɓa ga a sanyi ba. <verse eid="ACT 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 9:37"/>Dna sayi, nyasan wo, wa fi, owo anugundo ɓa nuwan fu wo ɓa wo pa ɓa wo ya dna n ʼnyakun she, kafin a bi wo. <verse eid="ACT 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 9:38"/>Amma ɓa wo ge Bitrus lo n Lida ɓa tnu wo ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 9:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 9:39"/>Ba lo n woi aba n ɓa ɓei woi dna. Anyigbayi ɓo fi ɓo nmwa ɓai ci bwi ɓawu wo anya n Tabita ɓei zhin woi ga ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 9:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 9:40"/>Bitrus wa ɓa kunya wa zhin aduwa, wa gna Dokas wo la kala, wa kpe awye ya wa gye Bitrus nu wa laka sase. <verse eid="ACT 9:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 9:41"/>Wa shi wo bwa wa laka wa yi a viyi ɓedo anyigbayi ɓa ɓe wa wo ga ɓa.<verse eid="ACT 9:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 9:42"/>Aza n mwa begye ɓa wo nabari ye, ɓa ku gaiciya ga. <verse eid="ACT 9:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 9:43"/>Bitrus wa sun sa dna n Joppa n Siman ʼpabmiyi puwa.<verse eid="ACT 9:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="ACT 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Malaika Wa Ɓe Koniliyus Aba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 10:1"/>Italiya yi ʼza ɓo dna n Kaisari- ya ai yi wo ge, Koniliyus, wo ɓei zhin soja tukwo da nu. <verse eid="ACT 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 10:2"/>Wo ɓei zhin oza nu nwo wo Shekwoyi edna duk n wo puwayi, woi ga sadaka dai-dai, woi zhin aduwa cici. <verse eid="ACT 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 10:3"/>N Iwyihoi n wyeshe yi wa gye ruya, malaika wa ɓe wo aba.<verse eid="ACT 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 10:4"/>Malaika gna wo ge, owo sadaka n aduwa yi ɓa ku si Shekwoyi aba.<verse eid="ACT 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5-6" style="v" pubnumber="5,6" sid="ACT 10:5-6"/> Tnu oza wa lo Joppa wo yi Bitrus ɓe cei, wo dna lo n Siman pa bmiyi puwa, wa e ho puwa.<verse eid="ACT 10:5-6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 10:7"/>Shi malaika ɓo la wonya lo, Koniliyus wayi wo afyenu ngun aba ɓedo n soja yi gmanyi. <verse eid="ACT 10:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 10:8"/>Wa da ɓa nya ko ku zhin wa tnu ɓa, ɓa lo Jop-pa.<verse eid="ACT 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9-10" style="v" pubnumber="9,10" sid="ACT 10:9-10"/> Nyipyei bayi ɓai ku wu vivi n Joppa yi, dei-dei n sayi yi Bitrus wa zhin aduwa mikun ɓei gun wo, n sayi sai wagye ngye wo nuna.<verse eid="ACT 10:9-10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 10:11"/>Wagye eshe la guya, wa gye kwanu dnagmayi kwoi ɓe kni. <verse eid="ACT 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 10:12"/>Wa gye abu gbo-gbo nfi, alu n awa i, n na nya yi n na ta ye ge a Yahudiyi ɓa gyi m.<verse eid="ACT 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 10:13"/>Wa wo ai da wo ge, lo ho kni hawu, ha gyi.<verse eid="ACT 10:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 10:14"/>Wa gna awo Dagayi ho kpe lo ge shi a mami, mi to shin ɓa gyi m ntu ge eyi awyidna ta ye ge yi gyi ɓam.<verse eid="ACT 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 10:15"/>Wa wo ai je wo da ge, to pmi Shekwoyi ɓeda bma m, n dei nya wa dage kwo gyi-gyi-yi lo kwo zhin gyi-gyi-yi nu.<verse eid="ACT 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 10:16"/>Wagye deye har abwa ata. Kafin a la kwo lo cei n she njesun. <verse eid="ACT 10:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 10:17"/>Bitrus wa damu, To wa kpe ɓo ye n ko nyi m. Dei-dei n sayi yi a tnu-tnu yi ai si puwa n wo ei dna nyi.<verse eid="ACT 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 10:18"/>Ba nya ɓo kwo gye Bitrus dna lo.<verse eid="ACT 10:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 10:19"/>Bitrus woi dna woi zhin nubo tu n nya nwa gye nyi. Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa da wo ge aza zhi lo ɓai ye ho. <verse eid="ACT 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 10:20"/>Lo da ɓa ha gni lo n ɓai, mi na tnu ho.<verse eid="ACT 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 10:21"/>Bitrus wa shin lo wa gna ominu zhin oza fye ye nyi, kniyi nu a?<verse eid="ACT 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 10:22"/>Ɓa gna wo soja tukwoda ɓo nu, Shekwoyi dnawoyi ngye shi malaika ɓe wo aba wa wu wo Bitrus aba wa ɓe ntu ge wa wu wo enya n Shekwoyi ye wa zhin.<verse eid="ACT 10:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bilrus Wa Lo Koniliyus Puwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 10:23"/>Ba ku wangye n Joppa, n labm yi wa gni lo n ɓai ɓedo na Yesu viyi hoi n Joppa.<verse eid="ACT 10:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 10:24"/>Nyipyei bayi ɓa si Kaisariya, Koniliyus woi shi wo pmi ɓa, shi ɓa ɓo ɓe wa yi wo azaje n anugundo yi ntu ge ɓa wo Bitrus ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 10:24"/><verse number="25-26" style="v" pubnumber="25,26" sid="ACT 10:25-26"/> Shi Bitrus ɓei lo Koniliyus puwa, Koniliyus wa yashi wa ga Bitrus mwa-mwa. Bitrus wa gna wo ge wo la laka ntu ge mi to zhin Shekwoyi, nu m.<verse eid="ACT 10:25-26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 10:27"/>Wa laka gni ɓa da ɓo na jei fyewyi, ɓa lo aba n aza ɓo yezhi nyi.<verse eid="ACT 10:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 10:28"/>Bitrus wa gna ge fye kpe lo ge a Yahudiya yi awyidna ta ye ge yi lo abye do puwa m. Amma Shekwoyi ku wumi dna n ruya ge mi to ci zaho-zahoi wyegba m. <verse eid="ACT 10:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 10:29"/>Ce na zhin mi ɓe wolo-wolo. Fye ye kni nya?<verse eid="ACT 10:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 10:30"/>Koniliyus kwa wa gna, “Anyipyei ngun-anyi n sayi mi yi dna mi-i zhin aduwa ma gye oza gni n ma bye, aje bui-bui yi kpe. <verse eid="ACT 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 10:31"/>Wagna mi ge omi aduwa n sadaka yi ɓa ku si Shekwoyi aba. <verse eid="ACT 10:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 10:32"/>Wa gna mi ge, Mi tnu Siman Bitrus ɓo n Joppa, wo dna lo n dna gbe n Siman pabmiyi puwa. <verse eid="ACT 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 10:33"/>Ce nu a zhin ma tnu ho ɓo hoi e. Yi zhi yi pmi ho nu ya wo enya n Shekwoyi ye ha gna yi.”<verse eid="ACT 10:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 10:34"/>Bitrus wa gna mi ku gye a Yahudiyi nu to zhin aza n Shekwoyi ye gmanyi m. <verse eid="ACT 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 10:35"/>Dna abye doho-doho yi Shekwoyi na za yi lo ɓai ga wo mwa-mwa, ɓai zhin ɓe manayi wohin kwa woi gwo ɓa.<verse eid="ACT 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36-37" style="v" pubnumber="36,37" sid="ACT 10:36-37"/> Ho ku nabari manayi wo a Israilayi salama n Shekwoyi yi dna n Yesu eye kwo? Almasihu nu zhin Dagayi anyi zhinyi. Nabari ye la gnami vinya n Yahudiya kwoi ya n Yohanna batisma yi dna Galili. <verse eid="ACT 10:36-37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 10:38"/>Ho kpe lo ge Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓo gnisun n Yesu yi, wa ga wo iko woi ka aza gna du azayi n ɓa aljanu yi, ntu ge Shekwoyi ɓo kunsun n woi.<verse eid="ACT 10:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 10:39"/>Eyihin abara yi zhin aseida da nu, tu aɓe deye n wo ɓei zhin dna Israila ɓedo n Urushelima yi, aba a ɓo wu wo tu n zundu nyi.<verse eid="ACT 10:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40-41" style="v" pubnumber="40,41" sid="ACT 10:40-41"/> Anyipyei ngun ata avun, Shekwoyi wa je wo wye-wyeyi ga wa wu wohin tukwo aza aba. To ge aza vinya m, sai dai eyi n yi ɓo gyi ya sin, n gnisun n woi, woi la lakala ev-ingwo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 10:40-41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 10:42"/>Wa tnu yi ntu ge ya zhin waʼazi ge Shekwoyi la Yesu ze wadayi. Anyi nya vinya awye-wyei da na fifiyi. <verse eid="ACT 10:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 10:43"/>Anabi vinya ɓo ku ka tu nwo tukwo ɓa gna ozaho-zaho nwa ga gaiciya, aba zhinwo alaifi gafara dna Yesu ye.<verse eid="ACT 10:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 10:44"/>Shi Bitrus ɓo da lo nu, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa ɓe kpe nɓa vinya, n ɓa ɓo wo wo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 10:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 10:45"/>Ce a wo a Yahudiyi n ɓa ɓo kun ɓe n Bitrus yi nyi, ɓa to ɓo kpe ge aɓa ga abye do Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi m.<verse eid="ACT 10:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46-47" style="v" pubnumber="46,47" sid="ACT 10:46-47"/> N tna jeje ɓawo ai da ɓo anyitalayi gbo-gbo ɓai ci Shekwoyi. Bitrus wa nya ge, “Zaho lo nwo ɓa wo ɓi ge mi to zhin ɓa batizma m, ɓai la Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi gwo ngye yihin?” <verse eid="ACT 10:46-47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="ACT 10:48"/>Sai wa zhin ɓa batizma dna n Yesu Masihu ye. Koniliyus wa gna Bitrus ge wo la dna kpa n ɓai anyipyei fyewyi.<verse eid="ACT 10:48"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="ACT 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Bitrus Wa Wu Lafiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 11:1"/>Safyewyi abara ɓa wo, abye do gaiciya ga ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 11:2"/>Shi Bitrus ɓo jezeɓe Urushelima, ɓa naɓo n woi. <verse eid="ACT 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 11:3"/>Ɓa gna wo ge, “Ho zhin zumunta na ʼbye do yi hoi gyi nyagyi n ɓai.” <verse eid="ACT 11:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 11:4"/>Bitrus wagna ɓa, nabari vinya. <verse eid="ACT 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 11:5"/>Wa gna, “Nwyihoi n Joppa ma zhin aduwa ma gye ruya. <verse eid="ACT 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 11:6"/>Ma gye kwanu dnagmayi koi shin zhin eshe. Ma gye abu fi gbo-gbo ana, alu, awa nya yi du anya yi n yi ta gyi m. <verse eid="ACT 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 11:7"/>Ma wo begye kwoi gna ‘Kni wu ha gyi.’<verse eid="ACT 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 11:8"/>“Ma gna awo Dagayi mi to shin anya deye gyi n yi awyidna gna yi to gyi nyin.<verse eid="ACT 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 11:9"/>“Amma ma je wo ge to gna ato bmiya lon, Shekwoyi woi ku gna ge a bmiya lom. <verse eid="ACT 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 11:10"/>Ko ɓo zhin lo nu har abwa ta, kafin aje kwanu yi la lo cei n she. <verse eid="ACT 11:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 11:11"/>Sa fyewyi aza ɓe ngun-ata ɓai kun n Kaisariya ɓai ɓe mi yi. <verse eid="ACT 11:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 11:12"/>Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa gna mi lo, mi to gna ge ɓa zhin abye do nu m. Aza ngun-tnanyi ɓa gni lo mi-i har Kaisariya. <verse eid="ACT 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 11:13"/>Ozaho wa gna yi, ngye shi malaika ɓei gna wo ge wo yi mi ɓe cei. <verse eid="ACT 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 11:14"/>Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa gna wo ngye shi mihin Bitrus ɓa wu-wo gni-gni zokwo.<verse eid="ACT 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 11:15"/>“Ma ya nabari manayi da, to mi yi ga zo m, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa yakpe ɓa n ɓa ɓo zhi ɓo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 11:16"/>Deye kwa zhin mi ma pa Dagayi ɓeda ɓo n wo ɓo gna ge Yohanna ɓo zhin batizma n nuwan yi, amma a ɓa zhin fye batizma n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. <verse eid="ACT 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 11:17"/>Shi Shekwoyi nu ɓo ga ɓa nyaga ngye yihin nyi, nka nu n miyi ma na ɓoʼa?”<verse eid="ACT 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 11:18"/>Shi a zaje ɓo wo lonu ɓa ku ɓa aɓena fa ɓa ci Shekwoyi. Ɓa gna, E, Shekwoyi la dama ga abye do ɓa ɓe wo aba ɓa bwa wye-wyei nyalo-nyalo.<verse eid="ACT 11:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abui-ye Yi N Antakiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 11:19"/>Aviyi n ɓa ɓei busi n wahala sa ai la Istifanus wu nyi ɓa lo har Finishiya Saiparus, ɓedo Antakiya yi ɓa da nabari manayi. Amma n na Yahudiyi aba kawai. <verse eid="ACT 11:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 11:20"/>Ama dai a viyi n ɓa ɓo lo Antakiya ɓai kun n Saiparus nyi, ɓa da nabari manayi ye, ga Helleniyi. <verse eid="ACT 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 11:21"/>Dagayi ɓo la ɓa ɓeda tu anabarka, har abye deye ɓa ku gaiciya ga.<verse eid="ACT 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 11:22"/>Shi ikklisiya Urushelima nya ɓei wo, ɓa tnu n Barnaba yi n Antakiya ntu ge wa bma a Yesu viyi zhin ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 11:23"/>Wasi Antakiya wagye aɓo wowoyi, n Shekwoyi a zhin nyi, a dawo n mwa, wa mi ɓa zhi, wa gna ɓa ge ɓa la nyima Dagayi. <verse eid="ACT 11:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 11:24"/>Barnaba ɓo zhin oza manayi nu n nunuyi n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. Deye kwa zhin har aza mwa begye ɓa ga Dagayi gaiciya.<verse eid="ACT 11:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 11:25"/>Barnaba wa laka wa lo Tarsusu woi ye Bulus. <verse eid="ACT 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 11:26"/>Wa ɓe woi n An-takiya ɓa fi ɓo eye yi gmanyi ɓai wu a viyi woi-woi nya. N ɓo nu a ɓei ya a viyi yi ge a Yesu viyi.<verse eid="ACT 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 11:27"/>Nsayi anabi ho ɓa kun n Urushelima ɓa ɓe Antakiya. <verse eid="ACT 11:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 11:28"/>Gmanyi n ɓa mi a yi wo Agabus wa laka gni wa zhin anabci shi Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓei wu wo, wa gna mikun ɓe lo n Israila kni. Deye ɓo zhin dna n sa nu Klaudiyus ɓo gyi ebe nyi. <verse eid="ACT 11:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 11:29"/>Ntu cenu a viyi ɓa zhin shawara ɓa tnu n nyagyi yi ga a viyi n Yahudiya, zaho-zahoi wa ga shi wo ɓa mi. <verse eid="ACT 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 11:30"/>Ɓa ku anyagyi ye ga Baranaba n Bulus yi ge, ɓa lo atukoda ikklisiya nya cei n Urushelima.<verse eid="ACT 11:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="ACT 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Bitrus Wan-wan Nwo Gni-gni Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 12:1"/>Dna n sayi esu Hirudus wa laka, woi zhin gaba na gaiciya ga yi. <verse eid="ACT 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 12:2"/>Wa bara gmanyi wu, watau Yakub Yohanna zado. <verse eid="ACT 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 12:3"/>Wa gye deye kwoi da a Yahudiyi, wa Bitrus wan wa wo gu n Paska sa. <verse eid="ACT 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 12:4"/>Wa wo dna n kurkuku, a soja ngun tnanyi ɓai gu wo. Hirudus ɓei n nufi ge wa wu wo nu n Paska avun. <verse eid="ACT 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 12:5"/>Amma aduwa zhin n wyenyi yi ɓa gun lo Shekwoyi aba, ikklisiya nu ɓo zhin aduwa ntu ge Shekwoyi wa gu wo dna n kurkuku.<verse eid="ACT 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 12:6"/>Amma n sukwoyi kafin a da wo wa, woi wangye dna na soja ngun aba atan-tasin, na gmai fi wo abwa ababa, na soja ajei zhi na bokunmi. <verse eid="ACT 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 12:7"/>Safyewyi wa gye buzangna wa gye malaika gni n wa ba wa gna wo, “La pye ha laka.” Shi wo ɓo da lonu a gna kaya zhi n kni. <verse eid="ACT 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 12:8"/>Malaika wa gna wo ge, “Ku ha je kpe ha ku abuada fi.” Waku zhin lonu wa je wo gna ge ku ho koti kpe ha vi mi ɓe.<verse eid="ACT 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 12:9"/>Bitrus wa gmi n kurkuku woi vi malaika lo. Amma wa gye ngye wo nuna nu. <verse eid="ACT 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 12:10"/>Ɓa du abokunmi n gun aba ya, ɓa ɓe abokunmi sunkna nya. Ɓa guya n ɓahin yi, ɓa duya ɓa zan-zan fyewyi malaika wa fawo.<verse eid="ACT 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 12:11"/>Bitrus n sayi wa kpe ge, Dagayi la wo malaika tnu, woi gni wo n Hirudus akun. <verse eid="ACT 12:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 12:12"/>Shi wo ɓo gni wa zhin tunani fyewyi, wa laka wa lo Maryamu Yohanna ʼya puwa, aba na aza ɓei yezhi ɓai zhin aduwa nyi.<verse eid="ACT 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 12:13"/>Wa je aba, ɓi nyikwoyi ho ai yi wo Roda, wa ɓe ntu ge wa gu aba ya. <verse eid="ACT 12:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 12:14"/>Shi wo ɓo kpe ge Bitrus begye nu, a da wo n mwa sosai. Wa busi lo mi wa gna aza ge Bitrus gni lo na bokunmi. <verse eid="ACT 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 12:15"/>To ɓa ga wo gaiciya m, amma to wa fa da ɓo m, sai ɓa gna Bitrus malaika nu.<verse eid="ACT 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 12:16"/>Bitrus wa gyi abye woi je aba Ɓa lo ɓa guya ceʼa wo ɓa. <verse eid="ACT 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 12:17"/>Wa gna ɓa ge ɓa ku ce pi, wa wu ɓa enya n kwa zhin, “Fye ku gna Yakub na za je yi, enya ko ku zhin.” Wa fa ɓa wa lo wo nya.<verse eid="ACT 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 12:18"/>N labmi yi a kurkuku da ku je-je ɓa nya ge Bitrus ma? <verse eid="ACT 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 12:19"/>Hirudus wa ku a soja wu. Ntu ge ɓa ɓo fa Bitrus wapwo. Nsayi wa lo Kaisariya wa sase bwai anyipyei fyewyi.<verse eid="ACT 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 12:20"/>N Kaisariya azaho ɓa ɓe ɓai kun Taya n Saidon yi, ntu ge ɓa gye Hirudus wo to ɓo dagma n ɓa yi m, amma ɓa ɓo ku ze anugundo ntu gniko gni ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 12:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 12:21"/>Ɓa nyipyei shi ntu ge ɓa wo Hirudus ɓeda. N wyihi wa ku wo asu jekpe wa ɓe wa tu wo asu ku-jara ntu ge wa da ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 12:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 12:22"/>Aza a ɓowyi ɓa gna, “Begye ye to zhin oza nyanu m, amma shekwoyi nyanu.” <verse eid="ACT 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 12:23"/>Nsayi-sayi yi malaika Dagayi nya wa ɓe wo n nyasanayi, avin ɓa gyi wo har wa fi, ntu ge wo to ɓei ga Shekwoyi mwa-mwa m.<verse eid="ACT 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Barnaba N Bulus Yi N Antakiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 12:24"/>Shekwoyi ɓeda kwa gyi abye wolo-wolo har a bwa a viyi n mwa begye.<verse eid="ACT 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 12:25"/>Barnaba n Bulus yi ɓa lo aza gye n Urushelima. Shi ɓa ɓo ku ɓo zo n ɓa ɓei lo zhin, ɓa jeze ɓe Antakiya n gnisun n Yohanna Marukus yi.<verse eid="ACT 12:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="ACT 13"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 13:1"/>Anabi ɓedo na malami yi ɓei mwa n Antakiya, Barnaba yi ɓei nyi n ɓa mi n Siman yi. Lukiyas n Manaya ɓei nyi n jesun, ɓedo n Bulus yi. <verse eid="ACT 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 13:2"/>N wyihoi ɓai zhin aduwa Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa cige, “Mi ye Bulus lo n Barnaba yi ntu tnu-tnu ɓo n mi ɓa gaɓa”. <verse eid="ACT 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 13:3"/>Shi ɓa ɓo ku aduwa n azumi yi zo, ɓa tuɓa anabarka ɓa ya tnu-tnu yi.<verse eid="ACT 13:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 13:4"/>Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi kwa wa ze ɓa gna bye. Ɓa lo Selusiya n Saparus yi. <verse eid="ACT 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 13:5"/>N ezhi ho ai yi ko ge Salamis, ɓa lo a Yahudiyi aduwa nyakun ɓa zhin waʼazi ɓo. Yohanna Markus ɓei knusun n ɓai.<verse eid="ACT 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6-7" style="v" pubnumber="6,7" sid="ACT 13:6-7"/> Ɓa zhin waʼazi n ekniyi vinya. Sanu ɓa ɓei si Pafos ɓa gye anabi katai ho, ai yi wo ge Bar-Yesu. Wo ɓei zhin esu nugundo nu. Esu yi ɓei zhin oza hankali da nu. Wa yi Bulus n Barnaba yi ntu ge ɓa zhin wo waʼazi. <verse eid="ACT 13:6-7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 13:8"/>Amma Elimas anabi katai hi, Owo ye maʼana nu, wa gna su ge wo to gwo ɓa ɓeda m. Wo to ɓei ye ge osu yi wo ga Shekwoyi ɓeda gaiciya m.<verse eid="ACT 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 13:9"/>Ntu cenu Bulus wa gyi minagyi sosai. Ntu ge wo ɓei nunuyi n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi. <verse eid="ACT 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 13:10"/>Wa ci wo ge, “Oho shetam ɓi ho zhin oza nukwoyi nu. Ho ta ye anya manayi m. Ho ta fa gaba zhin ɓo n Dagayi m? <verse eid="ACT 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 13:11"/>Nsaiye kwa Shekwoyi la kni tu ho. Ho ta gye wyeban har esa fyewyi.” Nsayi-sayi wa ze wyebuayi. Wa laɓa woi zan oza shin wa shi wo busi bwa. <verse eid="ACT 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 13:12"/>Shi esu yi ɓo gye lonu, wa ga Shekwoyi gaiciya n sai-sayi. Wa wo Shekwoyi dna n jesun.<verse eid="ACT 13:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Wa Lo Turki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 13:13"/>Bulus kuwa n wa nugundo yi ɓa fa Pafos ɓa lo Parga n Panfiliya ʼkni, Yohanna Markus ɓei jeze ya nu wa lo Urushelima. <verse eid="ACT 13:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 13:14"/>Amma Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓa godiya lo Antakiya n Bisidiya ʼkni. Ɓa lo aduwa nyakun n Satiwyi yi. Ɓa ɓei zhin ɓa lo aduwa n wyiyi nu. <verse eid="ACT 13:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 13:15"/>Shi aɓo la nya zo ba n ataurat ɓedo n anabawa yi, anya Bulus n wo ɓeda yi lo, wa ɓe wa da.<verse eid="ACT 13:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 13:16"/>Bulus wa lakala gni wa ya ɓeda wa cige, “Ofye a Israilayi n azayi n ɓa ga Shekwoyi mwa-mwa nyi.”<verse eid="ACT 13:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 13:17"/>“Shekwoyi ɓei kni ʼya dada wa gaɓa mwa-mwa dna Masar wo ɓei zhin deye n sayi nu n wo ɓei kun ɓa n Masar nyi. <verse eid="ACT 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 13:18"/>Wa kun sun n ɓai har aye shinyi n zhabui. Ɓai zan-zan laɓa n bmana. <verse eid="ACT 13:18"/><verse number="19-20" style="v" pubnumber="19,20" sid="ACT 13:19-20"/> Shi ɓa ɓei lo Kanʼana wa sun kun ga ɓa, har abye ngun-tnaba ku fi kutu-kutu Wa fi ɓa n alkali akun har aye 450. Oza n wo ɓei ya tu ɓa wonu zhin anabi Samuila.<verse eid="ACT 13:19-20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 13:21"/>“Nsayi aza gyi wye nge aga ɓa esu, Shekwoyi wa ga ɓa Saul Kish nugun. Wo ɓei zhin Banyami bye nu. Wa gyi be aye shinyi. <verse eid="ACT 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 13:22"/>Anuna Shekwoyi wa shin wo ya wa dna Dauda be. Dauda ɓei zhin ozanu n wo bugba ɓei shi n Shekwoyi aba. <verse eid="ACT 13:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 13:23"/>Njesun Dauda bye nu, wato Yesu ɓei nu Shekwoyi alkawali wa gn Israila.<verse eid="ACT 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 13:24"/>“Amma kafin wo ɓe, Yohanna Baptizma zhin yi ɓei la ɓe kpa. Wa zhin waʼazi ge aza ɓa fa ɓa laifi, ɓa pmi ɓe Shekwoyi aba. <verse eid="ACT 13:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 13:25"/>Sanu Yohanna ɓei ye wa fa tnu-tnu wa cige, ‘Fye gye ge mi zhin Kristi nu? Ai wo ɓa ɓe esayi fyewyi. Mi zhin za gbagbayi nu n waba sosai.’<verse eid="ACT 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 13:26"/>“Omi azaje Ibrahim a yawyi n fye abye do yi n fye wo Shekwoyi dna nyi, gni-gni ye zmn fye nya nu. <verse eid="ACT 13:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 13:27"/>A Yahudiyi n Urushelima, ɓei nu Shekwoyi ɓeda ɓa Yesu wu. Ɓa to ɓei kpe nya ye n ɓa zhin m. <verse eid="ACT 13:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 13:28"/>Ɓa to ɓei kpe nya ye n ɓa ɓa wu wo tu kwo m. Ntu cenu ɓa gna Bilatus ge wo wu wo kawai. <verse eid="ACT 13:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 13:29"/>Shi ɓa ɓei la wo wu wato ɓai ku anabi ɓeda nu a wo bi.<verse eid="ACT 13:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 13:30"/>“Amma Shekwoyi wa lawo kala n vingwo. <verse eid="ACT 13:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 13:31"/>Aza ku gye wo n jesun, wato aza n ɓa ɓei kun Galili ɓa gni Urushelima lo nwoi oɓanu ɓei da n ɓa gbei pei-pei ge Yesu ɓo la laka n vingwo.<verse eid="ACT 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32-33" style="v" pubnumber="32,33" sid="ACT 13:32-33"/> “Nabari nu kuwa n ya ɓe fye cei, Shekwoyi gni-gni la ɓe ya ba, ntu ge Yesu la laka n vigwo, Zabura sura 2 cige, ‘Nnaiye mila ho ze omi ɓi sosai.’<verse eid="ACT 13:32-33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 13:34"/>“Shekwoyi ɓei zhin alkawali ge, wo ɓa la Yesu kala n vingwo, wo ta shan fi m. Alkawali kwo-kwo yi kwa cige, Miɓa zhin ga ho anya wo-woyi n mi ɓei gna Dauda nyi. <verse eid="ACT 13:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 13:35"/>Zabura cige, Shekwoyi ta fa wo za Gyi-gyi-yi wa bwo m. <verse eid="ACT 13:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 13:36"/>Wo to ɓei da Dauda nu ɓo m. Ai Dawuda ɓo la fi har wa ku bwo dna vingwo. <verse eid="ACT 13:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 13:37"/>Amma wo ɓei da zado nu ɓo. Owo nu n efi to ɓo mi kwa shi wo m. Wato Yesu nu.<verse eid="ACT 13:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 13:38"/>“Omi azaje gafara zhin lo n Yesu aba nu kawai ntu fye alaifi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 13:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 13:39"/>Zaho-zahoi wa gawo gaiciya aɓa ze wo oza gyi-gyi yi, enya n a Yahudiyi owa ta mi kwa zhin m. <verse eid="ACT 13:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 13:40"/>Oh fye zhin peceiye, mi to cei pma anabi ɓeda ye kwa nu n fya ba m. Ntu ge ɓa ci ge, <verse eid="ACT 13:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 13:41"/>Fye gye, fya bwi, ofye awyegbaciyi, gama mi zhin aɓo wowoyi lo n fya ba, fyei ta ga gaiciya lon, ko ozaho yi wu fye awyega.”<verse eid="ACT 13:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 13:42"/>Aza ɓa fa aduwa nyakun n wyi yi n gye a tu ɓa dole nu ge ɓa kun. Ɓa gna Bulus ge wo ɓei jezeɓe ntu ge ba wo Shekwoyi ɓeda, n satiwyi nkwo ɓe lo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 13:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 13:43"/>Aza n mwabegye n wyiyi ɓa vi Bulus laɓa n Barnabas yi. Bulus wa gna ɓa ge ɓa ga Yesu gaiciya ɓa vi wo. <verse eid="ACT 13:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 13:44"/>Shi Satiwyi ɓei si aza ku nu aduwa nyakun sosai ntu ge ɓa wo Bulus eda.<verse eid="ACT 13:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 13:45"/>Amma shi a Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓei gye aza lonu minagyi kwa gyiɓa. Ɓa kni Bulus akmi ɓa gna ɓa aɓeda nukwoyi.<verse eid="ACT 13:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 13:46"/>Bulus n Barnaba yi kuwa ɓa cige, “Kwo yi zhin dole nu ya ɓe fya ba a Yahudiyi n nabari manayi. Amma n saiye fye la yi ɓo na, fye ta ye yi ɓeda lo m. Ntu cenu yi lo abyedo aba nu.” <verse eid="ACT 13:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 13:47"/>Shekwoyi ɓei gna yi lonu nu, nge ʼmi ku fye ze buzangna n abyedo aba fya kun ɓaya n wyegma.<verse eid="ACT 13:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="ACT 13:48"/>Shi abyedo ɓei wo lo nu, ɓa dagma ɓai ci Shekwoyi ntu wo ɓeda ɓo; aza akni-kniyi ntu wye-wyeyi nyalo-nyalo nya ɓo, ɓa bei ku gaiciya ga.<verse eid="ACT 13:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="ACT 13:49"/>Ezhi yi vinya kwa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda laɓa.<verse eid="ACT 13:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="ACT 13:50"/>Amma a Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓa la gyikici ka. Ɓa zhin a nya Bulus ya n zhi yi. <verse eid="ACT 13:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="ACT 13:51"/>Amma Bulus n Barnaba yi, ba kun abutukun ya n ɓa pita. Ɓa kun ɓalo Ikoniya. <verse eid="ACT 13:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="ACT 13:52"/>A Yesu viyi kwaɓa bwa bugba bui-bui yi sosai, n nunuyi n Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi.<verse eid="ACT 13:52"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="ACT 14"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 14:1"/>N Ikoniya Bulus n Barnaba yi, ɓa lo aduwa nyakun ɓa zhin waʼazi sosai nya. Har aza n mwa ɓa ga gaiciya.<verse eid="ACT 14:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 14:2"/>Amma a Yahudiyi ɓa ku kala ɓa da aɓo nukwoyi tu Bulus tukwo, ɓedo n Barnaba yi. <verse eid="ACT 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 14:3"/>Amma Bulus n Barnaba yi, ɓa fi ɓai zhin waʼazi, Shekwoyi kuwa wa gaɓa ikwo har ɓa zhin aɓo wowoyi n mwa. <verse eid="ACT 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 14:4"/>Aza n zhiyi kwa ɓa gna jeya, aza ho ɓa ye ge a wu ɓa, aza ho kwa ge a gye ɓa sun-sun.<verse eid="ACT 14:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Zabmazhi La Kagna Bwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5-6" style="v" pubnumber="5,6" sid="ACT 14:5-6"/> Sanu Bulus n Barnaba yi, ɓo kpe ge a yelo a luɓa sosai, ɓa busi n zhi yi ɓa lo Listra, Darbe n azhi ɓiyi-ɓiyi n Likaonia kni. <verse eid="ACT 14:5-6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 14:7"/>Ɓa da nabari na zhi ye laɓa.<verse eid="ACT 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 14:8"/>N Listra ɓa gye zabmazhi ho, aɓo mawo n wu lonu nu. <verse eid="ACT 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 14:9"/>Wa wo Bulus woi zhin waʼazi, Bulus kwa wa kukpe ge zaye n gaiciya gayi lo. <verse eid="ACT 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 14:10"/>Bulus wa ciwo ge, “Omi zado lakala.” Wa laka wa ya zan-zan.<verse eid="ACT 14:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 14:11"/>Shi aza ɓo gye lonu ɓa fi aku. Ɓa cige, “A shekwoyi ku ɓe ya naiye.” <verse eid="ACT 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 14:12"/>Ɓa yi Barnaba ge Zafas, Bulus kwa ɓa yi wo ge Hamis. Oɓa shekwoyi aye nu lo nu. <verse eid="ACT 14:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 14:13"/>Har ɓa ɓe n nakwo yi ntuge ɓa gba shan.<verse eid="ACT 14:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14-15" style="v" pubnumber="14,15" sid="ACT 14:14-15"/> Amma shi Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓei gye lonu, ɓa ci ge, “Kai! Fye ku I fa mana! Ai yi zhin aza nu n gye fye. Yi cei pma fya fa shan gba nu fya vi Yesu n wa zhin anyi vinya nyi. <verse eid="ACT 14:14-15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 14:16"/>N sapai Shekwoyi ɓei fa ɓa zhin nya ɓa gye. <verse eid="ACT 14:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 14:17"/>Amma Shekwoyi to ɓei fa wo hin n tna seida m, wa ga nuwan n anya manayi yi.”<verse eid="ACT 14:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 14:18"/>Dudu lonu ɓa ɓo fa dai ca nu, ɓa ɓo ye ɓa gba shan dole.<verse eid="ACT 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 14:19"/>Dna anyipyei fyewyi kawai a Yahudiyi ɓa kun n Antakiya ɓedo Ikoniya yi, ɓa la wahala kaia, ɓa kni Bulus akuta har a gni wo gni-gni a biwo ya n zhi mi, ɓai gye ge wo la fi. <verse eid="ACT 14:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 14:20"/>Amma a Yesu viyi ɓo shekna wo, wa lakala wa lo zhi mi n labmi yi ɓa lo Darba.<verse eid="ACT 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 14:21"/>Shi a ɓei zhin waʼazi ɓo ɓa jeze ɓe Listra, Ikoniya ɓedo n Antakiya yi. <verse eid="ACT 14:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 14:22"/>Ɓai bma a Yesu viyi zhin n Yesu ɓedayi, ɓa gna ɓa ge ɓa to fa Yesu m. Kwo wahalai nu ɓe, ntuge zokwo nu bwa sun nu n ko ɓa lo n yi n she. <verse eid="ACT 14:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 14:23"/>Ɓa kni abyeda ga ɓa, ɓa zhin aduwa gaɓa n azumi yi sosai, ɓa fi ɓa n jesun n Shekwoyi akun.<verse eid="ACT 14:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 14:24"/>Ɓa je lo ɓa duya Bisidiya ɓa lo Pamfiliya. <verse eid="ACT 14:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 14:25"/>Ɓa zhin waʼazi n Perga ɓa lo Ataliya.<verse eid="ACT 14:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 14:26"/>Ɓa jeze lo Antakiya n eya nuwan nya yi, ɓa ɓei ya, zan-zan ya nu. A ɓo fi ɓa n Shekwoyi akun n ya nu n jesun.<verse eid="ACT 14:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 14:27"/>Sa n ɓa ɓo zhi, ɓa yi a Yesu viyi ɓa wu ɓa lafiya nya n ɓa ɓo zhin. Ɓa gna ɓa shi Shekwoyi ɓei gu zokwo ya ntuge abyedo ɓa kpe Yesu ye. <verse eid="ACT 14:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 14:28"/>Ɓa ku mwasa nkunsun na Yesu viyi n Antakiya.<verse eid="ACT 14:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="ACT 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Atukwoda Shaula Kmisunyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 15:1"/>Esa nu Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓei fi Antakiya, azado ho ɓa kun n Yahudiya ɓa ɓe. Ɓai wu a Yesu viyi ge ndei ɓa ye gni-gni tile ɓa zhin ɓa kaciya, ɓa vi Musa owa njesun. <verse eid="ACT 15:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 15:2"/>Amma Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓa dna ɓedayi wye n naza hoi ngnisun. Har kwa ze ikklisiya Antakiya nya, ɓa tnu Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓa lo a tukwoda aba n Urushelima ntu wu-wu deye pya ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 15:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 15:3"/>Ikklisiya ku ɓa gnami ɓa kuka ɓa lo Urushelima, ɓa diya n Finishiya n Samariya yi ntu ge ɓa gye a Yesu viyi, ɓa da ɓa ngye shi abye do ga gaiciya lo n bai gbo-gbo.<verse eid="ACT 15:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 15:4"/>Shi ɓa ɓo ku si Urushelima, ɓa lo abyeda aba. Bulus n Barnaba yi, ɓa wu abyeda ngye shi Shekwoyi lo tnu-tnu lo n ɓai n abyedo aba. <verse eid="ACT 15:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 15:5"/>Amma Afarasiyi ho da lo ge, “Abyedo vinya nɓa ga gaiciya nyi, tile a zhin ɓa kaciya, ɓa vi Musa owa njesun.”<verse eid="ACT 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 15:6"/>Abyeda ɓa yi aje zhi ɓa gundo, ntu ge ɓa zhin shaula tu n ɓeda ho tukwo.<verse eid="ACT 15:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 15:7"/>Shi a ɓo la yezhi, Bitrus wa laka gni wa daɓo, aza yi ge, Omi azaje, fye kpe lo ge Shekwoyi ɓo la mi kni, ntu ge ma da nabari manayi abyedo aba, ntu ge ɓahin ɓa ga gaiciya. <verse eid="ACT 15:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 15:8"/>Shekwoyi n wo kpe aza bugba nyi, wo ɓo la tabata n kwoi lo ge wo ye abyedo lo, ntu ge wo ɓo la Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ga ɓa, ngye shi wo ɓei ga yi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 15:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 15:9"/>Wo to n gna yi tu lo n eyi atan-tasin nɓa yi m ntu ge wo la ɓa bugba zhanya ntu ɓa gaiciya ga ɓo ngye yihin. <verse eid="ACT 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 15:10"/>Shekwoyi ɓei bwi aba nu, nfye ɓa dna wo n zokwo har fya tu abyedo a kaya n yihin kwo eyi azakwoyi to ɓei mi ya la n? <verse eid="ACT 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 15:11"/>Fye ta kpe lo ge gni-gni zhin kyauta nu, Dagayi Yesu Kristi nya, n aza ba n?<verse eid="ACT 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 15:12"/>Shi wo ɓo zo ɓeda, aza vinya ɓa ku ce pi, ɓa wo ngye shi Shekwoyi zhin aɓo wowoyi lo, n Bulus yi ɓedo n Barnabas yi n abyedo aba.<verse eid="ACT 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 15:13"/>Shi ɓa bo ku zo da Yakub wa daɓo n aza yi wa gna ge, “Omi azaje fye wo. <verse eid="ACT 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 15:14"/>Bitrus ku gna fye esa n Shekwoyi ɓo ya abyedo kni, ntu ge wa kni aza ɓa la owo ye tu. <verse eid="ACT 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 15:15"/>Anabi ɓei ku abyedo abuiye ɓo da, ko ku nu n yi esa. Wo nya nu anabi Amo ɓo da.<verse eid="ACT 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 15:16"/>“Dagayi ɓo gna ge, Avun deye, ‘Mia jezeɓe ntu ge ma ze omi alkawali a woi-woi n jesun n Dawuda yi.<verse eid="ACT 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 15:17"/>“ ‘Ntu ge abyedo ɓa kpe Dagayi ye, ɓa zan wo shi njesun.’ <verse eid="ACT 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 15:18"/>Dagayi kpe wo shiri vinya, Wo ɓa mi wa zhin aɓo ngye shi wo shiri nyi tunyi nkmisun-yi.<verse eid="ACT 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 15:19"/>“Ntu cenu enya ma gye kwonu nyi, yi to tu abyedo n ɓa ye abui nyi tile ge ɓa vi eyi a Yahudiyi awyidna m. <verse eid="ACT 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 15:20"/>Amma yi ɓa kage ɓa to gyi a shan abum, ɓa fa anagbai zhin, to ɓa gyi nya a to zun sha m. <verse eid="ACT 15:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 15:21"/>Ntu ge ala hana anya deye yi vinya, n a Yahudiyi aduwa nyakun n Satiwyi yi.”<verse eid="ACT 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 15:22"/>Ikklisiya atukwoda n Urushelima ɓa kni Yahuda n Sila yi, ntu ge ɓai gni lo n Bulus yi n Barnaba yi har Antakiya, ɓa lo ɓo da enya n na da.<verse eid="ACT 15:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 15:23"/>Wasika nyi n ɓa ɓei lo cei, Wasika ye gmi n yi aba nu, eyi atukwoda ɓedo ikklisiya yi n Urushelima. Kwoi ɓe fye a Yesu viyi aba n Antakiya, Suriya ɓedo n Silisiya yi, yi ɓi fye gna lo.<verse eid="ACT 15:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 15:24"/>Yi ku wo ge a Yesu viyi ho n la kunya ɓai gmi fye aɓo aje ge, tile fya shi Musa awyidna bwa, yi nu to tnu ɓa m. <verse eid="ACT 15:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 15:25"/>Yi ku shaula zhin ntu ce, Yi gna ge yi ɓa tnu n Yahuda, Sila, Bulus n Barnaba yi ɓa ɓe fya ba.<verse eid="ACT 15:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26-27" style="v" pubnumber="26,27" sid="ACT 15:26-27"/> Yahuda n Sila yi ɓa ku ɓa wye-wyei ga ntu Kristi ɓo, Ɓa ɓa gna fye ngbei shaula n ya zhin. <verse eid="ACT 15:26-27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 15:28"/>Kwa da Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓedo n yihin, to ya tu fye tile ge fye zhin aɓo ngye a Yahudiyi m. <verse eid="ACT 15:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 15:29"/>Amma fye ɓa fa a shan nya gyi ɓo, n na nya yi n na to zun shan, to fya zhin anagbayi m. N fya zhin lonu ko la kun sai wyihoi.<verse eid="ACT 15:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 15:30"/>Aza ngun anyi ye ɓa kuka ɓa lo Antakiya, shi ɓa ɓo si ɓa ye a Yesu viyi zhi ɓa ga ɓa wasika. <verse eid="ACT 15:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 15:31"/>A Yesu viyi vinya ɓa dagma ɓai ci Shekwoyi, ntu ge wasika yi ɓei mi ɓa bugba gni.<verse eid="ACT 15:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 15:32"/>Sila n Yahuda yi, ɓa zhin waʼazi zhin-yi nu, ɓa zhin waʼazi ɓai mi a Yesu viyi gaiciya ga gni. <verse eid="ACT 15:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 15:33"/>Ɓa ɓo ku anyipyei bwa fyewyi n ɓai, ɓa kpe jeze lo Urushelima, ɓa lo ngna ɓi yi n atukwoda aba n Urushelima. <verse eid="ACT 15:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 15:34"/>Bulus n Barnaba yi, ɓa ku che fi n Antakiya anyipyei fyewyi. <verse eid="ACT 15:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 15:35"/>Ɓa ɓei bma amalami zhin ɓo, ɓahin ɓai zhin waʼazi, ɓai wu aza Shekwoyi ɓeda.<verse eid="ACT 15:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Ajegna N Barnaba Yi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 15:36"/>N wyihoi Bulus wa gna Barnaba ge, “Yi lo njesun yi gye aza n ɓa ɓo ga gaiciya nyi. Azhi gbo-gbo ya gye shi ɓa mwalo.” <verse eid="ACT 15:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 15:37"/>Barnaba wa ye, ama wa ye ge wa la Markus ɓa gni lo. <verse eid="ACT 15:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 15:38"/>Amma Bulus to ɓo ye ge, Yohanna Markus wa gnilo n ɓai m, ntu ge wo ɓo la jeze n Pamfiliya. <verse eid="ACT 15:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 15:39"/>Deye ɓo la Bulus n Barnabayi dna aɓona, n mwa har ɓa gnaje. Zaho-zaho wa lo wo nya nwo bwai. Barnabas wala Yohanna Markus ɓa lo Saipiris. <verse eid="ACT 15:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 15:40"/>Bulus wa kni Sila wa gni tnu-tnu zhin n woi. <verse eid="ACT 15:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 15:41"/>Ɓa lo Suriya n Silisiya yi ɓai mi ikklisiya zhi nbwai.<verse eid="ACT 15:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="ACT 16"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 16:1"/>Bulus n Sila yi ɓa lo Darbe, n sayi ɓa lo Listra aba nu ɓa ɓo gye Timatawus. Timatawus n wo aza mayi ɓa ɓei zhin a Yesu viyi nu! Owo ʼya ɓo zhin Yahudiyi nu amma owo dada ɓo zhin Heleniyi nu. <verse eid="ACT 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 16:2"/>Timatawus ɓo zhin oza manayi nu, har ai kpe wo ye n Listra ɓedo n Ikoniya yi ntu wo hali manayi ɓo. Wo ɓo n seida manayi yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 16:3"/>Ntu wo seida Yesu viyi manayi ɓo, Bulus ɓo gna wo ge wo gni lo n ɓai. Ntu ge to Ayahudiyi ɓa zhi gbo n woyi m, Bulus wa ku wo zhin kaciya gama ozaho-zahoi ɓei kpe ge owo dada ɓo zhin Heleniyi nu. <verse eid="ACT 16:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 16:4"/>Ɓa zan azhi yakwo, ɓai gna a Yesu viyi shaula n na ɓo zhin ntu abyedo ɓo, n Urushelima nyi. <verse eid="ACT 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 16:5"/>Ntu deye ɓo, ikklisiya kwa mwa fyegyi-fyegyi dna n gaiciya n begye yi njesun.<verse eid="ACT 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 16:6"/>Ɓa zan laɓa fi n Firijiya ʼkni, ɓedo n Galatiya yi. Amma Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓo la hana n ɓai, to ɓa zhin waʼazi n Asiya n sayi yi m. <verse eid="ACT 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 16:7"/>Sbi ɓa ɓo ku si Misiya ɓa zhin shaula ɓa lo Bitiniya, amma Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa hana n ɓai. <verse eid="ACT 16:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 16:8"/>Cenu ɓo zhin ɓa zan fi n Misiya ʼkni, har ɓa ɓe Turas.<verse eid="ACT 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Ɓewyegye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 16:9"/>N Turas Bulus wa nu ena n sukwoyi. Wa gye Makidoniya yi za woi gna ge, “Piya ɓe n ya ha bma yi zhin.” <verse eid="ACT 16:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 16:10"/>Ɓa zhin shaula ɓa lo Makidoniya ntu ge wo ɓo la tabata Ige Shekwoyi nu tnu n ɓai, ɓo zhin waʼazi nabari manayi nya n bwai.<verse eid="ACT 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 16:11"/>Ya kun n Turowas ya lo eya ya lo Samatiras. Ya si Niyapolis n nyipyei bayi yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 16:12"/>Ya duya ya lo Filibi, ko ɓo zhin galu nu a Roma yi nya, Ezhi dnagmayi nu dna n Makidoniya, ya ku fi ɓo anyipyei fyewyi.<verse eid="ACT 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 16:13"/>N Satiwyi ya lo ednagbe aba nu aza zhin ɓa yezhi ɓa zhin aduwa. Na bayi ya wu anyikwoza Shekwoyi ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 16:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 16:14"/>Nyikwoza gmanyi a yi wo Lidiya, wo gmi n Tiyatera wo ɓo zhin bwazeyi nu, woi kun aje nakwoyi nu, wa ɓe ntuge wa ci Shekwoyi wa gu wo bugba ya, wa ye abui, ntu waʼazi ɓo n Bulus ɓo zhin nyi. <verse eid="ACT 16:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 16:15"/>Ya zhin wo baptizma n na zayi nwo puwa vinya, wa gyi yi wye ge yi shin fi n wo puwa wa ci ge, “Ngye fye ku ye ge, mi zhin oza gaiciya danu n Dagayi aba, fye ɓe fya shin fi n mi puwa”. Ya ku ye ya lo wo puwa.<verse eid="ACT 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 16:16"/>N wyihoi, yi lo aduwa zhin n dnagbe, ya gye ɓinyikwoyi ho nu aljanu yi. Wo ɓei zhin woi da ɓo nɓa ɓa zhin abye, har deye kwoi ɓe owo adagayi n agyiwye yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 16:17"/>Wa vi yi ɓe woi ɓewyi, “aza deye Shekwoyi abara nu, ɓa ɓe ntu ge ɓa gna fye, shi aba zhin fye alaifi gafara.”<verse eid="ACT 16:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 16:18"/>Wo ɓo zhin lonu cici, har anyipyei fyewyi. Bulus wa gyi minagyi wa gnakni aljanu wa gna, “dna Yesu Kristi ye mi ye fya kun nwo.” Nsai-sayi yi aljenu ɓa kun.<verse eid="ACT 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 16:19"/>Amma owo a dagayi yi ɓa gyi minagyi n Bulus yi, ntu ge wo la agyiwye zokwo wun ɓaya, ɓa wan Bulus n Sila ɓa lo n ɓai na wadai aba n gnikwo (ntu ge awadayi ɓei zhi ɓo nu).<verse eid="ACT 16:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 16:20"/>Ɓa da ge a Yahudiyi ye n ɓa zhi nyi, ɓa wun yi zhi ya lo. <verse eid="ACT 16:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 16:21"/>Ɓai gna aza ge ɓa to zhin a Romayi awyidna vi m.<verse eid="ACT 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Wan-wan Fi N Kurkuku</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 16:22"/>Aza gyi minagyi, awadayi ɓa gna za ge ɓa lu Bulus n Sila yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 16:23"/>Shi ɓa ɓo ku ɓa lu dai-dai, ɓa ku ɓa gu fi n kurkuku, a gna kurkuku guyi ge wo to ye ge ɓa bu si m.<verse eid="ACT 16:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 16:24"/>Kurkuku guyi wa ku ɓa, wa ku ɓa gufi n mi mi, wa ku ɓa gyi n apita.<verse eid="ACT 16:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 16:25"/>N sukwo sadu yi Bulus n Sila yi ɓa ya anyi kwo ga Dagayi, akurkuku da aje ɓa wo ɓai ko anyi. <verse eid="ACT 16:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 16:26"/>Sa fyewyi ekni kwa ya ashan-shan, kurkuku kwa shan-shan abokunmi ɓa guya agma ɓa kunya nɓa abwa duk na pita yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 16:27"/>Shi kurkuku guyi ɓo kun agyewyi wa gye kurkuku abokunmi la guya, wa gye ngye aza wan-wan yi la busi, wa la ebe yakwo ntu ge wa wu wohin. <verse eid="ACT 16:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 16:28"/>Amma Bulus wa sawyi, “To wu hohin, gye yi fi lo ya vinya.”<verse eid="ACT 16:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 16:29"/>Woi gni wo vin ntu edna ɓo, wa gna ge ɓe n na yi. Wa lo ɓe kurkuku wa chakwo-kwo shi n Bulus abye n Sila yi. <verse eid="ACT 16:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 16:30"/>Wa kun ɓa ɓe cei wa nya ɓa ge, amalemi nɓa zhin wuna ma pwoo a?<verse eid="ACT 16:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 16:31"/>Ɓagna wo ge, “Ga Yesu Kristi gaiciya ho ɓa pwo n aza yi n ho puwa vinya.”<verse eid="ACT 16:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 16:32"/>Ɓa gna wo nabari manayi ɓedo azayi n wo puwa vinya. <verse eid="ACT 16:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 16:33"/>N sukwoyi yi wa zhan ɓa a ciya, owohin n wa ʼzayi vinya nwo puwa a ku ɓa zhin baptizma. <verse eid="ACT 16:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 16:34"/>Wa ku ɓa wa lo ɓai nwo puwa wa ga ɓa nya gyi. Owo puwa vinya kwa dagma, ntu ge ɓa ku ze a Yesu viyi. <verse eid="ACT 16:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 16:35"/>N labmiyi awadayi ɓa tnu n dan-sanda yi ge wo gna kurkuku guyi ge a Bulus ɓa lo. <verse eid="ACT 16:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 16:36"/>Kurkuku guyi wa gna Bulus n Sila yi ge ɓa lo.<verse eid="ACT 16:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 16:37"/>Amma Bulus wa gna “awo, ɓa ku yi lu n aza awye ɓai kuyi fi n kurkuku n tna wada, eyi n yi zhin Romayi, n sayi ɓa ye ya lo fiya kpe-kpe! Ɓa ɓe n ɓahin ɓa loyi ya.”<verse eid="ACT 16:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 16:38"/>Dan-sanda wa jeze lo wa gna awadayi, shi ɓa ɓo wo ge Bulus n Sila yi zhin a Romayi nu ɓa wo dna.<verse eid="ACT 16:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 16:39"/>Ɓa ɓe kurkuku ɓa gyi ɓa wye ge, ɓa la kun nzhi hi ɓa lo ɓa nya.<verse eid="ACT 16:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 16:40"/>Bulus n Sila yi ɓa kun n kurkuku, ɓa lo Lidiya puwa, ɓa gye a Yesu viyi nfi ɓo, ɓa mi ɓa bugba zhi, ɓa kpe kala ku ɓa lo ɓa nya.<verse eid="ACT 16:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="ACT 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Bulus La Lo Azhingye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 17:1"/>Avun ɓa duya n Amfipoli ɓedo Apoloniya yi ɓa lo Tasalunaika. A Yahudiyi aduwa nyakun ɓei gni ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 17:2"/>Bulus wa lo aduwa nyakun wa zhin waʼazi wo ɓo da Shekwoyi ɓeda, har Asati ngun ata n vi do lo. <verse eid="ACT 17:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 17:3"/>Woi ga bayani anabci n na ɓei zhin tu Yesu wahala ɓo, ɓedo nwo kala layi n vingwo, wa wu shi Yesu nu zhin Kristi. <verse eid="ACT 17:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 17:4"/>A Yahudiyi ho ɓa ku gaiciya ga ge, Yesu nu zhin Kristi. A Helleniyi n mwabegye anugbayi na nyikwoza yi ɓa ku yabui ɓa ze a Yesu viyi. N mwa begye nɓa mi ɓa ɓo zhin aza dnagmayi nu n Tasalunaika.<verse eid="ACT 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 17:5"/>Amma a Yahudiyi, n ɓa to ɓei ye ɓa ga Kristi gaiciya nyi m, ɓa zhin aza ɓa la wahala kala. Ɓa lo Jason puwa ɓo kun a Bulus n Sila yi ɓei cei ɓa lo n ɓai n azhi tukwoda aba, a ga ɓa tata.<verse eid="ACT 17:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 17:6"/>Amma to ɓa gye ɓa fi ɓom, ɓa wan Jason ɓa gni wo ɓe cei ɓedo nna Yesu viyi ho yi, ɓa ce akata fi ɓa nna iko da abye ɓa gna ɓa nu la wahala ka dna n zhi, n gye Bulus n Sila yi. <verse eid="ACT 17:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 17:7"/>Ɓa ce akata fi Json ge, wo ku a Bulus so fi n wo puwa. Har ma ge Bulus n Sila yi, ɓedo n Jason yi, ɓa da lo ge Yesu nu zhin esu do, gbo n Kaisar yi.<verse eid="ACT 17:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 17:8"/>Shi a iko da ɓo wo a ɓe deye tu Bulus tukwao, ɓedo n Sila yi, har n Jason yi ɓa ku je-je. <verse eid="ACT 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 17:9"/>A iko da ɓa Jason ya ɓedo na Yesu viyi, ai la ɓa gwo bwashi.<verse eid="ACT 17:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 17:10"/>N sukwoyi a Yesu viyi, ɓa gna a Bulus n Sila yi ge, ɓa lo Beriya. She ɓa ɓo si bwai ɓa lo a Yahudiyi aduwa nyakun. <verse eid="ACT 17:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 17:11"/>Aza n Beriya ɓei n yeyei du a Tasalunaikayi. Ɓa gwo Shekwoyi ɓeda na gmadai, ɓai ba fyegyi-fyegyi dna n Shekwoyi ɓeda, ntu ge ɓa kpe ge nya n Bulus da nyi kwo zhin gaiciya nu. <verse eid="ACT 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 17:12"/>Ntu deye ɓo, aza n mwa begye a Helleniyi anugbayi na nyikwozayi, ɓa ku gaiciya ga, ɓa ku ze a Yesu viyi.<verse eid="ACT 17:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 17:13"/>Amma shi a Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓo wo ge, a Bulus ku waʼazi Shekwoyi ɓeda nya da, ɓa gyi minagyi, ɓa la wahala ka dna n zhi. <verse eid="ACT 17:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 17:14"/>A Yesu viyi ɓa gna Bulus ge wo lo ela gbe, amma Sila n Timatawus yi, ɓa ku ce fi n Beriya. <verse eid="ACT 17:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 17:15"/>Aza nɓa ɓei da Bulus apye nyi, ɓa gni lo n woi har Atina. Bulus wa tnu ga Sila n Timatawus yi ge ɓa ɓe wolo-wolo. Aberiya yi n ɓa ɓei gni lo n Bulus yi nyi, ɓa nu ɓo jeze lo a Timatawus n tnu-tnu yi.<verse eid="ACT 17:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 17:16"/>Kafin Sila n Timatawus yi ɓa lo, Bulus ɓo ku ashan gyewye n Atina; wa ku kpe ge ɓa ta kpe Shekwoyi Gaiciya nya ye lo m. <verse eid="ACT 17:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 17:17"/>Walo aduwa nyakun, ntu ge wa zhin shaula n a Yahudiyi, ɓedo abyedo yi n ɓa ku gaiciya ga nyi, wo ɓei zhin waʼazi cici n gnikwo.<verse eid="ACT 17:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Nna Beyekpeyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 17:18"/>Wa gye aɓeyekpeyi ho, shi wo ɓo gna ɓa Yesu efi ɓo, nwo kala la yi, ɓa ma wo san, ɓa kpe wo agye, ɓa ci wo wyegba ɓa gna ge, “Wo nuna nu kwo ge wa ɓe n kunnu woi-woi nu.”<verse eid="ACT 17:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 17:19"/>Ɓa la Bulus ɓa lo woi, aba a yi ge Arasa, ɓa gna, “Ɓe ha gnayi ho kunu woi-woi ɓo.” <verse eid="ACT 17:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 17:20"/>Ho da anya ɓo lo n yi ta kpe ɓa yelo m, yi ye ya kpe ɓa ye. <verse eid="ACT 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 17:21"/>Atina yi ɓedo azhiɓeyi zhin ɓa ye ntuge ɓa wo aɓo woi-woi.<verse eid="ACT 17:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 17:22"/>Bulus wa laka tu abaho ngye epe, wa da ɓo n ɓai wa gna, “Ofye Atinayi mi ku gye fye zhin a knunu bwashiyi nu.<verse eid="ACT 17:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 17:23"/>“Ntu ge ma zan, mi gye fye bagadi mi gni, n rubutu yi kakpe ge ‘Shekwoyi n ata kpe woye m. Emihin mi da wo nu ɓeda,’ n fye ga wo mwa-mwa dna n wyegma nyi.<verse eid="ACT 17:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 17:24"/>“Owo nu na zhin anyi, anya yi vinya a ɓa fi n ɓa nyi, wo ta dna aduwa nyakun nami na bwai m, ntu ge eshe n ʼkniyi wo nu zhin ɓa Dagayi. <verse eid="ACT 17:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 17:25"/>Oza ta mi wa biya n wo bukata yi m, ntu ge wo to anya kmayim. Wonu ga nyaho-nyahoi wye-wyei n sun yi, woi ga zaho-zahoi wo bukata. <verse eid="ACT 17:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 17:26"/>Wo na zhin aza vinya tunyi n Adamu sa, wa gna abye ya zhin anyi tunyi kmisunyi, wo nu kpe abye ye n ɓa ɓa kuka n begyi, esa yi nɓa ɓa duya. Wonu na zhi ɓa n ɓa zhiba.<verse eid="ACT 17:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 17:27"/>“Owo ɓemwi nu ɓei nyi ntu ge, abye ye vinya ɓa zanwo shin, wo ye ntuge ya ze owo nya, wo lo vivi n yi. <verse eid="ACT 17:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 17:28"/>Nwo mi nu yi bwa wye-wyei yi zan. Ngye shi fye zhin fya da dna fye anyi ɓesisi ge ‘Yi zhin Shekwoyi aɓi nu.’ <verse eid="ACT 17:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 17:29"/>Ndei deye gaiciya nu, kwo to bmiya ya gye Shekwoyi ngye ashan nu, n ʼza zhin n zinariyi ko azurfa ko kuta m. <verse eid="ACT 17:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 17:30"/>Esa n kwa duya nyi aza ɓei gba a shan, Shekwoyi wa zhin hankuri nɓai. Amma nsaiye Shekwoyi ye aza vinya ɓa fa ashan gba, ɓa ga wo nu mwa-mwa. <verse eid="ACT 17:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 17:31"/>Ntu ge wo nyipyei shi lo, n wo ɓei da anyi wa cei dna ɓefyece n oza aba n wo ɓei la wo ka n vingwo nyi, wo nu ɓo da aza wa.”<verse eid="ACT 17:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 17:32"/>Shi Bulus ɓo da afifiyi kala ku ɓo, aza ho ɓa ma san. Amma azaho ɓa gna yi ye cei pma lo ya wo n sado. <verse eid="ACT 17:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 17:33"/>Bulus ɓeda kmaknayi nu n ɓai wa lo wo nya. <verse eid="ACT 17:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 17:34"/>Azaho ɓa ku gaiciya ga. Diyonisisi shaula zhinyi n Atina ɓedo n nyikwoza hoi ai yi wo ge Damaris ɓa ku ye abui, n na azajei.<verse eid="ACT 17:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="ACT 18"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 18:1"/>Bulus wa fa Atina wa lo Korinti. <verse eid="ACT 18:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 18:2"/>N Korinti wagye Akila n wo nyikwoyi Biriskila, ɓa ɓo ku sase n Italiya amma n sayi ɓai fi Korinti nu. A ɓo ma Akila n Pontus nu. Ɓa ɓo fa Italiya ntuge Kaisar Klaudi ɓei la Ayahudiyi nya ya n ɓa ɓo fi n Roma nyi. <verse eid="ACT 18:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 18:3"/>Bulus wa knu tnu-tnu zhin n ɓai, ntu ge oɓa tnu-tnu ɓei zhin gmanyi nu watau alubui zhinyi.<verse eid="ACT 18:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Nɓa Lo Abyedo Aba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 18:4"/>Bulus ɓei zhin wa lo aduwa nyakun n satiwyi doho-doho yi, woi wu a Yahudiyi ɓedo n a Helleniyi ge Yesu nu zhin Kristi. <verse eid="ACT 18:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 18:5"/>Timatawus n Sila yi ɓa fa Makidoniya ɓa ɓe da Bulus n Korinti. Shi ɓa ɓo ku ɓe da wo, Bulus wa gyi abye n waʼazi yi, woi wu a Yahudiyi Yesu nu zhin Kristi. <verse eid="ACT 18:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 18:6"/>Amma a Yahudiyi ɓa na waɓo, wohin ce wa kun wo aje butukun ya wa gna, ofye ami ɓa tu lo nfye, amma mi kni-kniyi lo, n sayi nɓa zhin waʼazi na byedo aba nu.<verse eid="ACT 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 18:7"/>Avun wa lo wa shin dna n Titus puwa. Wo ɓei zhin ebye do nu, amma wo ɓo zhin woi ye Shekwoyi, woi ga wo mwa-mwa. Owo puwa ɓei wu vivi n aduwa nyakun yi. <verse eid="ACT 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 18:8"/>Krispas nu ɓei zhin aduwa nyakun Itukwoda. Owo puwa vinya ɓa ku vi Yesu, aku ɓa zhin baptizma ɓedo nazadohoi.<verse eid="ACT 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 18:9"/>Shekwoyi wa daɓo n Bulus yi dna n ena, wa gna wo ge, “To wo dna kwo ha busi m, daɓo, to ce pi m.” <verse eid="ACT 18:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 18:10"/>Ntu ge mi gnisun lo n hoi, ozaho ta zhin ho nyaho m, mi azayi lo dna n ezhi deye n mwa. <verse eid="ACT 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 18:11"/>Elonu Bulus wa gyi abye, woi wu Shekwoyi ɓeda har eye gmanyi n tokun yi.<verse eid="ACT 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 18:12"/>Amma esa n Galiyo ɓo gyi gwamna dna Akaya, a Yahudiyi ɓa la gyikici ka n Bulus yi, ɓa zhin wo kala n gwamna aba. <verse eid="ACT 18:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 18:13"/>Ɓa gna ge, Bulus gna aza ge, ɓa ga Shekwoyi mwa-mwa n azokwoyi n ɓa zhin gaba n Romayi awyidna yi. <verse eid="ACT 18:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 18:14"/>Bulus woi ye wa daɓo, amma Galiyo wa gna akala da ge, oza deye ɓo gna wo ku laifi zhin, mo kna fye ɓeda Itnubua. <verse eid="ACT 18:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 18:15"/>Amma shi ko zhin adini ɓo nu nyi, fye da n fyehin yi, omi anuwan to dna lon. <verse eid="ACT 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 18:16"/>Wa ɓa kunya j n kotu.<verse eid="ACT 18:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 18:17"/>Sai a Yahudiyi ɓa wan Sostina, ɓa lu wo shi bmi wo nu ɓei zhin tukwoda woi-woyi, amma Galiyo to wa gye wa nuwan.<verse eid="ACT 18:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 18:18"/>Shi aɓo ɓo ku zo, Bulus wa dna ɓo anyipyei n mwa begye, wa kpe piya lo Suriya ɓedo n Biriskila n Akila yi. Bulus wa tukwo wun n Kankiriya ntu ge wo ɓo la nyasi si. A Yahudiyi knunu nu ɓa zhin lo nu. <verse eid="ACT 18:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 18:19"/>Shi yi ɓei si aya lo ɓa n Afisusu wa fa yi fi n eya wa lo aduwa nyakun wa daɓo n a Yahudiyi n ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 18:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 18:20"/>Ɓa gna wo ge wo la gni nɓai, amma esa to ɓei nyi m.<verse eid="ACT 18:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 18:21"/>Wa gna dole ma lo mi sun dna Urushelima. Amma wa zhin ɓa alkawali ge, wo ɓa je ɓe ndei Shekwoyi waye, ya lo yi nya.<verse eid="ACT 18:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 18:22"/>Ya kpe zhi n jesun aya lo ɓa n Kaisariya, Wa lo wa ɓi ikklisiya gna ya kpe duya lo Antakiya. <verse eid="ACT 18:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 18:23"/>Ya ku sun sa fi ɓo, avun wa laka wa lo Turki njesun, Wa duya n Galatiya ɓedo n Firijiya yi, Wa zhin ziyara woi bma a Kristi yi zhin, ɓa mwa dna n Dagayi.<verse eid="ACT 18:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 18:24"/>N sayi Apollos ɓei dna n Afisus, wo ɓei zhin malami dnagmayi nu Shekwoyi ɓeda nya, Wo ɓei gmi n Alekzandariya n Masar kni nu. <verse eid="ACT 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 18:25"/>N Masar ozado ho ɓo ku Nabari manayi gna wo ntu Yohanna Baptisma zhin yi ɓo, n wo wu-wu yi tu Yesu tukwo, wo to ɓei n Shekwoyi yekpe yi n du deye m. <verse eid="ACT 18:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 18:26"/>Wa ya waʼazi zhin n kala yi, n iko yi n mwa dna na duwa nyakun wa gna ge, Kristi ɓe lo fye zhin shiri fya gwo wo. Briskilia n Akila yi ɓai fi ɓai wo, shi wo ɓei ku zo ɓa yi wo, ɓa zhin wo bayani ntu Yesu ɓo. Watau wo la ɓe, woi la fi, woi la laka n vingwo, woi la gun lo eshe, woi jeze ɓelo njesun. <verse eid="ACT 18:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 18:27"/>Apollos wa ye ge wa lo Akaya, a Kristi yi ɓa mi wo gni ge wo lo. ʼBa ka a Kristi yi ge a gwo wo n agmadayi shi wo ɓo si ɓo. Shekwoyi wa zhin apma n woi, wa mi ikklisiya gni. <verse eid="ACT 18:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 18:28"/>Nɓo wa wu a Yahudiyi dna n Shekwoyi ɓeda ge, Yesu nu zhin Kristi n tna shaka.<verse eid="ACT 18:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="ACT 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Agaiciyagayi Nla Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi Gwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 19:1"/>Esa nu Apollos ɓo dna cei n Korinti Bulus wa duya n Turki wa lo Afisus wa sun abara hoi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 19:2"/>Wa nya ɓa ge? “Fye ɓo la Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi gwo esa nu fye ɓei ga gaiciya nyi?” Ɓa gna ge, “Awo.” Yi ta kpe Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ɓo ye lon har ge ya gwo Wo m.<verse eid="ACT 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 19:3"/>Wa nya ɓa ge, “Fye ɓo ga kniyi nu gaiciya har a zhin fye batisma?” Ɓa gna ge, “anya n Yohanna baptisma zhinyi ɓo wu nyi.”<verse eid="ACT 19:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 19:4"/>Bulus wa gna ɓa ge, Yohanna baptisma ɓei zhin nya nu nkwo wu abui ye n laifi. Aza na ɓei zhin ɓa baptisma nyi aɓo zhin ɓa ntu ge ɓa vi Yesu nu. Aye aza vinya ɓa fa laifi ɓa zan Shekwoyi shin.<verse eid="ACT 19:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 19:5"/>Avun a zhin ɓa batisma dna Yesu Kristi ye. <verse eid="ACT 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 19:6"/>Bulus wa kpe ɓa abwa na tukwo Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa shinkpe nɓa, Nsai-sayi ɓa daɓo anyitalayi ɓai zhin anabci. <verse eid="ACT 19:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 19:7"/>Abara yi ɓei nyi awocei-aba nu.<verse eid="ACT 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 19:8"/>Avun deye Bulus wa lo aduwa Inyakun cici, woi zhin waʼazi n ikoyi wo ɓei zhin lo nu n satiwyi doho-dohoi har apya ngun-ata. Woi wu ge Yesu nu zhin Kristi. <verse eid="ACT 19:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 19:9"/>Amma aza ho ɓa naɓo ɓai da ɓeda nukwoyi tu Yesus tukwo. Wa fa ɓa to wa jeɓa waʼazi zhi m, ama wa ye a Kristi yi zhin n Tiranus makaranta wa zhin a waʼazi fyegyi-fyegyi. <verse eid="ACT 19:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 19:10"/>Wo ɓei zhin waʼazi ɓo aye ngun-aba, har aza vinya n Turki n Asiya yi ɓa wo Shekwoyi ɓeda, a Yahudiyi ɓedo, a Helleniyi yi. <verse eid="ACT 19:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 19:11"/>Shekwoyi wa ga Bulus iko wa zhin aɓo wo-woyi n ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 19:12"/>Har owo amisa wunya je, sa nu a ya kwo kpe nyasanyi wa gwo kagna. Aljanu ɓai kun na za.<verse eid="ACT 19:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 19:13"/>Amma a Yahudiyi a zan-zan yi ho, n ɓa zan azhi gbo-gbo ɓai kun aljanu ya, ɓa zhin tunani ge ɓa kun aljanu ya dna Yesu eye. Ɓa gna, “Ma gna fye dna Yesu eye n Bulus zhin wo waʼazi nyi fye kun.” <verse eid="ACT 19:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 19:14"/>Aza deye ɓei zhin Sisiva aɓi nu ngun-tnaba wohin ɓei zhin a Yahudiyi prist nu. <verse eid="ACT 19:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 19:15"/>Shi ɓa ɓei tumwi lonu, aljanu da wa gna, mi kpe Yesu yelo, n Bulus yi, amma nyikanu n fyei ya? <verse eid="ACT 19:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 19:16"/>Aljanu da wa she pui ɓa ngun-aba wa lu ɓa, ɓa sakun n nyakun ntna wando fi yi n ɓahin wuwuyi.<verse eid="ACT 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 19:17"/>Nabari ye kwa gnami fi Afisus vinya, a Yahudiyi na Helleniyi ɓawo, aza ɓa wo edna n mwa ɓa la Yesu eye tu. <verse eid="ACT 19:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 19:18"/>Aza n ɓa ɓei ga gaiciya nyi ɓa ɓe, ɓai da ɓa laifi duk na zoku shei.<verse eid="ACT 19:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 19:19"/>Ɓa ɓe nɓa azoku zhe nya yi, na laya yi, ɓa kpe ɓa ena. Atakarda azoku nya nɓa ɓo kpe na nyi oɓa gyewye ɓei ɓa sun ngye ₦3,000. <verse eid="ACT 19:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 19:20"/>Deye ɓo wu ge ɓa la Shekwoyi ɓedo gwo n gaiciya yi dna.<verse eid="ACT 19:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Aɓona-kpaje N Afisus</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 19:21"/>Avun Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa wu Bulus ge, wo lo Akaya kafin wo lo Urushelima, wa gna dole ma lo Roma. <verse eid="ACT 19:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 19:22"/>Amma wa tnu Timatawus ɓedo Arastis na bye ɓa lo Akaya, amma wohin wa ce dna n Turki. Aza n wo ɓo tnu nyi ɓa ɓei zhin owo abmazhin yi nu.<verse eid="ACT 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 19:23"/>N sayi wahala kwa laka na Kristi yi n Afisus. <verse eid="ACT 19:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 19:24"/>Pyada ho ai yi wo Dimitiriyus wo nu ɓei la wahala ka, wa gna apyada je ge ɓa zhin ashan azurfa nya a Helleniyi shekwoyi Diyana nya. <verse eid="ACT 19:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 19:25"/>Wa yi apyada je wa gna, tnu-tnu nkwo nyi, yi bwa nyagyi nkwonu n agyiwyei.<verse eid="ACT 19:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 19:26"/>N sayi fye kpe lo ge Bulus ku aza bugba wan, har eyi ashan n yi zhin nyi, ato gye ɓalo ngye a shekwoyi nu m, ntu lonu eyi abwaze, ta gyi abye m, kwoi ta to yi nu bwa ya gmanyi m, amma du akni do yi. <verse eid="ACT 19:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 19:27"/>N yi to zhin nyaho n za ye yin, yi ta bwi agyiwye nu nuwan gmanyin, amma du n yi Diyana yi, okwo nu aza ga kwo mwa-mwa nyi vinya, anyi ɓa ku zamwi, fye ɓa ye lo nu?<verse eid="ACT 19:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 19:28"/>Shi ɓa ɓei wo lonu oɓa minagyi kwa laka, n sai-sayi ɓa ya aku fi ɓa gna, “Diyana Afisus nya zhin nya Dnagmayi nu.” <verse eid="ACT 19:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 19:29"/>Nsai-sayi yi aza yezhi ezhi kwa totu n sunu yi. Ɓa wan Gayus ɓedo Aristakus yi ɓa lo ɓai n kwotu, nge ada ɓa wa. Ɓa gna aza deye zhin, Bulus atnu-tnu kun-zhin-yi nu. <verse eid="ACT 19:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 19:30"/>Bulus ɓo ye wa lo wo gye ɓa, amma a Kristi yi n Afisus to ɓa yem. <verse eid="ACT 19:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 19:31"/>A Romayi dan sanda tukwoda ɓa gna Bulus ge wo to lo m, kada ɓa wu wo. A dan-sanda tukwoda ye ɓei zhin Bulus anugun-do nu.<verse eid="ACT 19:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 19:32"/>Aza ɓai ɓowyi fi n kwotu, ngye anyasin yi, aɓo ɓa ku gmaje har azaho ma to ɓa kpe dalili nkwo zhin ɓa lo ɓo m.<verse eid="ACT 19:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 19:33"/>A Yahudiyi ɓa wan Alikzanda ɓa gni wo lo cei na bye. Wa ku abwa wu n she woi ye wa da ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 19:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 19:34"/>Amma shi aza ɓei kpe ge wo zhin Yahudiyayi zanu ɓa gna aku fi-fi har awa n gun aba. Ɓai ci ge, “Diyana Afisus nya, ko zhin nya dnagmayi nu.”<verse eid="ACT 19:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 19:35"/>Ezhi sakatare wa ɓe wa gna aza ge, “fye ku ce pi, fye kpe lo ge Afisus nu zhin adini Diyana nya tukwo, okwo nu nkwo degbe ɓei kaya ɓe da yi n she, <verse eid="ACT 19:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 19:36"/>Mi gyi fye wye shi fye ku kpe ge ko nu zhin gaiciya n Afisus. Afisus nu zhin adini tukwo njesun ntu diye ɓo fye to gyi minagyi nɓei na da nkwo tukwo m, fye to zhin nyaho dna n pye-pye m. <verse eid="ACT 19:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 19:37"/>Gaiciya nu oza n fya ɓe cei nyi, wo to wyi Diyana nyahom, woi to ka kwo mwa-mwa ya m, nyaho to lo nkwo ka Diyana mwa-mwa ya m, ko cewyi.<verse eid="ACT 19:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 19:38"/>“Ndei Dimitiriyus nɓo yi lo n ɓai, sai wa ɓe n kala yi n kwotu, alkali ɓa zo ɓa ɓeda vinya. Amma kwo bmiya fya vi owa. <verse eid="ACT 19:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 19:39"/>Njesun nfye aɓo do yi lo n ɓai aɓa mi a da fi n esu bokun. <verse eid="ACT 19:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 19:40"/>Yi wo dna lo ntu ge a Romayi Gmamnati ɓa yi yi ɓa nya yi dalili wahal a nya. Deye to kunce lo, mi ta mi ma ga ɓa dalili m.”<verse eid="ACT 19:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 19:41"/>Shi wo ɓo zo da lonu, wa ku aza gnami vinya.<verse eid="ACT 19:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="ACT 20"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 20:1"/>Shi aɓei ku aɓo wan zhi Bulus wa zhin waʼazi amigna nya wa kpe Akaya lo. <verse eid="ACT 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 20:2"/>Bulus ɓei zhin waʼazi lo cei na zhi yakwo woi lo Akaya. <verse eid="ACT 20:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 20:3"/>Wo ɓei dna Akaya har apya atnu, woi zhin shiri ge wa lo Suriya, a gna wo ge a Yahudiyi ye lo ɓa wu wo. Ntu ce nu wa lo Makidoniya.<verse eid="ACT 20:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 20:4"/>Sopata, Pihas nugun Biriya yi za, Aristakus n Sekundus a Tasalunikayi Gayus n wo gmi n Darba nyi. Timatawus n Tikikus yi ɓedo n Tirofimus yi aza ye vinya ɓa gni lo n Bulus yi ɓa lo Turki. <verse eid="ACT 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 20:5"/>Aza deye ɓo ku lo ɓa pmi yi zhi n Turowas. <verse eid="ACT 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 20:6"/>Shi Paska ɓo ku zo, ya lo eya n Filibi ya bwa anyi-pyei ngun atnu, ya kpe Turowas si. Ya fi ɓo har mako gmanyi.<verse eid="ACT 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ɓinuyi La Kaya Woi La Fi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 20:7"/>N Lahadi wyi a Kristiyi ɓa ye zhi ɓa gyi Dagayi tebur. Bulus wa zhin waʼazi n mwa kpa har sadu ntu ge efye ɓa gyi wa laka. <verse eid="ACT 20:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 20:8"/>Ena ɓei nyi n buzangna yi dai-dai n nyakun she n yi ɓei fi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 20:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 20:9"/>Shi Bulus ɓo gni woi daɓo Utikus woi tu woi wan gye, wa kaya n nyakun she tahi wa fi. <verse eid="ACT 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 20:10"/>Bulus wa shin lo wa la wo shi, wa gna aza ge fye to damun wo wye-wyei lo, a da aza. <verse eid="ACT 20:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 20:11"/>Ɓa jeze lo ɓa gyi abye n Dagayi tebur gyi yi. Bulus wa gyi abye n ɓedai har nya knaya. N labmi yi ɓa gna aje ammi. <verse eid="ACT 20:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 20:12"/>Sa fyewyi ɓa ɓe n Samariyi nwye-wyei, a da aza n mwa.<verse eid="ACT 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 20:13"/>Bulus wa zan-zan wa lo Asos, ama yi da ya lo eya ya ku si nwa bye. <verse eid="ACT 20:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 20:14"/>Shi yi ɓo sun na jei ɓo, ya knu eya lo ya lo Mitilini. <verse eid="ACT 20:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 20:15"/>Shi efye ɓo gyi ya si Kos, nyipyeyi do ya si Samos ya ɓe har Melitus.<verse eid="ACT 20:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Ɓeda Amigna Nya Nafisus</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 20:16"/>Nsa deye Bulus to ɓo ye ge wa kpe gni Afisus m, Wa lo Urushelima cewo ntu Paska ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 20:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 20:17"/>Shi yi ɓo si Melitus, Bulus wa tnu Afisus atukwoda ɓo, ɓa she gun yi n nuwan gbe.<verse eid="ACT 20:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 20:18"/>Shi ɓa ɓei ɓe wa gna ɓage, “Fye kpe lo ge tunyi nyipyei kmisunyi n mi ɓei ɓe Turki har sayi. <verse eid="ACT 20:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 20:19"/>Mi ku Dagayi tnu-tnu zhin ntukwo gba yi, saho ma ci bwi, mi-i sun wahala. A Yahudiyi ye cici ge ɓa wu mi.<verse eid="ACT 20:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 20:20"/>“Amma mi to fa fye gaiciya gna ɓo m. Mi ku gaiciya gna fye naza bye har ma dna n fye a puwa. <verse eid="ACT 20:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 20:21"/>Nabari gmanyi nu n mi cei ntu a Yahudiyi ɓo ɓedo abye do yi, nabari ho ko nu nyi ge aza ɓa fa laifi ɓa ɓe Shekwoyi aba. Tile zaho-zahoi wa ga Yesu gaiciya.<verse eid="ACT 20:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 20:22"/>“N sayi mi lo Urushelima nu, ntu ge Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi na gna mi ge mi lo. Amma mita kpe nya ye lo nkwo ɓo zhin mi ɓo m. <verse eid="ACT 20:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 20:23"/>Amma Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi ku gna mi ge wahala lo na bye. <verse eid="ACT 20:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 20:24"/>Omi wye-wyei zhin gbeloyi nu sai dai ma zhin a pma n kwoi, ma zhin tnu-tnu n Shekwoyi ga mi nyi. Emi tnu-tnu nu ge ma gna azaje Shekwoyi yeye ɓo, nwo alheri yi.<verse eid="ACT 20:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 20:25"/>“Mi kpe lo ge zaho-zahoi nfye mi, ta je mi wye gye m. <verse eid="ACT 20:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 20:26"/>Gaiciya nu n mi da zaho-zahoi ami ta tu n min.<verse eid="ACT 20:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 20:27"/>“Ntu ge mi to so Shekwoyi ɓeda m, mi-i ku kwo gna zaho-zahoyi. <verse eid="ACT 20:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 20:28"/>Suku-suku, fye kpa akni Shekwoyi nya wato owo ikklisiya nwa si n wo ami yi nyi, Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi na kni fye fya ze aɓo wyednayi. <verse eid="ACT 20:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 20:29"/>Mi kpe lo ge shi mi fa fye a malami a nukwoyi ɓa gna fye gna-gna, ɓa zhin a cam-cam nu. <verse eid="ACT 20:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 20:30"/>Azaho ma nfye mi ɓa ɓa shan gaiciya do, ntu ge ɓa gni aza ga ɓahin. <verse eid="ACT 20:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 20:31"/>Fye dnawye fya pa ngye shi ma gye ma nuwan n fyei esa nu ma sase n fya ba, har aye ngun ata. Saho ma cibwi ntu fye ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 20:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 20:32"/>N sayi ma fa fye n Shekwoyi akun n wo ɓeda yi, n kwo iko yi kwa mi fye gaiciya ga, wa ga fye gado anabarka nwo cei zhin shiri a owo aza nyi. <verse eid="ACT 20:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 20:33"/>Mi to shin agyiwye san gyi ko aje manayi m.<verse eid="ACT 20:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 20:34"/>“Fye kpe lo n gye shi ma zhin tnu-tnu n ma bwai, ntu mi bukata ɓo ɓedo n ma tnu-tnu kun-zhin-yi yi. <verse eid="ACT 20:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 20:35"/>Mi la ze gurbi nfye aba ntu ge ma ku bma awyekwoi zhin. Ma zhin lonu ntu ge mi pa Yesu Kristi ɓeda ɓo n wa da ge, ‘Nyaga du gwo-gwo n anabarka.’ ” <verse eid="ACT 20:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 20:36"/>Shi wo ɓei ku ɓeda zo wa ca-kwo-kwo wa zhin aduwa n ɓai. <verse eid="ACT 20:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 20:37"/>Ɓa cibwi n kala yi ɓa gna je ami. <verse eid="ACT 20:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 20:38"/>Ɓa ɓo zhin bugba zhi-zhiyi, ntu ge wo ɓei gna ge ɓa ta je wo wye gye m. Ɓa kun lo n woi har eya aba.<verse eid="ACT 20:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="ACT 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Zan Kmaknayi Lo Urushelima</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 21:1"/>Shi yi ɓei ku aje gna mi, na Afisus yi a tukwoda yi, ya lo eya ya lo Kos Efya gyi ya si Roda ya du ya lo Patara.<verse eid="ACT 21:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 21:2"/>N Patara ya lo eya kwoi lo Fonishiya n Suriya ʼkni. <verse eid="ACT 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 21:3"/>Ya duya ya gye Saipurus, amma yi to ɓei kpe zhi ɓo m, sai n Tayar dna n Suriya kni, n ɓo nu eya ɓei lo na kaya yi. <verse eid="ACT 21:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 21:4"/>Ya kun ya lo ya sun a Kristi yi ya fi n ɓai har mako gmanyi. Shekwoyi wa daɓo n Bulus yi n ɓa gbe ge wo to lo Urushelima m. <verse eid="ACT 21:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 21:5"/>Shi Lahadi ɓei wu vi ya jeze lo eya aba n gnisun a Kristi yi nɓa anyikwo yi n ɓa aɓi yi. N nuwan gbe eyi vinya ya kniakwokwo ya zhin aduwa. <verse eid="ACT 21:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 21:6"/>Yaku ka, ɓahin ɓa jeze lo api.<verse eid="ACT 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 21:7"/>Shi yi ɓo ku a Kristi yi ɓi gna n Tayar, ya lo Pitolemi, ya kpe zhi ɓo n nyipyei yi gmanyi, ya ɓi a Kristi yi gna. <verse eid="ACT 21:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 21:8"/>Ya ku ka ɓo, ya lo Kaisariya, ya lo Filibbus puwa waʼazi zhinyi nu n woi, wo zhin gmanyi nu dna aza, tnaba aɓei kni ntu nyagyi gna ɓo nyi. <verse eid="ACT 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 21:9"/>Wo ɓei anyigun yi ngun-anyi ɓa ɓei zhin anabi nu.<verse eid="ACT 21:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 21:10"/>Sa yi ɓo fi ɓo, Agabus wa gmi n Yahudiya wa ɓe, wo ɓei n nyaga anabci nya yi. <verse eid="ACT 21:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 21:11"/>Shi wo ɓei ɓe yi amisa, wa ku Bulus belti, wa pa wohin apita na bwa yi, wa gna, “Zafun Gyi-gyi-yi wa gna ge elo nu aɓa zhin n belti dagayi yi a Yahudiyi ɓa pa wo n Urushelima ɓa ga wo dna a Romayi akun.” <verse eid="ACT 21:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 21:12"/>Shi yi ɓo wo lonu a Kristi yi n Kaisariya n yi gnisun n woi nyi, ya gna wo ge wo to lo Urushelima m.<verse eid="ACT 21:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 21:13"/>Amma wagna ge, “Kni nu zhin fyei ci bwi a? Fye bma mi bugba ya nu. Mi n shiri zhin lo to ge ma lo kurkuku n Urushelima gmanyi m, amma ma fi ntu Dagayi Yesu Kristi ɓo.” <verse eid="ACT 21:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 21:14"/>Shi yi to ɓo mi n wo ɓo m, ya ku yi nya fa wa gna, “Shekwoyi ɓeye kwo ze lo nu.”<verse eid="ACT 21:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 21:15"/>Ya kuka ya ku eyi a kaya ya lo Urushelima. <verse eid="ACT 21:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 21:16"/>A Kristi yi n Kaisariya fyewyi ɓa kun lo n yi har Urushelima, shi yi ɓo si ya lo Manason puwa Saipuriyi za, Kristi yi kmisunyi nu ɓei n woi. <verse eid="ACT 21:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 21:17"/>A Yesu viyi vinya ɓa gwo yi na gmada yi.<verse eid="ACT 21:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 21:18"/>Efya gyi Bulus wa ku yi wa lo cei n Yakubu aba ɓedo ikklisiya; atukwoda yi n Urushelima, ya yezhi n ɓai. <verse eid="ACT 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 21:19"/>Shi yi ɓo ku aje ɓi gna Bulus wa gna ɓa anya vinya n Shekwoyi ku zhin n ya ba n abye do a tantasin.<verse eid="ACT 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 21:20"/>A da ɓa vinya ɓai ci Shekwoyi, ɓa gna omazado a Yahudiyi lo n mwa nɓa ku gaiciya ga, amma ɓa zhi ge har sayi a shi owa bwa na kunnu yi. <verse eid="ACT 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 21:21"/>A Yahudiyi a Kristi yi n ya ɓa ku wo ge ho zhin gaba lo n Musa owa yi na Yahudiyi kunnu yi, hoi gna ge a to zhin aɓi kaciya m. <verse eid="ACT 21:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 21:22"/>Yi ɓa zhin wunna? Ntu ge ɓa ɓa wo ge ho dna lo n ya.<verse eid="ACT 21:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 21:23"/>Yi ku kpe nya yi ɓa zhin, Aza lo n ya ngun-anyi nɓa ku shiri zhin ɓa wun tukwo ɓa zhin alkawali. <verse eid="ACT 21:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 21:24"/>Kun lo n ɓai a wun fye tukwo aduwa nyakun. Nha zhin lonu zaho-zahoi ɓa kpe ge ho ye lo na Yahudiyi kun-nu yi.<verse eid="ACT 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 21:25"/>Amma yi ta gna abye do lo, n ɓa vi Yesu nyi ge ɓa zhin kunnu ye m. Yi gna ge ɓa vi aɓo n yi ɓei ka fi ɓa n wasika nyi nu. To ɓa zhin anagbayin.<verse eid="ACT 21:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 21:26"/>Shi wo ɓei wo lonu, wa ye wa vi ɓa shaula wa lo aduwa nyakun wa ku kunnu. <verse eid="ACT 21:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 21:27"/>Ɓa ga sakirifais har anyipyei tnaba, nyipyei tnaba Yi a Yahudiyi ho a. Turkiyi, ɓa ɓe Urushelima ɓa gye wo dna aduwa nyakun. Ɓa zhin aza ɓa la rigima ka n Bulus yi. <verse eid="ACT 21:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 21:28"/>Ɓa wan wo ɓai ɓo wyi ɓai gna A Israilayi fye yewu. Oza i nyi n wo zhin waʼazi gaba n yi, woi gna aza ge ɓa to shi a Yahudiyi owa n. Har ma woi tu aduwa nyakun cegye, woi lo ɓe abyedo yi. <verse eid="ACT 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 21:29"/>Ɓa ɓo da lonu ntu ge, ɓa ɓo ku gye Bulus n Kunsun n Tirafimus yi. Wo ɓo zhin ebyedo nu, woi gmi Afisus n Turki ʼkni. Ɓa gye ngye Bulus la lo ɓe n woi nu na duwa nyakun.<verse eid="ACT 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 21:30"/>Ezhi vinya kwa ku wo ɓo na da tu Bulus tukwo. Ɓa gmi wo ya na duwa nyakun ɓa ku aba gu. <verse eid="ACT 21:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 21:31"/>Ɓai ye ɓa wu wo, amma a soja tukwoda wa wo sunu n zhi mi. <verse eid="ACT 21:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 21:32"/>N sai-sai yi wa tnu a soja yi ɓa lo rigima aba. Shi a Yahudiyi ɓo gye asoja ɓai ɓe ɓa ku fa Bulus lu ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 21:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 21:33"/>Soja tukwoda wa Bulus wan, wa wo pa agmayi, wa nya a Yahudiyi ɓo enya n Bulus zhin. <verse eid="ACT 21:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 21:34"/>Ɓa je kala ku na ɓeda yi ngye azhi n gnikwo. Amma to wa bwa ɓo kpalayi m, wa gna a soja ge ɓa lo n Bulus yi nɓa barki. <verse eid="ACT 21:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 21:35"/>A Yahudiyi ɓa vi lo ɓa zhin atna ge ba wu Bulus, amma a soja ɓa wo la tu agbe-gbegye ntu ge ɓa gni wo. <verse eid="ACT 21:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 21:36"/>Ɓai ɓowyi, ɓai gna a lo woi, a lo woi.<verse eid="ACT 21:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 21:37"/>Ai ye a lo dna n Bulus yi n nyakun, wa gna soja tukwoda ge, suku mi ye ma daɓo. Soja tukwoda wa nya wo ge, “Wo wo Helleni lo?” <verse eid="ACT 21:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 21:38"/>Oho nu to zhin Masar za n wo ɓo la wahala ka aye fyewyi n ɓa duya nyi har haku aza wuyi 4,000 ha lo ɓai n zhabui m.<verse eid="ACT 21:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 21:39"/>Bulus wa gna awo. Mi zhin Yahudiyayi nu mi gmi n Tarusus nu, n Silisiya kni. Mi ɓa ho ha ye ge ma daɓo na za deye yi.<verse eid="ACT 21:39"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Kna Aza Wyeya Tu Nwo Tnu-Tnu Ɓo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 21:40"/>Soja tukwoda wa esa ga wo, Bulus wa tu n nyakun she bayi, wa gna za ɓa ce pi wa da aɓeda ye n Ibrahim bye yi.<verse eid="ACT 21:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="ACT 22"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 22:1"/>Omi azaje n na dada yi fye wo mi ɓe da. <verse eid="ACT 22:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 22:2"/>Shi ɓa ɓo wo woi daɓo n Ibrahim bye yi, ɓa ku gna cece pi. <verse eid="ACT 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 22:3"/>Mi zhin Yahudiya yi nu, a ma mi n Tarsus Silisiya kni. Ma zhin makaranta n ya nu n Urushelima. Galnaliyo nu ɓei zhin mi Malami, wawu mi shi mi ɓa shi a Yahudiyi owa bwa na kunnu yi, mi ɓei zhin mi yi la Shekwoyi tu cici, ngye shi fye zhin n naiye nyi. <verse eid="ACT 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 22:4"/>Ma ga ikklisiya wahala mi wan a Kristi yi anugbayi na nyikwoyi ma gu ɓa fi n kurkuku. <verse eid="ACT 22:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 22:5"/>Piristi dnagmayi kwo na shaula zhinyi, wo ɓa ci mi seda ge mi da gaiciya nu. Ntu ge n ɓa aba nu n mi ɓo zhin ma gwo takarda izni nya, ntu ge ma lo Dimashika ma wan a Kristi yi ɓe cei n Urushelima ntu tata ɓo.<verse eid="ACT 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 22:6"/>N wyihoi mi lo Dimashika buzangna dnagmayi nshe kwa knaya she mi gun, kwo ɓo zhin n nyipyei bwai nu vivi n Dimashika yi. <verse eid="ACT 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 22:7"/>Nsai-sa yi ma miya shi n kni, ma wo begye kwoi gna, “Shawulu, Shawulu kniyi nu zhin hoi ga mi wahala?”<verse eid="ACT 22:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 22:8"/>Ma nya ge, nkanu daɓo mi ya, Shekwoyi mwasa hoi, Wa gna “Omi nu Yesu Nazaratiyi n ho ga wo wahala nyi.” <verse eid="ACT 22:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 22:9"/>Aza nɓa ɓei gnisun n mi nyi ɓa gye buzangna, amma to ɓa gane n ɓei na da m. <verse eid="ACT 22:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 22:10"/>Ma nya ge, “Dagayi nɓa zhin wuna?” Dagayi wa gna mi, “Laka ha lo Dimashika aɓo wu ho ɓo nho ɓa zhin na bye deye.”<verse eid="ACT 22:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 22:11"/>Buzangnayi ɓo ku awye bua mi, ashi mi busi bwa shishi nu ma lo Dimashika. <verse eid="ACT 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 22:12"/>Hananiya ɓei zhin Shekwoyi za nu woi vi a Yahudiyi o wa, ɓai kpe wo ye vinya n Dimashika ntu wo hali manayi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 22:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 22:13"/>Oza ye wa ɓe mi aba wa gni vivi n mi, Yi wa gna, “Omizado Shawulu. Gwo wyeba gye,” n sai-sayi ma mi ma gye wo wye n anya yi nɓa ɓo she mi gun nyi.<verse eid="ACT 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 22:14"/>Wa gna mi ge, Shekwoyi eyi dada nya n la ho kni, ha kpe wo ɓemwi ye, ha gye Masihu ha wo wo ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 22:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 22:15"/>Ho ɓa da owo nabari aba vinya. Ho ɓa da enya n ha wo n nya yi nha gye. <verse eid="ACT 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 22:16"/>Kniyi nu ɓa zhin ha zhin kalala? Laka azhin ho batizma a zhan ho alaifi ya, ha yi Shekwoyi. <verse eid="ACT 22:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 22:17"/>N wyihoi mi dna aduwa nyakun mi-i zhin aduwa ma nu ena. <verse eid="ACT 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 22:18"/>Ma gye Shekwoyi woi gna mi ge, Laka ha fa Urushelima ntu ge aza ta kna ho ɓeda tnubua n ya m.<verse eid="ACT 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 22:19"/>Ma gna ge, Dagayi ɓa kpe lo vinya ge ma ku oho a viyi ga wahala, mi yi fi ɓa n kurkuku. <verse eid="ACT 22:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 22:20"/>Sa aɓo wu Istifanus cei nyi mi ɓei gni, mi nu ɓo go aje n aza ɓo kma zhin, ɓa kpe wo akuta kni nyi.<verse eid="ACT 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 22:21"/>Amma Shekwoyi wa gna ge, “Fa Urushelima gama mi ye ma tnu ho n kpai nu abye do aba.”<verse eid="ACT 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 22:22"/>Shi Bulus ɓo sa abyedo ye, ɓa je kala ku n wyiɓoyi n kala yi ngye anya-cei. Ɓai gna, alo woi, a wu wo, ko to kunce lo oza deye wa bwa wye-wyei m. <verse eid="ACT 22:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 22:23"/>Ɓa gyi abye n wyiɓo yi, ɓai she aje ya gun she, ɓai she amwi ya laɓa.<verse eid="ACT 22:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 22:24"/>A soja tukwoda walo dna n Bulus yi n nyakun, wa gna soja ho ge wo lu wo ntu ge wa da wo alaifi. Wo ɓo zhin lonu ntu ge wa kpe dalili nkwo zhin a Yahudiyi ɓai zhin aɓo ngye anyacei.<verse eid="ACT 22:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 22:25"/>Shi ɓa ɓo la wo pa ge ɓa lu wo, Bulus wa nya soja yi ge, kwo wu lo dai-dai a lu Romayi za to ai da wo owan?<verse eid="ACT 22:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 22:26"/>Shi wo ɓo nya wo lonu, wa laka wa lo asoja tukwoda aba, wa nya wo ge kniyi nu ho zhin a? Gye oza deye zhin Romayi nu.<verse eid="ACT 22:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 22:27"/>Soja tukwoda wa lo wa nya Bulus ɓo, “Gna mi, ho zhin Romayi za nu?” Bulus wa gna mi zhin kwo nu. <verse eid="ACT 22:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 22:28"/>A soja tukwoda wa ci ge kafin mi zhin Romayi za miɓo ku agyiwye wu n mwa. Amma Bulus wa gna wo ge mi da to sisi nu m, a ma mi mama nu n zhin Romayi za. <verse eid="ACT 22:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 22:29"/>A soja n ɓa ɓo ye ɓa lu wo nyi, shi ɓa ɓo wo ge wo zhin Romayi nu, ɓa busi. A soja tukwoda n wohin wa wo dna ntu ge wo ku gna a soja ge ɓa pa wo ɓa lu wo.<verse eid="ACT 22:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Gni Nna Shaula Zhinyi Abye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 22:30"/>Efya gyi a soja tukwoda wa wo loya wayi a prist dnagmayi ɓa yezhi, wa ɓe n Bulus yi n ɓa bye ntu ge wa wo dalili nkwo zhin ɓai lagyi-kici ka dna n zhimi.<verse eid="ACT 22:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="ACT 23"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 23:1"/>Shi Bulus ɓo gni a shaula zhinyi abye wa gna, Omi azaje, mi ku zan-zan n Shekwoyi abye cici n bugba manayi yi.<verse eid="ACT 23:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 23:2"/>Nwo ɓeda zun-zunyai Hannaniya prist dnagmayi wa gna zaho ge wo lu Bulus ngbe.<verse eid="ACT 23:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 23:3"/>Bulus wa gna ge Shekwoyi ɓa ce hohim pmi, oho nyakunpa bui-bui, kni alkali yi pya nu tu, to woi vi owan woi gna za ge wo ce mi pmi a?<verse eid="ACT 23:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 23:4"/>Aza nɓa ɓei zhi vivi n Bulus yi ɓa gna wo ge, ɓedanu n ho da n Shekwoyi piristi dnagmayi?<verse eid="ACT 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 23:5"/>Bulus wa gna, mi ta kpe lo ge wo nu zhin pirist dnagmayi m, ntu ge Shekwoyi ɓeda gna ge to da ɓeda nukwoyi tu n fye abegyiyi tukwo m.<verse eid="ACT 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 23:6"/>Amma shi Bulus ɓo kpe ge a Sadukiyi ɓei fi ɓo ɓedo Afarisiyi wa gna, omi azaje mi zhin Farisiyi nu emi azakwoi vinya ɓei zhin Afarisiyi nu Mihin kwa a da mi owa ntu ge mi gaiciya ga ge efi kalaku lo nu.<verse eid="ACT 23:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 23:7"/>Shi wo ɓei da lonu aza yezhi, ɓa gnaj e ngun aba a Sadukiyi na Farisiyi. <verse eid="ACT 23:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 23:8"/>Ntu ge a Sadukiyi gna ge efi kalaku to nyi m, amalaika to nyi m, Zafun nyalo-nyalo nya to nyi m, amma a Farisiyi n gaiciya ga na ɓeye vinya.<verse eid="ACT 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 23:9"/>Aɓo ɓa ku gmaje na shaula zhin ba. A Yahudiyi abye da ɓai gna ɓa to gye Bulus laifi m, Ɓa naɓo najei. Ɓa gna kpesun Zafun ko malaika nu ɓei daɓo n Bulus yi n Dimashika zokwo.<verse eid="ACT 23:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 23:10"/>Ɓai ɓowyi n kala yi, aza ku she Bulus gnu ɓai gni wo laɓa. Safyewyi a soja tukwoda wa gna asoja ge ɓa la Bulus lo cei n ɓa barki woi gye ngye a Yahudiyi ɓa wu wo.<verse eid="ACT 23:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 23:11"/>Nsukwoyi Dagayi wa daɓo n Bulus yi wa gna wo ge to damun, ngye shi ho ku mi seda zhin n Urushelima aza abye nyi elonu ho ɓa zhin n Roma.<verse eid="ACT 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12-13" style="v" pubnumber="12,13" sid="ACT 23:12-13"/> N labmi yi aza ɓei du shinyi (40) nɓa ɓei la nyasi si ge ɓa ta gyi nyagyi kwo ɓa sin nuwan, sai ɓa la Bulus wu. <verse eid="ACT 23:12-13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 23:14"/>Ɓa lo ɓa ku gna a Pristi dnagmayi na byeda yi enya ɓa ye ɓa zhin. <verse eid="ACT 23:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 23:15"/>“Fye lo fye gna asoja tukwoda” nji a prist ɓedo abye da yi “wa ɓe n Bulus yi njesun a shaula zhin ba, shi a ɓe n woi, ya wu wo n zokwo.”<verse eid="ACT 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 23:16"/>Amma Bulus zhalu wa ku wo, wa lo wa ku gna Bulus na soja barki.<verse eid="ACT 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 23:17"/>Bulus wa yi soja dnagmayi ho wa gna wo ge, “Lo n ɓi ye yi nfye tukwoda aba wo ɓo kpakala yi lo wa gna wo.”<verse eid="ACT 23:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 23:18"/>Soja yi wa lo woi wa gna, Bulus na gna ge mi ɓe nɓi ye yi nho aba, nge wo nɓei lo wa gna ho.<verse eid="ACT 23:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 23:19"/>A soja tukwoda wa la ɓihi wa gni n woi n gna-gna wa nya wo ge, Ho ye ha gna mi kni ɓo yi nu a?<verse eid="ACT 23:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 23:20"/>Ɓihin wa gna nsu a Yahudiyi ɓei gna ho ge ho ɓe n Bulus yi na Shaula zhin ba njesun. <verse eid="ACT 23:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 23:21"/>Amma to ɓei ye m. Aza lo n du shinyi n bwi fi n gbe-gbe ge, shi aɓe nwoi ɓa wu wo n zokwo. Ɓa ta sin nuwan kwo ɓa gyi nyagyi m, sai ɓa la Bulus wu. Ɓa cei kma lo ɓa ɓe ɓa nya ho.<verse eid="ACT 23:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 23:22"/>A soja tukwoda wa gna oɓihi n ge to gna zaho-zahoi ge ho ku ɓeye gna mi m. <verse eid="ACT 23:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 23:23"/>Sai a soja tukwoda wa yi asoja dnagmayi aje wa gna ɓa ge, Ifye zhin shiri na soja yi 200 ɓa lo Kaisariya nsukwoyi naiye. Fye ku amashi da 200 a dokwo da yi 70. <verse eid="ACT 23:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 23:24"/>Fya ga Bulus dokwo wa tu fya lo woi n Gwmna Fileks aba.<verse eid="ACT 23:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 23:25"/>Wa ku wasika ka ga Feliks wa gna.<verse eid="ACT 23:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 23:26"/>Wasikaye gmi n Klaudiyus Lisiyas aba nu kwoi ɓe Gwamna Feliks aba Shekwo mwasa hoi, gnaɓi ɓe ho aba.<verse eid="ACT 23:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 23:27"/>Oza deye a Yahudiyi na wan wo ɓai ye ɓa wu wo, amma ma tnu na soja yi ɓa gwo wo nɓa kun ntu ge nɓo ku wo ge wo zhin Roma yi nu. <verse eid="ACT 23:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 23:28"/>Ma la wo ma lo cei nɓa shaula zhinba, ntu ge ma wo laifi n wa zhin. <verse eid="ACT 23:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 23:29"/>Ma gye ko zhin oɓa a Yahudiyi adini ɓo nu n na kunnu yi. Ɓehin-hin ɓe ho to lo nkwo ɓa zhin adna wo n kurkuku m. <verse eid="ACT 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 23:30"/>Amma shi ma wo ge ɓa ku shiri zhin ɓa wu wo, ce na zhin mi tnu n woi n ho aba. Mi ku gna owo akala zhinyi ge ɓa ɓe n wo alaifi yi nho abye. Aku zo.<verse eid="ACT 23:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 23:31"/>A soja ɓa la Bulus n sukwoyi ɓa lo woi n Antipata. <verse eid="ACT 23:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 23:32"/>N Labmi yi a soja ɓa jeze ɓe ɓa barki ɓa fa Bulus na dokwo da yi, ɓa lo woi n Kaisariya.<verse eid="ACT 23:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 23:33"/>Shi ɓa ɓei si Kaisariya ɓa wasika ga Gwamna, ɓa wu wo Bulus njesun. <verse eid="ACT 23:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 23:34"/>Shi wo ɓo la wasika ba wa nya Bulus aba n wo gmi, Bulus wa gna mi gmi n Silisiya nu.<verse eid="ACT 23:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 23:35"/>Gwamna wa gna wo ge n ɓei wo ho ɓeda, esa nho akala gayi ɓei ku ɓe. Gwamna wa gna asoja ge ɓa la wo dna n kurkuku n Hirudus galukwo.<verse eid="ACT 23:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="ACT 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Gni Nna Romayi Ikoda Abye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 24:1"/>A bwa anyipyei ngun-atnu Hananiya ɓedo a yahudiyi abyeda yi n Tetullus yi ɓa lo I Kaisariya. Ɓa ɓe ntu ge ɓa da Bulus alaifi. Hananiya nu ɓei zhin prist dnagmayi, Tetullus Bei zhin loya nu. <verse eid="ACT 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 24:2"/>Shi Gwamna ɓo yi Tetullus ge wa da Bulus alaifi wa gna, “Shekwo mwasa, eyi a Yahudiyi yi kpe lo ge ho la salama, n loloya yi ga yi n ho kni.<verse eid="ACT 24:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 24:3"/>“Ntu deye ɓo a da yi lo n mwa. <verse eid="ACT 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 24:4"/>Yi ta ye ya wun ho sa ya m, amma yi ɓa ye ha wo yi, nɓa da anya n ɓa gna yi gna-gna n Bulus yi. <verse eid="ACT 24:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 24:5"/>Wahala gayi nu n woi, wo ku zhin a Yahudiyi vinya ɓai la gyikici ka, ɓai zhin gaba na Romayi gwamnati yi. Wo nu zhin a Kristi yi tukwoda. <verse eid="ACT 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 24:6"/>Wo ɓo zhin atna wa tu aduwa nyakun cegye ya wan wo. Yi ɓo ye ya da wo owa bisa ga eyi adini.<verse eid="ACT 24:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 24:7"/>“Amma Lisiyas asoja tukwoda wa wo gwo n ya kun na kala yi. <verse eid="ACT 24:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 24:8"/>Wa gna aɓa da Bulus owa bisa ga a Romayi wyidna Ho ɓa wo gaiciya n wohin aba.”<verse eid="ACT 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 24:9"/>A Yahudiyi vinya ɓa fi aku, ɓa gna, enya n Tetullus ku da nyi gaiciya nu.<verse eid="ACT 24:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 24:10"/>Kwa si Bulus sa, Gwamna wa gna wo ge wo laka wa daɓo. Bulus wa gna, “Shekwo mwasa hoi mi kpe lo ge ho la mwasa hoi da a Yahudiyi owa aye yi mwa begye, ada mi lo.<verse eid="ACT 24:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 24:11"/>“Nya mi ye ma da nyi kwo ɓa wu ho ge, ma lo Urushelima ntu mwa-mwa ga ɓo nu, anyipyei awo-cei-aba nɓa duya nyi. <verse eid="ACT 24:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 24:12"/>Ho ɓa gye njesun ge, mi to shin gyikici kala la ko aduwa nyakun, ko ezhi doho-dohoyi m. <verse eid="ACT 24:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 24:13"/>Aza deye ta mi ɓa ga seda, ntu anya ɓo n ɓa da ge ma zhin nyi m.<verse eid="ACT 24:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 24:14"/>“Enya mi zhin waʼazi tu ko cici okwonu zhin gni gni zokwo. Okwo nu n ɓa gna wuwu nukwoyi. Mi zhin ma zhin Shekwoyi bauta shi eyi a zakwoyi zhin. Mi gaiciya yi ga a Yahudiyi owa, na nyai vinya n ɓa kafi anabi a littafi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 24:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 24:15"/>Mi gaiciya yi ga n efi kalaku n vingwo, a ɓefye-cei ɓedo aza nukwoyi, ɓahin lo nu ce. <verse eid="ACT 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 24:16"/>Ntu aɓo deye ɓo mi zhin atna n mi akala yi vinya, ma zhin ɓo ko bmiya n Shekwoyi abye, na za yi.<verse eid="ACT 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 24:17"/>“Mi ɓo la gmiya na ye yi mwa begye, ma je ze ɓe Urushelima na gyiwyei shi ma bma a Yahudiyi zhin, ma zhin sakirifais ga Shekwoyi. <verse eid="ACT 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 24:18"/>Aza deye ɓo gye ml na sakirifais zhin ba nu. Mi la tukwo wun shi owa da. Zaho-zahoi to ɓei gni n ma ba m gyikici to ɓo nyi m, amma a Yahudiyi ho a Turki ɓei zhi ɓo. <verse eid="ACT 24:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 24:19"/>A Yahudiyi ye, ɓei gna ɓa zhi lo n ya, ɓo da laifi n ma zhin.<verse eid="ACT 24:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 24:20"/>“Aza deye ɓo sun mi, mi yi zhin kni ɓe nukwoyi nuʼa? <verse eid="ACT 24:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 24:21"/>Enya Pi gmanyi nu n mikpe lo, n mi ɓei da na wada ba ge, ‘Mi gni ai da mi owa ntu efi kalaku ɓo nu n vingwo.’ ”<verse eid="ACT 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 24:22"/>Fileks kpe lo ge a Kristi yi ta la gyikici ka m, ntu ce nu wa gna Yahudiyi ge ɓa ku pmi sai Lisiyas la e kafin wo zo ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 24:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 24:23"/>Wa gna a je ze lo n Bulus yi n kurkuku, amma a gye ɓa nuwan n woi daidai, a fa owo anugundo ɓa ɓe wo aba ɓa gye wo, ɓa ga wo anya ntu ge wa bwa agmada.<verse eid="ACT 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 24:24"/>Anyipyei fyewyi avun Feliks wa ɓe n Dirasilayi owo nyikwo, wo ɓei zhin Yahudiyi za nu. Ɓa tnu Bulus ɓo ntu ge wa gna ɓa Yesu ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 24:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 24:25"/>Wa daɓo nɓai tu efyece ɓo, n ɓemanayi zhin yi, n wa da yi nkwo ɓo lo nyi. Feliks wa wo dna shi wo ɓo wo aɓeye. Wa gna Bulus ge, “Lo kpa nɓa je ho yi mi la esa bwa.”<verse eid="ACT 24:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 24:26"/>Wa gye ngye Bulus ɓa ga wo toshi, ntu ce nu wa tnu wo ɓo cici woi daɓo n woi. <verse eid="ACT 24:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 24:27"/>Wa gyi abye woi yi Bulus nasasayi, har aye ngun-aba. Amma Bulus to ɓei gawo toshi m, Avun a shan Feliks do, abe n Posho Festus yi. Feliks woi ye ge a Yahudiyi ɓa bwa agmada n woi, wa Bulus fa dna n kurkuku.<verse eid="ACT 24:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="ACT 25"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 25:1"/>A nyipyei ngu ata shi Festos ɓei ɓe Kaisariya wa lo Urushelima. Wo ɓei ɓe Kaisariya ntu ge wa la Feliks tnu-tnu nu wato Gwamna eknihi nya nu. <verse eid="ACT 25:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 25:2"/>A Urushelima yi atukwoda ɓa gye wo nɓo, ɓa gna wo Bulus ɓeda vinya. <verse eid="ACT 25:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 25:3"/>ʼBa gyiwo wye ntuge wa ɓe n Bulus yi n Urushelima, ɓa ɓei ye ɓa wu wo nu. <verse eid="ACT 25:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 25:4"/>Amma Festos wa ci ɓa ge, “Bulus lu Kaisariya du woi ɓei gni woi lo ɓo nu nwohin <verse eid="ACT 25:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 25:5"/>Ntu cenu aza n ɓa kpe ɓeye ye lo ɓa ɓe Kaisariya n ɓahin nabai a dawa nbwai.”<verse eid="ACT 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">A Ya Bulus Wada</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 25:6"/>Shi anyipyei ngu awo ɓei ku si, wa jeze lo Kaisariya. Efya gyi wa ya Bulus wa da.<verse eid="ACT 25:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 25:7"/>Shi Bulus ɓei lo dna n kotu a Yahudiyi nɓa ɓei kun n Urushelima nyi, ɓa ku yezhi, ɓai da owo alaifi ɓo n tna asaida. <verse eid="ACT 25:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 25:8"/>Bulus wa na aɓo, wa gna, “Mi to n laifi yi lo m, ntu ge mi to zun Ayahudiyi awyidna gna m, ko ma da ɓenukwoyi tu aduwanyakun tukwo m, ko ma zhin gaba n Roma yi gwanmati yi m.”<verse eid="ACT 25:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 25:9"/>Festus woi ye owo ɓo kwa da Ayahudiyi wa nya wo ge, “Ho ɓa ye halo Urushelima, mi da ho owa n bwai?”<verse eid="ACT 25:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10-11" style="v" pubnumber="10,11" sid="ACT 25:10-11"/> Ama Bulus wa ye wa gna, “awo, miɓa ye Esu Roma nya wa wo mi. Ho kpe lo ge mi to n laifi yi lo m. Ndei mi ku laifi zhin nkwo kunce lo n fi yi, mi ta naɓo lo ge ma fi m, ama ndei mi zhin oza kni-kniyi nu, ozaho to iko yi lo wa dna mi n aza deye akun ntu ge ɓa wu min. Nɓa ye ma lo Kaisar aba.”<verse eid="ACT 25:10-11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 25:12"/>Festus wa zhin shaula nwo shaula gayi, wa gna, abmiya lo la ye ge ha lo Kaisar aba, Kaisar aba nu n ho ɓa lo!<verse eid="ACT 25:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 25:13"/>Anyipyei ho fyewyi ɓa duya, Esu Agarippa n Banis yi ɓa ɓe Festus gnaɓi. <verse eid="ACT 25:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 25:14"/>Dna anyipyei n ɓa ɓei fi ɓo nyi, Festus wa zhin shaula tu n Bulus tukwo n ʼsu yi wa gna wo ge, “Za-wan-wan ho dna lo n ya n Feliks ɓei ya wo ɓeda shi ge ma da. <verse eid="ACT 25:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 25:15"/>Esa nu mi ɓei dna n Urushelima a malami adnagmayi ɓedo Ayadudiyi abyeda yi, ɓa ku ɓa lafiya wu mi har ɓa gna mi ge mi la wo wu. <verse eid="ACT 25:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 25:16"/>Ma ku wu ɓa ge a Romayi owa ta zun oza kni to ai da wo owan, a zhin a esa ga wo ɓa da ɓo n za yi nɓo nɓai dna a je yi.<verse eid="ACT 25:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 25:17"/>“Shi ɓa ɓo ɓe ya, efye kwa gyi, a ɓeda kun zhi, ma ɓe n Bulus yi. <verse eid="ACT 25:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 25:18"/>Ama ma wo aɓeda n ɓa ɓo da tu nwo tukwo nyi, to ma gye aɓo nu n mi ɓei cei mwi m. <verse eid="ACT 25:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 25:19"/>Oɓo nyi tu nɓa kunnu tukwo nu, oza ho ge a yi wo ge Yesu, wa fi, amma Bulus wa gyi tu ge wo n wye-wyei lo. <verse eid="ACT 25:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 25:20"/>Ma ku jeje ngye shi mi ɓa zun ɓeda ye ya, ma nya wo kwo wo ɓa ye a da wo owa tu aɓeye tukwo n Urushelima. <verse eid="ACT 25:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 25:21"/>Ama Bulus wa gna ge, wo ɓa ye wa lo n ɓeda yi n Kaisar aba. Shi wo ɓo da lonu, ma gna ge a lo n woi, o la wo je gu, har ma zhin shiri ma tnu n woi n Esu dnagmayi aba.”<verse eid="ACT 25:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 25:22"/>Agaribas wa gna ge, nɓa ye ma wo wo ɓeda n mihin. Festus wa gna wo ge, Ho ɓei wo wo nsu.<verse eid="ACT 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 25:23"/>Shi efye ɓo gyi, esu ɓedo n Barniki yi ɓa ɓe kwotu nɓa mwa-mwa ɓedo asoja atukwo da yi, n aza adnagmayi ezhi hi Festus wa gna ge a ɓe n Bulus yi.<verse eid="ACT 25:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 25:24"/>Festus wa da ɓo na za yi wa gna, “Esu Agaribas ɓedo aza yi vinya, Ayahudiyi n ɓa ʼya ɓedo aza yi n ɓa lo n Urushelima, ɓa ce pma ge awu oza deye. <verse eid="ACT 25:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 25:25"/>Amma n mi wyegye, wo to zhin nyaho nkwo kunce awu wom. Dudu lonu wo ku na ge wo ɓa lo nɓeda yi n Kaisar aba, omihin mi to nɓodo yi lo nmi ɓa zhin m, sai ma tnu woi. <verse eid="ACT 25:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 25:26"/>Ama mɓa ka kniɓeyi ma ga Esu dnagmayi hi a? Ntu ge mi to gye wo laifi, na gna ge wa zhin m, cenu a zhin mi ɓe nwo yi n fye abye vinya, Oho Esu Agaribas ha mwi wo, ha wu mi nya mi ɓa ka. <verse eid="ACT 25:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 25:27"/>Ntu ge kwo ta wu mi lo dei-dei ma tnu n za wan-wan yi n Esu dnagmayi aba ntna ɓo tukwo m.”<verse eid="ACT 25:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="ACT 26"/>
  <para style="s1">Bulus Wa Kna Wohin</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 26:1"/>Agaribas wa gna Bulus ge, “Gya bye ha gna yi ho ɓeda.” Bulus wa wu obwa, wa ya ɓeda da.<verse eid="ACT 26:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 26:2"/>Wa gna, mi gye mihin tukwo Esu Agaribas nzhin arzikida nu, shi mi ye ma da mihin ɓeda nho abye. <verse eid="ACT 26:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 26:3"/>Ntu gemi kpe lo ge, ho zhin oza nu, n wo kpe Ayahudiyi owa ye ɓedo n ɓa akunnu yi. Nsayi mi gyi ho wye ha kna tnubua.<verse eid="ACT 26:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 26:4"/>“Ayahudiyi kpe lo sarai ge ma ku makaranta Ayahudiyi nya zhin dna Tarsus, avun ma ɓe Urushelima ma ku aɓo zhin dei-dei. <verse eid="ACT 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 26:5"/>Ɓa ɓei ɓa ye ɓa da, ɓa kpe lo ge mi zhin Farisiyi nu nwo ta ye ge afua wye n Ayahudiyi owa yi ɓedo nɓa akunnu yi m. <verse eid="ACT 26:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 26:6"/>Ama dalili nkwo zhin ɓai ga mi laifi nyi kwo lo gbo, ɓa ga mi laifi ge mi na wyetu yi ntu alkawali nu ɓo n Shekwoyi ɓo zhin ga eyi azakwoyi nyi. <verse eid="ACT 26:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 26:7"/>A Israilayi abye ngun awo-cei-aba, ɓa zhin atna nyipyei n sukwoyi ge ɓa gye alkawali ye nunu nɓa ʼsa, ama nsayi ɓa la mi ze laifi da. <verse eid="ACT 26:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 26:8"/>Kwo zhin laifi nu ge oza wa ga gaiciya ge efi kala ku lo? Kwo to zhin gaiciya nu ge Shekwoyi n iko yi lo wa je za wye-wyei gan?<verse eid="ACT 26:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 26:9"/>“N ɓei zhin mi gye ngye kwo bmiya lo ma ga aza wahala n ɓa vi Yesu nyi. <verse eid="ACT 26:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 26:10"/>Nɓo ku aza fi n kurkuku n mwa begye n Urushelima, n iko amalami dnagmayi nya yi, esa nɓa da aza owa ofi nya, kwa da mi har ma ye nɓei nɓa zhin nyi.” <verse eid="ACT 26:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 26:11"/>Mi ɓei zhin ma ga a Yesu viyi wahala abaho-baho yi, mi ye ge ɓa na Yesu aɓo. Mi ɓei pyena nɓayi, mi zan ɓa shin azhi yakwo, akniyi gbo-gbo.<verse eid="ACT 26:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12-13" style="v" pubnumber="12,13" sid="ACT 26:12-13"/> “N wyihoi mi lo ɓa zanshi n Dimashika, mi la izni gwo n malami, dnagmayi, n nyipyei na tukwo, buzangna dnagmayi ndu nyipyei nya, kwa bmiya fi yi ɓedo aza yi nɓa ɓo gnisun n mi yi. <verse eid="ACT 26:12-13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 26:14"/>Eyi vinya ya miya zhi nkni, ma wo begye kwoi daɓo n mi yi n Ibraniyi bye yi, kwoi gna Shawulu, Shawulu kniyi nu zhin hoi ga mi wahala? Ho ga hohin nu wahala.<verse eid="ACT 26:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 26:15"/>“Ma nya ge, ‘nkanu hoi ya?’ Dagayi wa ye ga gna, ‘Omi nu Yesu n ho ga wo wahala nyi. <verse eid="ACT 26:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 26:16"/>Laka! Ntu ge mi la ho kni ha ze mi fyenu n mi saida da yi, ce na zhin mi wu mihin tukwo n ho aba. Ho ɓa gna anyi aɓo ho ku gye, n aɓo n ho ɓa gye, esa n ma wu mihin tukwo n ho aba. <verse eid="ACT 26:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 26:17"/>Nɓa kna ho n ho azaje aba ɓedo abyedo yi. Nɓa tnu ho n abye do aba, <verse eid="ACT 26:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 26:18"/>ha kpe ɓa awye ya, ɓa gye gaiciya ɓa ye abui, ɓa zan-zan dna buzangna Shekwoyi nya, maimakon shetan wyegma, ntu ge ɓa bwa gafara oɓa alaifi nya, ɓa ze gado Shekwoyi nya, ɓedo aza yi abaho-bahoi vinya, oɓa nu a la oɓa alaifi zhan ya ntu ɓa gaiciya ga ɓo omi aba.’<verse eid="ACT 26:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 26:19"/>“Ntu deye ɓo, O esu Agaribas, mi to ɓei na ɓo n ɓewyegye eshe nya yi m. <verse eid="ACT 26:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 26:20"/>Ma ya waʼazi zhin ga aza n Dimashika mi, n Urushelima yi ɓedo n Yahudiya ekni yi, n jesun n abyedo aba, mi-i gna ɓa ge ɓa fwa alaifi ɓa pmibma ɓe Shekwoyi aba, ɓa wu oɓa bmapmi a tnu-tnu manayi. <verse eid="ACT 26:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 26:21"/>A Yahudiyi ɓa wan mi dna aduwa nyakun ntu waʼazi zhin ɓo, ɓai ye ɓa wu mi. <verse eid="ACT 26:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 26:22"/>Ama Shekwoyi wa mi gni, cenu zhin mi gni n wye-wyei n naiye, ma gna aza dnagmayi n aza anawyi yi gaiciya ye. Mi ta wu nyaho lo gbo n nya yi annabi edo n Musa yi ɓei da m. <verse eid="ACT 26:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 26:23"/>Nge Masihu ɓa sin wahala, wa ze oza kmisunyi n wo ɓo laka la evingwo, wa ɓe n buzangna yi na Yahudiyi aba ɓedo n abye do yi.”<verse eid="ACT 26:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 26:24"/>Festus wa da ɓo nkalayi ngye wa kaya nshe, wa ci ge, “Bulus ho la cenya. Oho nyaba nmwa la tukwo pmi ho ya!”<verse eid="ACT 26:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 26:25"/>Ama Bulus wa gna, “Mi ta cenya nu m, Festus duduyi, ama mi da gaiciya nu Behinhin. <verse eid="ACT 26:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 26:26"/>Esu Agaribas kpe aɓeye lo, Mi da ɓeda ye n bugba kala yi, ntu ge aɓeye to zhin aɓo woi-woi nu nwo aba m, ntu ge ato zhin ɓa n vi nu m. <verse eid="ACT 26:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 26:27"/>Esu Agaribas ha ga annabi gaiciya! Mi kpe lo ha ga gaiciya.”<verse eid="ACT 26:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 26:28"/>Agaribas wa gna wo ge, n aɓedeye yi ho ye ma ze Yesu viyi-i? <verse eid="ACT 26:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 26:29"/>Bulus wa ye wa gna, Mi gyi Shekwoyi wye lo omi ɓeda kwa zhin ho ɓedo aza yi vinya nɓa zhi lo ya, ɓa ku ze ngye mi, sai dai to ngye agma n ɓa fi n mi nyi m.<verse eid="ACT 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 26:30"/>Sai esu, n gwamna yi, Barniki aza yi vinya ɓa kukala ɓa kunya. <verse eid="ACT 26:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 26:31"/>Shi ɓa ɓo zhin shaula ɓa gna, “Oza deye to zhin laifi n wo ɓa fi ko a dna wo n kurkuku m.”<verse eid="ACT 26:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 26:32"/>Agaribas wa gna Festus ge, wo to ɓei ku gna ge, wo ɓa lo n ɓeda yi n Kaisar aban, o la wo loya.<verse eid="ACT 26:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="ACT 27"/>
  <para style="s1">Ozan Kwoi Lo Roma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 27:1"/>Shi a ɓo ku shiri zo zhin, ntu geakuyialonyin Roman eya nuwan nya yi, a ku a Bulus ɓedo aza wan-wan ajei, fi n akurkuku guyi tukwoda ho akun, ai yi wo eye ge Jiliyos, esu gu yi nu ɓei n woi. <verse eid="ACT 27:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 27:2"/>Ya kuka n ʼya yi, nkwo ɓa lo kwoi kpegni aba yi mwabegye lo ce yi n Turki edna gbe. Aristakus ɓei gnisun n yi.<verse eid="ACT 27:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 27:3"/>Shi efye ɓei gyi ya si Sida, Jiliyos wa ye ge Bulus wo la gmi gni wa ɓi anugundo gna, ɓa gwo wo agmadayi. <verse eid="ACT 27:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 27:4"/>Shi yi ɓo je lo fi eya, ese dnagmayi kwa ci, to ya mi ya dna eya n zokwo m, har kwa zhin ya duya Saiprus sunbwa. <verse eid="ACT 27:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 27:5"/>Ya duya vivi n Silisiya yi, n Panfiliya yi, ya ɓe ya kpezhi n Mira n Lisiya ekni. <verse eid="ACT 27:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 27:6"/>Nɓo nu eyi tukwoda wato Jiliyos, wa gye eya a Masariyi nya, kwoi gmi Alekzanderiya, kwoi lo Italiya wa ku yi fi nkwo.<verse eid="ACT 27:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7-8" style="v" pubnumber="7,8" sid="ACT 27:7-8"/> Yi ɓo ku anyipyei bwa n mwa, yi sun wahala n eya dna yi, ya si Kimdus deca, ese kwoi gna kala bwa-bwa, ya duya vivi n Karita, ya lo Salmoni. N wahala yi, ya lo peceye peceye, yi lo edna ʼgbe yi har ya ɓe aba ho a yi kwo ge Akpezhiba Manayi, vivi ezhi hoi a yi kwo Laisiya. <verse eid="ACT 27:7-8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 27:9"/>Ya ku kpe zhi ɓo anyipyei n mwa begye. Ntu ge wahala ɓo nyi n aɓa zan-zan n kpai nyi, ntu ge vinyikwo ɓo la shi, Bulus wa gna a kurkuku gu yi tukwoda ge.<verse eid="ACT 27:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 27:10"/>“Ofye, mi gye lo wahala lo abye, kpekni yi ɓa sin asala eya kwa ɓaya, akaya ɓa bwi, aza ɓa bwa nyasan har efi.” <verse eid="ACT 27:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 27:11"/>Ama akurkuku guyi tukwoda to wa wo Bulus ɓe da m, sai aya dna yi tukwoda ɓeda. <verse eid="ACT 27:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 27:12"/>Shi kwo nyi Akpezhiba Manayi to ɓei bmiya n ɓa ɓa zhi n vinyikwo yi m, ayadna yi ɓa gna ge a zhin atna a lo Finiksa ɓo fi ɓo n vinyikwo yi. Finiksa ɓei zhin ayakpezhi ba manayi nu.<verse eid="ACT 27:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 27:13"/>Esa fyewyi ese kwa ya ci peceye ɓa gye ngye kwo bmiya lo ɓa kuka, ɓa lo eya ya, ɓa ya lo vivi edna ʼgbe yi.<verse eid="ACT 27:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14-15" style="v" pubnumber="14,15" sid="ACT 27:14-15"/> Esa sun fyewyi ese nyakwo kwa ya ci n kala yi, kwa ce eya abwaya lo cei nla. Ɓa zhin atna ge ɓa jeze ɓe n eya yi la gbe, to ɓa mi m, ɓa fa kwo kwa ce kwa vi ese lo.<verse eid="ACT 27:14-15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 27:16"/>Ya duya n muse ɓiyi ho avun, a yi muse yi ge Kalauda, nɓo nu n yi ɓo wankma deca, n aya ɓiyi-ɓiyi bmazhin yi, <verse eid="ACT 27:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 27:17"/>Ya mi ya gyi eya nawyi. Ayadnayi ɓai wo dna ge kpesun ese ɓa ce eya abwaya har kwa lo Afrika, kni, ntu deye ɓo, ɓa aje loya nɓa gyi eya she nyi.<verse eid="ACT 27:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 27:18"/>Shi efye ɓo gyi, ɓa gye ese kwoi gna cici, eya atnu-tnu yi ɓa ya akaya kunya fi n nuwan. <verse eid="ACT 27:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 27:19"/>Dna nyipyei tahi, ɓa kun eya atnu-tnu kaya anya yi vinya ɓa she ɓa ya. <verse eid="ACT 27:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 27:20"/>Ese yakwo kwa ci nkala yi to kwoi shan fa m har anyipyei mwa begye, ngmayi, har ɓa bugba gmiya n pwo-pwo ɓo yi.<verse eid="ACT 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 27:21"/>To aza yi gyi nyagyi m, ama Bulus wa yi aya tnu-tnu-zhin yi wa gna ɓa ge, “Ofye, fye ɓo gna fya wo mi ɓeda nkmisunyi, to ye kuka n Akpezhiba manayi m, to yo sin asara ye m. <verse eid="ACT 27:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 27:22"/>Ama agu tu yi ngye apma, zaho-zahoi ta bwi wo wye-wyei nuwan, eya ɓa ɓaya.<verse eid="ACT 27:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 27:23"/>“Ntu ge nsukwoyi naiye, Malaika omi Shekwoyi nya, n mi zhin wo bauta nyi, wa ɓe mi aba. <verse eid="ACT 27:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 27:24"/>Woi gna mi ge, ‘Bulus to wo edna m, ntu ge Shekwoyi ku howyegyi wo, sai ha gni agni n Kaisar abye, woi ɓa aza gni, nɓa gnifi n ya n hoi nyi’. <verse eid="ACT 27:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 27:25"/>Ntu cenu fye ku mi zhi, ntu ge mi la gaiciya ga Shekwoyi, kwo ɓa ze lo nu ngye shi wa da. <verse eid="ACT 27:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 27:26"/>Ama eya ɓa ɓaya ya wankma kpe n muse ho.”<verse eid="ACT 27:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 27:27"/>Dna nyipyei awo-cei-nyihi, ogma ɓedo n ʼse yi n sadu sa, yi kpe n nuwan Adriya nya, yi lo nawyei, na vuyi ese yi ce yi abwa ya, aya dnayi ɓa gye ngye yi ku wu vivi nkma yi. <verse eid="ACT 27:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 27:28"/>Ɓa mwi nuwa lolo ɓa gye kafa 120. Esa fyewyi ɓa je mwi, ɓa gye kafa 90. <verse eid="ACT 27:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 27:29"/>Shi ɓa ɓo gye lonu, ɓa kpe ge yi ku ga okma si, ama ntu edna ɓo ge kpekni agye akuta nyi ndna gbe, ɓa ya eya akpegninya fi nuwan ngun-anyi, ɓai shin-shin ge efye kwo gyi.<verse eid="ACT 27:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 27:30"/>Aya dnayi ho, ɓai ye ge ɓa busi ɓa fwa eya, ɓai la ya ɓai lo eya ɓiɓiyi ɓai zhin ngye ɓa ye ɓa ya eya kpegninya fi n nuwan nabye bwa. <verse eid="ACT 27:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 27:31"/>Ama Bulus wa gna asoja ɓedo nɓa tukwoda yi ge, “Fye ɓa ku fi vinya sai dai ozaho-zaho yi wa kpe dna n ya. <verse eid="ACT 27:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 27:32"/>Asoja ɓa zun owun ya, ɓa fwa eya ɓiɓiyi kwa kaya.”<verse eid="ACT 27:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 27:33"/>Shi efye ɓo la gyi, Bulus wa gyi aza wye ge ɓa ku nyagyi gyi wa ci ge, “Fye ku sun nu, a mako ngun aba to fyei to nyagyi wo m. <verse eid="ACT 27:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 27:34"/>Mi gyi fye wye fye ku nyagyi ntu fye lafiya ɓo! Ntu ge kwo tukwoyi gmanyi oza ho nya, kwo ta bwi m.”<verse eid="ACT 27:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 27:35"/>Shi wo ɓo zo da lonu, wa la bredi wa zhin Shekwoyi godiya nɓa abye vinya, wa sa wa gyi. <verse eid="ACT 27:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 27:36"/>Nsayi-sayi oɓa vinya ɓa bwa sauki ɓa ya nyagyi gyi. <verse eid="ACT 27:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 27:37"/>Aza vinya tagyi aba, ncei shi tnaba cei tnanyi (276) eyi yewa nu n yi ɓei fi n eya yi vinya. <verse eid="ACT 27:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 27:38"/>Shi aɓo ku nyagyi gyi aya atnu-tnu yi ɓa kun alkama ɓa she ya fi n nuwan eya shanwo kwa ce gmiya.<verse eid="ACT 27:38"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Eya La aya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 27:39"/>Shi efye ɓo la gyi, to ɓa kpe aba nɓa zhi-n ama ɓa ta wye ɓa gye okma n amwi yi, ɓa zhin shaula ge kwo ese ɓa ce ɓa bwaya fi akuta, kwa kun ɓa va kpe na mwi. <verse eid="ACT 27:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 27:40"/>Ɓa gna ɓa ɓa zhin atna ɓa gbe awun ya ɓa fwa eya akpezhi nya ya fi n nuwan, ɓa ya eya avun, ɓa ku eje wu abye ɓa lo edna gbe. <verse eid="ACT 27:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 27:41"/>Ama eya tukwo kwa lo kwa bi dna n amwi. Eya tukwo kwa bi dna dei-dei, eya avun kwa la wu, nuwan dokwo kwoi ɓe kwoi lu kwo nkalayi har eya kwa ya ɓaya.<verse eid="ACT 27:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 27:42"/>Asoja ɓa gna oɓa tukwoda ge, ɓa ku aza wan-wan wu vinya kada oza ho nɓa mi wa she nuwan wa piya wa busi. <verse eid="ACT 27:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 27:43"/>Ama Jiliyos to ɓei ye ge awu Bulus m, wa gna ɓa ge a to zhin lo nu m. Wa gna ɓa ge oza n wo ɓa mi wa she nuwan wo she wa piya tu nkma. <verse eid="ACT 27:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 27:44"/>Aza nɓa ce nyi, ɓa zhin atna ɓa wan eya apisayi ɓa wan kma. Elonu aza vinya ɓa ku wan kma n lafiya yi.<verse eid="ACT 27:44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="ACT 28"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 28:1"/>Esa fyewyi ya kpe ge muse n ya wankma kpe nyi, a yi kwo ge Malita nu. <verse eid="ACT 28:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 28:2"/>Aza nɓa ɓei fi ɓo nyi ɓa wu yi yeye, ɓa ku ena fin yi ya wye ntu ogma ɓo nkwo ɓo lu yi, ese yi fu yi nyi.<verse eid="ACT 28:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 28:3"/>Ngye shi Bulus ɓo ku ashinwan wa ya kpe nna, gbezhi kwa kun ntu gugurgu ɓo, kwa knanyi Bulus nbwa. <verse eid="ACT 28:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 28:4"/>Shi a Malitayi ɓei gye kwo shegyi n Bulus bwa, ɓa gna aje ge, “Ozaye zhin zawuyi nu ɓehinhin! Wo la pwo n nuwan, ama ɓenukwoyi kwo nu ta ye ge wo pwo m.”<verse eid="ACT 28:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 28:5"/>Ama Bulus wa mi kwo ya fi n na, wa ce wo nya gni ntna ɓoho. <verse eid="ACT 28:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 28:6"/>Aza yi bwa zhi ɓai gye ge, esa fyewyi wo ɓa ya sun, wa miyashi wa fi, amma shi ɓa ɓo gye esa la mwa to ɓoho kwoi zhin wo m, ɓa ɓeda shando ɓa gna ge, wo zhin shekwoyi ho nu.<verse eid="ACT 28:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 28:7"/>Vivi aba yi n yi ɓo wankma nyi, oza ho ɓei nyi ɓo a yi ge Bubliyus, wo nu ɓo zhin gwamna muse yi nya. Wa gwo yi n bugba bui-bui yi, wa ga yi nyagyi har anyipyei ngun-ata. <verse eid="ACT 28:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 28:8"/>Bubliyus dada wo ɓo n nyasan yi, nayi nagun ɓedo n goro-san yi. Bulus wa lo wa zhin aduwa, wa to wo bwa wa wo kagna. <verse eid="ACT 28:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 28:9"/>Azaje vinya, nɓa to ɓei n lafiya yi m n muse yi, ɓa ɓe a ɓa kagna. <verse eid="ACT 28:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 28:10"/>Ntu deye ɓo aza ɓa ɓe yi n kyauta yi n mwa, esa nu yi ɓo ye ya kuka, aza ɓa ɓe yi na nya yi gbo-gbo n yi ɓa zhin akma n cei n zokwo. <verse eid="ACT 28:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 28:11"/>Apya ɓo ku sun ngun-ata, ngye shi eya ɓei ɓaya, ya kuka njesun, nsa deye yi ɓo zan-zan n eya Alekzandariya nya yi nkwo zhin vinyikwo shi n muse hi, ai yi kwo ge “Aza aba.” <verse eid="ACT 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 28:12"/>Eyi akpezhiba kmisunyi sai Sirakusa, ya bwa anyipyei ɓo ngun-ata. <verse eid="ACT 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 28:13"/>Ya kuka ɓo ya pmi lo Rigiyum, ya bwa nyipyei gmanyi ese kudu nya kwa ya ci, nyipyei bahi yisi Butiyoli, <verse eid="ACT 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 28:14"/>Nɓo ya sun a Yesu viyi hoi, ɓa gyi yi wye ge yi ku fi nɓa yi har anyipyei tnaba. Ya kpe kala ku ya lo Roma.<verse eid="ACT 28:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 28:15"/>Eyi azaje nɓa ɓei fi n Roma nyi, ɓa ku wo ge yi ɓe lo, ɓa ɓe shegun yi n Abiyu gnikwo. Azado ɓa shegun yi n Ashiragyi ngun-ata. Shi Bulus ɓo gye ɓa, wa zhin Shekwoyi godiya, wa bwa bugba kala.<verse eid="ACT 28:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 28:16"/>Shi yi ɓo si Roma, a ye Bulus ge wo dna wo nya abaho-baho n wo ɓa dna, sai dai soja ɓei zhin woi gu wo. <verse eid="ACT 28:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 28:17"/>Shi wo ɓo si wa bwa anyipyei ngun ata, wa yi a Yahudiyi atukwoda wa da ɓo nɓai wa gna, “Omi azaje, a Yahudiyi nɓa fi n Urushelima nyi, ɓa na wan mi ɓai dna mi a Romayi akun, ko shi ko nyi mi to zhin nyaho-nyaho yi m, ko ma zhi za wuya kwo ɓo n kwo zhin kunnu eyi azakwoyi nya m.<verse eid="ACT 28:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 28:18"/>“A Romayi ɓa ku owa da mi, ɓai ye ɓa ya mi, ntu ge ɓa to sun nyaho n mi aba nkwo kunce lo nfi yi, ngye shi a Yahudiyi atukwoda ɓei gna ge awu mi nyi m. <verse eid="ACT 28:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 28:19"/>Shi a Yahudiyi atukwoda to ɓo ye a shaula yi m, to a wun aje bugba m, ma gye ko la mi ze tile ma gyi abye n ɓeda yi kwa lo Kaisar aba. <verse eid="ACT 28:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 28:20"/>Ma yi fye ge fye ɓe n naiye ge ya kpe ajeye, magna fye ge, mi dna n agma ye ge, mi n gaiciya ga yi lo ge Masihu wa ɓe nu.”<verse eid="ACT 28:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 28:21"/>ʼBa ye ɓa gna wo ge, “Yi to wo ɓoho tu nho tukwo m! Yi to bwa wasika n Yahudiya, ko naza nɓa kun lo n Urushelima, ɓai ɓe iya nyi m. <verse eid="ACT 28:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 28:22"/>Ama yi ce pma ya wo enya ho gaiciya yi ga, enya dei n yi kpe lo, okwo nu ge abaho-bahoi vinya, aza ta ye a Yesu viyi lo m.”<verse eid="ACT 28:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 28:23"/>Ɓa esa shi, nwyihi aza nmwa begye ɓa yezhi n wo puwa. Wa daɓo n ɓai tu Shekwoyi ebemi ɓo, woi wu ɓa aɓo ntu Yesu ɓo ngye shi aka fi n Littafi Gyi-gyi-yi, wa ya ɓa wu n attaura Musa nya ɓedo anabi yi, Wa ya ɓa wu n labmi yi har wyeshe!<verse eid="ACT 28:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 28:24"/>Azaho ɓa ku gaiciya ga, ama azaho to ɓa gaiciya m. <verse eid="ACT 28:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 28:25"/>Ɓa na Bo aje yi n mwa, ɓa kuka n ɓeda gmanyi shi n Bulus ɓo da ge, “Zafun Gyi-gyiyi ɓo ku ɓeda da cewo n anabi Ishaya gbe ge,<verse eid="ACT 28:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 28:26"/>“Wa gna a Yahudiyi ge, ‘Fye ɓa wo fyei gye ama fye ta bwa awyega m, <verse eid="ACT 28:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 28:27"/>ntu ge ofye abugba shin-shin lo, ofye atnubua ta ye lo ɓa wo m, fyei ku fye awye kpe to fya bwa awye gam, ntu ge fye ta ye lo fya gye, fya wo, fya bwa awye ga, fya ɓe ma ka fye gna m.’ <verse eid="ACT 28:27"/><verse number="28-29" style="v" pubnumber="28,29" sid="ACT 28:28-29"/> Mi ye fya kpe ge, gni-gni Shekwoyi nya ye, kwo nyi ntu abyedo ɓo nu ce, ɓai ɓa gwo kwo.”<verse eid="ACT 28:28-29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 28:30"/>Bulus wa wo nya dna n wohin haya nyakun har aye ngun aba, woi gwo azhiɓeyi doho-doho nɓa ɓei ɓe wo wyegye. <verse eid="ACT 28:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 28:31"/>Woi gna ɓa Shekwoyi ebe mi ɓo, n Dagayi Yesu Kristi yi, zaho-zaho yi to ɓo wo wo ɓi m.<verse eid="ACT 28:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 28"/>
</usx>
